NK020(wa)003:1: // 'dus pa mdo'i cho ga'i zur 'debs dpag bsam snye ma bzhugs so //
NK020(wa)003:3: 'dus pa mdo'i sgrub dkyil sgrub khog dang bcas pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4: zur 'debs las rab 'byams kyi 'dod pa ster byed
NK020(wa)003:5: dpag bsam snye ma zhes bya ba /
NK020(wa)003:6: bla ma dang 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:7: mi 'gyur mchog bde'i sgyu 'phrul rol pa'i gar //
NK020(wa)003:8: grangs med zhi khro'i 'khor lo bsgyur ba po //
NK020(wa)003:9: rigs kun khyab bdag dpal ldan rdo rje sems //
NK020(wa)003:10: bka' drin mnyam med bla ma'i zhabs la 'dud //
NK020(wa)003:11: 'dus pa mdo yi sgrub thabs dkyil chog dang //
NK020(wa)003:12: sgrub khog bcas pa'i zur 'debs phyogs gcig tu //
NK020(wa)003:13: sdebs pa phrin las rab 'byams 'dod pa'i 'bras //
NK020(wa)003:14: ster byed dpag bsam snye ma deng 'dir 'khrungs //
NK020(wa)003:15: 'dir slob dpon gyis sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa
NK020(wa)003:16: sogs la nye bar mkho ba lha'i ngo bo mdo
NK020(wa)003:17: thun mong ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams a nu rang lugs
NK020(wa)003:18: kyi sgrub tshul ltar lus dkyil du 'god pa'i las
NK020(wa)003:19: byang gnas skabs khyer bde ba'i ched du lung chung
NK020(wa)003:20: ba zhi thung dang khro thung la brten nas 'bri
NK020(wa)003:21: bar bya ste / de la thog mar zhi khro thun mong gi sngon 'gro ni /
NK020(wa)003:22: gnas dben par rten dang mchod gtor sogs nye bar mkho ba'i yo byad rnams tshogs par byas la /
NK020(wa)003:23: chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa kun tu
NK020(wa)003:24: bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i rang rtsal
NK020(wa)003:25: las / badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:27: bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag
NK020(wa)003:28: zhag gcig phyag gnyis pa rdo rje dang dung khrag
NK020(wa)003:29: 'dzin pa yum kro d+h+ai shwa d+ai ma dang mnyam
NK020(wa)003:31: phata phata badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la /
NK020(wa)003:34: thugs ka'i h+aum las khro bo'i sprin spros pas gdug pa can thams cad tshar bcad /
NK020(wa)003:35: tshur 'dus pa las steng 'og phyogs mtshams bcur nyi ma la gnas pa'i phyogs skyong bcu'i snying gar /
NK020(wa)003:36: badz+ra kro d+ha k+ai la ya phata dzah zhes phur
NK020(wa)003:37: bu'i tshul du btab pa rnams khro bo bcur gyur
NK020(wa)003:38: pa ni / h+aum k+aa ra badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:39: de bzhin du h+aum k+aa ra'i tshab tu /
NK020(wa)003:47: tree lo kya bi dza ya /
NK020(wa)003:48: ma h+aa ba la rnams bcug ste /
NK020(wa)003:49: zhes brjod pa'i rkyen gyis rim pa bzhin /
NK020(wa)003:54: lho nub tu mi g.yo ba /
NK020(wa)003:58: byar shar du khams gsum rnam rgyal /
NK020(wa)003:59: 'og tu stobs po che rnams sku stod khro bo
NK020(wa)003:60: la smad phur bu 'bar ba'i rnam pas bgegs la
NK020(wa)003:61: gzir ba / dbyings kyi yum can /
NK020(wa)003:62: sprul pa'i phra men nyi shu dang yang sprul bye
NK020(wa)003:63: ba sa ya'i tshogs kyi sprin 'phro bas phyogs kun
NK020(wa)003:64: gtams te cis kyang mi shigs par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)003:66: steng 'og phyogs mtshams dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:67: khro bcu yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK020(wa)003:68: phyogs bcur gnas pa'i bgegs rnams kun bsal nas //
NK020(wa)003:69: sgrub pa'i bar gcod ming yang med par shog /
NK020(wa)003:72: rang gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK020(wa)003:73: bla ma rig 'dzin zhi khro rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i
NK020(wa)003:74: tshogs dang bcas pa mkha' khyab tu sad par mos
NK020(wa)003:75: la / ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags byas pa te /
NK020(wa)003:77: sgrib pa rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:78: yid kyis mngon du bshags pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:79: sgrib pa ye nas dag pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:80: ye shes rnam gnyis mngon du gsal bar shog /
NK020(wa)003:82: de nas mchod rdzas rnams ram yam kham gis bsregs gtor bkrus te stong par sbyangs /
NK020(wa)003:83: stong pa'i ngang las snod dbyings kyi b+hany+dzana bcud dam
NK020(wa)003:84: rdzas bcu ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gnas pa'i dbus
NK020(wa)003:85: su che mchog he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:86: bdag bdud rtsi 'khyil bar gsal ba'i g.yon pa'i mtheb srin la rta mgrin yab yum /
NK020(wa)003:89: bdag gi 'od kyis 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi bsdus nas thim pas zhu zhing /
NK020(wa)003:90: rta mgrin yab yum rol pa'i byang sems dang ro
NK020(wa)003:91: gcig tu 'dres nas ye shes kyi bdud rtsir gyur
NK020(wa)003:92: / spro na dngos grub blang ba dang bsang gtor gsum yang bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:93: stong pa'i ngang las gtor gzhong yum lnga'i mkha' klong du /
NK020(wa)003:94: ma h+aa ba lim ta te dzo ba lid+ta ba
NK020(wa)003:95: la b+aa d+ya gu h+ya sa ma ya h+aum phata
NK020(wa)003:97: gtor ma ye shes lnga'i rol pa 'dod yon longs spyod kyi gter du gyur /
NK020(wa)003:98: stong ba'i ngang las snod pad+ma 'bar ba'i dbyings su /
NK020(wa)003:99: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK020(wa)003:101: bcud rak+ta ye shes kyi rba klong 'khrug pa la
NK020(wa)003:102: khams gsum gyi rak+ta thams cad zhu zhing 'dres par
NK020(wa)003:103: gyur / stong pa'i ngang las mchod snod dbyings kyi
NK020(wa)003:104: zhing khams su mchod rdzas ye shes lnga'i rnam rol
NK020(wa)003:106: na ma s+saman+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga na sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:107: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK020(wa)003:110: zhes brjod pas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK020(wa)003:112: thun mong rdzas kyi dngos po cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)003:113: mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK020(wa)003:114: 'dod pa'i yon tan yongs su rdzogs gyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:115: dus gsum bde gshegs ma lus mchod par shog /
NK020(wa)003:122: dbyings ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK020(wa)003:123: ye shes rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)003:124: gnyis dbyer med pa'i sras bde ba chen po rtsa
NK020(wa)003:125: ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor las sngags kyi
NK020(wa)003:126: sgra gdangs kyis rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor du
NK020(wa)003:128: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra /
NK020(wa)003:129: du ti nan rat+na s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma /
NK020(wa)003:131: nam mkha' thams cad yum lnga'i mkha' klong 'byung lnga'i
NK020(wa)003:132: dkyil 'khor la brten gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo
NK020(wa)003:133: bzhi pa rta babs brgyad kyis brgyan pa'i dbus su
NK020(wa)003:134: seng ges btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri pad nyi
NK020(wa)003:135: zla ba brtsegs pa'i gdan dang bcas pa bkra lam
NK020(wa)003:138: snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:139: gzhal yas dbang chen bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:140: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:141: 'og min gnas su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:144: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa m+aan+ta a /
NK020(wa)003:146: gdan gyi steng du bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK020(wa)003:147: kun tu bzang po sku mdog mthing ga zhi zhing
NK020(wa)003:148: rab tu 'dzum pa'i nyams can mtshan dang dpe byad
NK020(wa)003:150: phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can rdo rje'i
NK020(wa)003:151: skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'i pang du yum kun
NK020(wa)003:152: tu bzang mo sngon mo phyag gnyis kyis yab la
NK020(wa)003:153: 'khyud cing pad+ma'i skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba /
NK020(wa)003:154: gnyis ka'ang dar gyi chas gos lnga dang rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis spras te /
NK020(wa)003:155: 'od zer bye ba drug phrag drug 'phro ba'i klong
NK020(wa)003:156: na bde stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs
NK020(wa)003:157: pa'o // rang gzhi lus kun bzang yab yum du
NK020(wa)003:158: gsal ba'i thugs kar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte
NK020(wa)003:159: pa'o // bar / h+aum m+aum zhes pas /
NK020(wa)003:160: mi bskyod pa yab yum sngon po rdor dril /
NK020(wa)003:163: rnam snang yab yum dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK020(wa)003:165: lhor rin 'byung yab yum ser po rin po che dang dril bu /
NK020(wa)003:167: nub tu snang mtha' yab yum dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK020(wa)003:169: byang du don grub yab yum ljang khu ral gri dang dril bu /
NK020(wa)003:170: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:171: rigs lnga yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:172: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:173: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK020(wa)003:175: g.yas phyogs kyi dbang po'i rtsa bzhi la /
NK020(wa)003:177: mig la sa snying dang sgeg mo /
NK020(wa)003:178: dz+rim h+r+aih rna bar phyag rdor dang glu ma /
NK020(wa)003:180: sna la nam snying dang phreng ba ma /
NK020(wa)003:182: lce la spyan ras gzigs dang gar ma /
NK020(wa)003:183: g.yon phyogs kyi dbang po la /
NK020(wa)003:184: mee dzah mig la byams pa dang spos ma /
NK020(wa)003:186: rna bar sgrib sel dang me tog ma /
NK020(wa)003:188: sna la kun bzang dang mar me ma /
NK020(wa)003:189: mum hoh lce la 'jam dpal dang dri chab ma /
NK020(wa)003:190: dbang po rnam shes yul dus cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:191: sems dpa' sems ma bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:192: thams cad lha dang lha mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:193: zhing dang spyod yul yongs su dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:195: snying ga'i 'khor lo'i mdun dang rgyab tu /
NK020(wa)003:197: byed pa po dang bya ba mo /
NK020(wa)003:198: yid dang chos kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:199: kun bzang yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:200: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:201: chos sku 'gyur med lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:203: k+r+aim dpral bar lha'i thub pa /
NK020(wa)003:204: h+aum trum lce steng du lha min gyi thub pa /
NK020(wa)003:205: srum snying gar mi'i thub pa /
NK020(wa)003:206: bram lte bar byol song gi thub pa /
NK020(wa)003:207: k+sham gsang bar yi dwags kyi thub pa /
NK020(wa)003:208: ye rkang mthil g.yon par dmyal ba'i thub pa /
NK020(wa)003:209: 'gro ba rigs drug dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:210: thub pa drug tu bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:211: rol pa cir yang snang ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:212: sangs rgyas mdzad pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:214: rkang lag gi mthil bzhi la /
NK020(wa)003:215: h+aum dzah lag g.yas su gshin rje gshed dang lcags kyu ma /
NK020(wa)003:216: h+aum h+aum g.yon par stobs chen dang zhags pa ma /
NK020(wa)003:218: rkang g.yon la rta mgrin dang lcags sgrog ma /
NK020(wa)003:219: h+aum hoh g.yas par bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang dril bu ma /
NK020(wa)003:220: yan lag bzhi yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:221: sgo ba yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:222: bar du gcod pa ma lus kun bsal nas //
NK020(wa)003:223: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:225: de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo thams cad dwangs
NK020(wa)003:226: pa'i mtsho la gza' skar shar ba ltar bkra lam
NK020(wa)003:228: de nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:229: rigs lnga'i dbang rgya spyi bo'i gnas lngar 'jog cing /
NK020(wa)003:230: ma h+aa shunya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)003:236: spyi bo'i gnas lngar de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga
NK020(wa)003:237: yab yum rjes chags kyis zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i
NK020(wa)003:238: chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK020(wa)003:239: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngas dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:241: rdo rje'i phyag rgya gnas gsum du gtug cing /
NK020(wa)003:242: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)003:244: gnas gsum du zla ba pad+ma nyi ma la gnas pa'i +aahh+aum /
NK020(wa)003:245: 'od zer 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang /
NK020(wa)003:247: mi bskyod pa rnams kyis rgyas btab par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:249: lus ngag yid gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:250: dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK020(wa)003:251: nyon mongs dngos po ma lus kun byang nas /
NK020(wa)003:252: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:254: de nas ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drang ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:255: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah sa snyan gsan phab la //
NK020(wa)003:256: thugs rje'i lcags kyu sogs kyi mthar /
NK020(wa)003:257: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzah h+aum bam hohs spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)003:258: dzah h+aum bam hohs bstim la /
NK020(wa)003:259: tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par byas te /
NK020(wa)003:260: dam tshig gi 'khor lo dang dbyer med du bzhugs par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:262: sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir bde gshegs spyan drangs bstim pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:263: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:264: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:266: de nas dbyings la ye shes sam lha la lha
NK020(wa)003:267: rol pa'i tshul gyis phyag mchod byas par mos la
NK020(wa)003:268: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa t+wa ban+d+ha n+aam ka ro mi /
NK020(wa)003:269: a ti pu hoh pra ti pu hoh zhes phyag byas la /
NK020(wa)003:271: bzang ngan che chung khyad par cir dkyil 'khor lha
NK020(wa)003:272: la phyag btsal byin ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i
NK020(wa)003:273: don gnyis su med par lhun gyis na mo h+aum
NK020(wa)003:275: 'byung ba chen po nam mkha' ni //
NK020(wa)003:276: 'byung ba chen po lnga yi mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:279: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs kyis kun bzang /
NK020(wa)003:280: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa sogs kyis zhabs bsil /
NK020(wa)003:281: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+hu pe d+h+au /
NK020(wa)003:286: bdag dang gzhan gyi dngos po cir dkyil 'khor lha
NK020(wa)003:287: rnams mchod pa'i 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i don
NK020(wa)003:288: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis na mo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:289: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa his sman mchod phul /
NK020(wa)003:291: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:292: zhes sman gyis dngos grub blangs la /
NK020(wa)003:294: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir bdud rtsi sman
NK020(wa)003:295: mchog mchod pa'i byin yun du gnod pa'i nad rnams
NK020(wa)003:296: kun bral nas // skye shi med par lhun gyis grub na mo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:297: ma h+aa bi lim ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa his gtor ma phul la /
NK020(wa)003:299: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir dam rdzas gtor
NK020(wa)003:300: mas mchod pa'i byin 'phral du skabs 'tshol gnod pa
NK020(wa)003:301: kun bsal nas // 'gyur ba med par lhun na mo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:302: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa
NK020(wa)003:303: ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko & ham
NK020(wa)003:304: / zhes lha thams cad snyoms 'jug gi bde bas mnyes par bsam pa sbyor mchod dang /
NK020(wa)003:305: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK020(wa)003:306: ces byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis sprin spros
NK020(wa)003:307: pas 'khor ba'i 'khrul rtog 'od gsal gyi dbyings su
NK020(wa)003:308: bsgral bas bsgral mchod phul la /
NK020(wa)003:310: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir tan gan rnam
NK020(wa)003:311: gnyis phul ba'i byin nyon mongs dug gsum rtsa nas
NK020(wa)003:312: dag gyur te // bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:314: ma h+aa p+au dza hoh zhes pas snang ba thams
NK020(wa)003:315: cad 'dod yon gyi rol mor 'char zhing de nyid
NK020(wa)003:316: dbyings rig dbyer med bde ba chen por ro mnyam
NK020(wa)003:318: yul dang dbang po'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:319: 'dod yon rnam lngas mchod pa'i byin yul sems gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:320: spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:324: dbyings kun rang bzhin rnam dag pas //
NK020(wa)003:325: thugs rje'i dbang gis skur bzhengs pa //
NK020(wa)003:326: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs dag /
NK020(wa)003:327: rang snang lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:330: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:331: glu dang sgra snyan rol mos bstod pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)003:332: thams cad theg pa chen po'i sgrar gyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:333: gsang sngags don nyid kun gyis rtogs par shog /
NK020(wa)003:335: smon lam dang 'dod don gsol ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:336: hoh phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK020(wa)003:337: cad kyi bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje
NK020(wa)003:338: sems dpa' la sogs pa rigs lnga rgyal ba rgya
NK020(wa)003:339: mtsho 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bcas pa
NK020(wa)003:340: thams cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)003:341: bdag cag rnal 'byor gyi mchod pa dam pa rig
NK020(wa)003:342: pa'i khyad par las byung ba phyi nang gsang ba
NK020(wa)003:343: gsum gyi tshul du phul bas sku gsung thugs kyi
NK020(wa)003:344: rgyud mnyes pa chen pos khyab par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:345: de'i byin rlabs kyi mtha' yas ba'i sems can thams
NK020(wa)003:346: cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur cig
NK020(wa)003:347: / bdag cag gi dam tshig nyams pa thams cad
NK020(wa)003:348: skongs te dngos grub kyi snod du gyur nas yi
NK020(wa)003:349: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar sangs rgyas te
NK020(wa)003:350: 'khor ba kar dag par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:351: a la la hoh zhes dang /
NK020(wa)003:352: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon par zhugs pa rnams //
NK020(wa)003:355: yid la bsam pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:356: smon lam mngon du btab pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:357: yid la ci bsam lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK020(wa)003:358: 'gro don ma lus lhun gyi grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:361: gzhi lus kyi ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar zla
NK020(wa)003:362: ba la yig sngon po bzla bya'i sngags phreng gis
NK020(wa)003:364: lus dkyil gyi lha rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK020(wa)003:365: so so'i sku las 'phros pa'i 'od zer gyis mkha' khyab kyi rgyal ba rnams mchod /
NK020(wa)003:366: sems can thams cad kyi sgo gsum gyi sdig sgrib
NK020(wa)003:367: sbyangs te rang gzhin lha sngags 'od gsal gyi 'khor
NK020(wa)003:368: lo / gnas pa mngon du byas sangs rgyas thams
NK020(wa)003:369: cad kyi rdo rje gsum dang dbyer med du gyur
NK020(wa)003:370: lo / / 'od zer de rnams slar 'dus rang
NK020(wa)003:371: la thim pas khams gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du sad
NK020(wa)003:372: lo / / par mos la / lus kyi sgul bskyod ci byas dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK020(wa)003:373: ngag gi bzlas brjod chos nyid kyi sgra gdangs //
NK020(wa)003:374: sems kyi dran rtog dbyings rig dbyer med rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems su rtogs par byas te /
NK020(wa)003:375: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:376: zhes spyi 'dzab kho na bzla zhing //
NK020(wa)003:377: spro na sgrub thabs rgyas pa ltar zhi ba'i bskyed sngags rnams kyang ci nus bazla'o //
NK020(wa)003:379: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:380: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi'i 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)003:381: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:382: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:384: des zhi lung gi dngos gzhi tshar ro //
NK020(wa)003:385: gnyis pa khro bo'i lung ni //
NK020(wa)003:386: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa rtsa ba
NK020(wa)003:387: byang chub kyi sems rang byung gi ye shes ma
NK020(wa)003:388: 'dres yongs rdzogs su gsal ba las /
NK020(wa)003:389: sngags kyi sgra gdangs kyis rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor du sad par gyur pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:390: e yam ra sum kem ram /
NK020(wa)003:391: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+ha ny+dza dz+ny+aa na tsakra /
NK020(wa)003:392: s+aur+ya man+da la de ba tish+tha nam ti ra bam /
NK020(wa)003:394: rang gi sems dbugs khrag dang sha rus drod rnams
NK020(wa)003:395: ye shes kyi rtsal snang dur khrod kyi rdzas kyi
NK020(wa)003:396: ngo bo las / yum lnga'i mkha' klong 'byung lnga'i
NK020(wa)003:397: dkyil 'khor du gsal ba la brten pa'i dur khrod
NK020(wa)003:398: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa
NK020(wa)003:399: rta babs brgyad kyis brgyan pa'i dbus su 'khor lo
NK020(wa)003:400: rtsibs brgyad rdo rje'i brag chen pad nyi zla ba
NK020(wa)003:401: rnams brtsegs pa'i steng du dbang phyug khyo shugs nyi
NK020(wa)003:402: shu rtsa bzhi byol song gtso bo brgyad kyis barjisa
NK020(wa)003:403: pa'i gdan dang bcas pa gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)003:405: dur khrod rdzas kyi dngos po cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)003:406: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:407: rdzas su lta ba'i rtog pa kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)003:408: gnas mchog rab 'byams lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:410: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:411: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:413: gdan gyi steng du bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK020(wa)003:414: chen po che mchog he ru ka sku mdog mthing
NK020(wa)003:415: nag 'bar ba chen po'i gzi byin can /
NK020(wa)003:416: mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum /
NK020(wa)003:417: phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rdo rje rtse dgu rtse lnga rtse gsum pa /
NK020(wa)003:419: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum dor stabs kyis stan la rol pa /
NK020(wa)003:420: yum gnam zhal dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma sngon mo
NK020(wa)003:421: g.yas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon thod khrag stob pa
NK020(wa)003:422: / gnyis ka'ang gar gyi nyams dgus sgeg cing dur
NK020(wa)003:423: khrod rol pa'i chas can ye shes kyi me 'bar
NK020(wa)003:425: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK020(wa)003:426: zhabs kyi gdan khri nas gtsug tor man chad la
NK020(wa)003:427: rdzogs par snang ba'i bdag nyid chen por gyur pa'o
NK020(wa)003:428: // rang gzhi lus che mchog he ru kar gsal
NK020(wa)003:429: ba'i thugs kar 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad lte ba dang
NK020(wa)003:430: // bcas pa la / tsit+ta'i rtsa dgu'i bcud he ru ka dgu dang /
NK020(wa)003:431: rtsa dgu kro d+h+ai dgur gsal ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:434: rdo rje khrag 'thung mthing ga rdo rje dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:435: rtsibs brgyad kyi shar du h+aum h+aum sangs rgyas khrag 'thung smug nag 'khor lo dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:436: lhor h+aum h+aum rin chen khrag 'thung ser nag rtse gsum dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:437: nub tu h+aum h+aum pad+ma khrag 'thung dmar nag ral gri dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:438: byang du h+aum h+aum las kyi khrag 'thung ljang nag rgya gram dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:439: shar lhor h+aum h+aum rak+sha he ru ka mthing nag dbyug to dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:440: lho nub tu h+aum h+aum sa nu he ru ka ser nag dgra s+t+wa dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:441: nub byang du h+aum h+aum gu h+ya he ru ka dud kha ral gri dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:442: byang shar du h+aum h+aum yak+sha he ru ka ljang nag be con dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)003:443: de thams cad kyang gar dgu'i nyams can dur khrod
NK020(wa)003:444: kyi chas kyis brgyan te rang mdog dang mtshungs pa'i
NK020(wa)003:445: yum rnams g.yas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon dung khrag
NK020(wa)003:447: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum gyis dregs pa khyo shugs dang /
NK020(wa)003:448: khyad par rigs lnga'i khrag 'thung lngas byol song gdug pa can zung re dang bcas pa bardzisa pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:450: ru tra rnam gsum dngos po cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)003:451: khrag 'thung dgu ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:452: bdud dang srin po'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)003:453: ye shes dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:455: khams gsum sa dgu'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:456: yum chen dgu ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:457: ma bdud srin mo'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)003:458: thig le dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:460: dbang rten gyi rtsa zung bzhi'i rtsa nang du gnas ma brgyad ni /
NK020(wa)003:461: mig gnyis su ha ha zhes pas g.yas par goo r+ai dang /
NK020(wa)003:463: rna ba g.yas g.yon du ha ha pe t+aa li dang g+hasma r+ai /
NK020(wa)003:464: sna g.yas g.yon du ha ha tsoo r+ai dang sme sha /
NK020(wa)003:465: lce'i g.yas g.yon gyi char ha ha pra mo h+aa dang tsan+da l+ai /
NK020(wa)003:467: rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:468: goo r+ai brgyad du bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:469: yul la mngon par rtog pa kun bcom nas //
NK020(wa)003:470: rnam par rtog pa'i 'du shes med par shog /
NK020(wa)003:472: dbang rten gyi rtsa'i phyir rol tu yul ma brgyad ni /
NK020(wa)003:473: mig g.yas g.yon la he he seng gdong ma dang rgod gdong ma /
NK020(wa)003:474: rna ba g.yas g.yon du he he wa gdang dang kang+ka'i gdong ma /
NK020(wa)003:475: sna g.yas g.yon du he he stag gdong ma dang khwa gdong ma /
NK020(wa)003:476: lce'i g.yas g.yon du he he khyi gdong ma dang 'ug gdong ma /
NK020(wa)003:478: dur khrod brgyad kyi dngos po cir phra men brgyad
NK020(wa)003:479: du bsgoms pa'i dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun
NK020(wa)003:480: bsgral nas // rnal 'byor bar chod ming yang med par shog /
NK020(wa)003:482: yan lag gi mthil bzhi la sgo ma bzhi ni /
NK020(wa)003:483: lag pa g.yas g.yon du phata phata rta gdong ma dang phag gdong ma /
NK020(wa)003:484: rkang pa g.yon g.yas su phata phata sprel gdong ma dang spyang gdong ma /
NK020(wa)003:486: skye rga na 'chi'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:487: sgo ma bzhi ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:488: bar du gcod pa'i bdud bzhi kun bcom nas //
NK020(wa)003:489: skye gnas rnam bzhi'i ming yang med par shog /
NK020(wa)003:491: gnas yul sgo skyong rnams sku mdog zhal dang phyag
NK020(wa)003:492: mtshan rgyan rnams sgrub thabs rgyas pa ltar gsal gdab
NK020(wa)003:493: bo // lus kyi phyogs mtshams su 'bar ma brgyad ni //
NK020(wa)003:495: snying gar nyi zer can ma /
NK020(wa)003:497: g.yas phyogs kyi nu mar me khyer glog phreng ma /
NK020(wa)003:501: sog par srin mo ral gri'i skra can /
NK020(wa)003:503: sog phrag tu klu mo lce 'bebs ma /
NK020(wa)003:505: g.yon phyogs kyi sog par gnod sbyin khyung thogs ma /
NK020(wa)003:509: nu mar mig 'byin snying sreg ma ste /
NK020(wa)003:510: thams cad kyang sku mdog dmar nag rdo rje dang dung khrag bsnams pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:512: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi dngos po cir spor ma brgyad
NK020(wa)003:513: du bsgoms pa'i lha srin sde brgyad bar chad kun
NK020(wa)003:514: bsgral nas // 'jig rten bar chad ming yang na mo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:515: sog pa'i 'og gi g.yas g.yon gyi rtsib ma dang
NK020(wa)003:516: po gnyis gnyis te nam tshong rtsib ma bzhi la
NK020(wa)003:518: dzah g.yas kyi dang por dkar mo rgyas 'debs ma rdo rje /
NK020(wa)003:520: g.yon dang por ser mo tshe 'phel ma mda' gzhu /
NK020(wa)003:522: g.yon 'og mar dmar mo dbang sdud ma rgyal mtshan /
NK020(wa)003:523: hoh g.yas 'og mar nag mo rmongs byed ma dril bu /
NK020(wa)003:525: dwangs ma bzhi yi dngos po cir gsang ba'i yum
NK020(wa)003:526: bzhi bsgoms pa'i bem por lta ba'i mtshan ma kun
NK020(wa)003:527: bsal nas // thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK020(wa)003:529: mjing tshigs lnga sgal tshig nyi shu mjug tshigs gsum
NK020(wa)003:530: rnams sdoms pa'i sgal tshigs nyer brgyad la b+h+yo zhes
NK020(wa)003:531: pas dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad po rang
NK020(wa)003:532: rang gi mgo brnyan can sku mdog phyag mtshan dang
NK020(wa)003:534: yang na thams cad kyang smug nag rtse gsum thogs pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:535: so sum cu rtsa gnyis la e zhes pas mkha'
NK020(wa)003:536: 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis po thams cad smug nag
NK020(wa)003:537: rdo rje gshog pa dang dung khrag bsnams pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:539: so dang sgal tshigs dngos po cir mkha' 'gro dbang
NK020(wa)003:540: phyug bsgoms pa'i lo zla mi mthun gnod pa kun
NK020(wa)003:541: bsal nas // bar chad bgegs kyi sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK020(wa)003:544: h+aum zhes pas ma mo bdun /
NK020(wa)003:545: rkang lag gi rgyab sreg ne bzhi la ting zhes
NK020(wa)003:546: pas sring mo bzhi ste thams cad 'jo sgeg mdzes
NK020(wa)003:547: dmar gyi tshul can g.yas 'khyud stabs dang g.yon dung
NK020(wa)003:549: dgra dang bgegs kyi bar chad cing ma bdun sring
NK020(wa)003:550: bzhi bsgoms pa'i tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chad kun
NK020(wa)003:551: bsgral nas // nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad bsrung bar shog /
NK020(wa)003:553: rtsib ma nyer bzhi las na ma tshong bzhi steng
NK020(wa)003:554: dang 'og tu g.yas g.yon gyi rtsib thung re re
NK020(wa)003:555: bor ba'i gur rtsib bco brgyad la ha zhes pas
NK020(wa)003:556: ging bco brgyad po sngo skya gri dang bsgral bya
NK020(wa)003:558: gnod pa'i bsam sbyor ngan pa cir ging chen bco
NK020(wa)003:559: brgyad bsgoms pa'i ki kang gshed gzhi'i gnod pa kun
NK020(wa)003:560: bsal nas // rnam par rtog pa'i bar chad med par shog /
NK020(wa)003:562: rkang lag gi sor tshigs bco lnga phrag bzhi re
NK020(wa)003:563: re la'ang rtsa drug drug la pho nya sum brgya
NK020(wa)003:565: sor tshigs kyi rgyab kyi rtsa tshigs rus dang bcas
NK020(wa)003:566: pa la h+aum hum zhes pas steng gi pho nya
NK020(wa)003:567: khro bo khro mo ya drug cu po thams cad
NK020(wa)003:570: keng rus tshig kyi dngos po cir khro bo khro
NK020(wa)003:571: mo bsgoms pa'i khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun
NK020(wa)003:572: bsgral nas // drag po'i phrin las lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:574: sor tshigs bco lnga phrag bzhi'i g.yas g.yon gyi rtsa
NK020(wa)003:575: bzhi bzhi ste drug cu la phyogs kyi pho nya
NK020(wa)003:577: dzah lag g.yas kyi tshigs kyi rtsa la sku'i pho nya dkar mo lcags kyu thogs pa drug cu /
NK020(wa)003:578: h+aum lag g.yon gyi tshigs kyi rtsa la yon tan
NK020(wa)003:579: gyi pho nya ser mo zhags pa thogs pa drug
NK020(wa)003:581: rkang g.yon gyi tshigs kyi rtsa la gsung gi pho
NK020(wa)003:582: nya dmar mo lcags sgrog thogs pa drug cu hoh
NK020(wa)003:583: rkang g.yas kyi tshigs kyi rtsa la phrin las kyi
NK020(wa)003:584: pho nya nag mo tho ba thogs pa drug cu
NK020(wa)003:586: rtsa dang bcud kyi dngos po cir pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)003:587: dgra dang bgegs kyi bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)003:588: bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:590: mthil phyogs kyi sor tshigs bco lnga phrag bzhi'i rtsa re re la /
NK020(wa)003:591: ma zhes pas las byed kyi pho nya ma mo
NK020(wa)003:592: byu ru'i mdog can gtun shing thogs pa drug cu
NK020(wa)003:594: sha dang khrag gi dngos po cir ma mo drug
NK020(wa)003:595: cu bsgoms pa'i srid gsum gdug pa ma lus kun
NK020(wa)003:596: bsgral nas // phrin las thams cad lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:598: gzhan yang skra rnams dus gsum gyi rig 'dzin bla ma bye ba sa ya'i tshogs dang /
NK020(wa)003:599: ba spu rnams sprul pa dang yang sprul phyag brnyan
NK020(wa)003:600: 'bum phrag mtha' yas pa'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab
NK020(wa)003:601: par snang ba / de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor
NK020(wa)003:602: lo thams cad dwangs pa'i mtsho la gza' skar shar
NK020(wa)003:603: ba ltar ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su bkra lam gyis
NK020(wa)003:604: par snang ba / gsal bar gyur / de nas
NK020(wa)003:605: dbang bskur dang byin rlabs zhi ba ltar byas rjes
NK020(wa)003:606: par snang ba / gsal bar gyur / / spyan 'dren ni /
NK020(wa)003:607: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:609: thugs rje lcags kyu sogs kyi mthar /
NK020(wa)003:610: e h+ye hi sh+r+ai he ru ka a ra li
NK020(wa)003:611: dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya
NK020(wa)003:612: s+t+wam / dzahh+aum bam hoh e a ra li h+r+aim h+r+aim zhes pas spyan drangs la /
NK020(wa)003:613: dzahh+aum bam hosa bstim pa nas bzung /
NK020(wa)003:614: 'dod yon gyi mchod pa'i spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:616: zhes pa'i bar zhi ba ltar las /
NK020(wa)003:617: khyad par gtor mchod kyi rjes su /
NK020(wa)003:618: ma h+aa rak+ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kha his rak+ta phul la /
NK020(wa)003:620: zhen cing chags pa'i dngos po cir khams gsum khrag gi rgya mtsho phul ba'i mthus //
NK020(wa)003:621: dug lnga ma lus rtsa nas dag gyur te //
NK020(wa)003:622: gnyis med mchod pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:623: na mo h+aum zhes pa bcug /
NK020(wa)003:626: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK020(wa)003:627: byams dang snying rjes dgra zun mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)003:628: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'das pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:629: 'jigs byed khro bo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:632: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)003:635: hoh phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK020(wa)003:636: cad kyi bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das che mchog he
NK020(wa)003:637: ru ka la sogs te he ru ka dgu klong
NK020(wa)003:638: 'bar ba / khro bo dang khro mo bsam gyis
NK020(wa)003:639: mi khyab pa thams cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol
NK020(wa)003:640: 'bar ba / / bdag cag rnam 'byor gyi mchod pa dam pa zhes pa nas /
NK020(wa)003:641: 'gro don ma lus lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:645: gzhi lus kyi ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar nyi
NK020(wa)003:646: ma la h+aum yig sngon po bzla bya'i sngags phreng
NK020(wa)003:647: gis bskor ba las zhes bsgyur ba ma gtogs zhi
NK020(wa)003:648: ba ltar las / bzla bya'i sngags spyi 'dzab gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na kho na'am /
NK020(wa)003:649: spro na sgrub thabs rgyas pa ltar khro bo'i bskyed sngags rnams kyi ci 'grub bzlas mthar /
NK020(wa)003:651: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i sogs sngar ltar ro //
NK020(wa)003:652: de ltar zhi khro gang byed kyang rjes chog thun mong ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:653: tshogs kyi yo byad rnams kro d+hi shwa r+ais bsang /
NK020(wa)003:654: ram yam kham gis bsregs gtor bkrus te sbyangs /
NK020(wa)003:655: stong pa'i ngang las tshogs gzhong pad+ma 'bar ba'i snod
NK020(wa)003:656: du tshogs rdzas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi 'dod yon
NK020(wa)003:657: gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa so so'i
NK020(wa)003:658: lha mo'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sprin
NK020(wa)003:659: 'phro ba'i longs spyod kyi gter du gyur par bsam
NK020(wa)003:661: lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK020(wa)003:662: bdag mchod kun mnyes thams cad tshim //
NK020(wa)003:663: kun la phan pa'i sman yin te //
NK020(wa)003:664: rnal 'byor bdag nyid chen po yis //
NK020(wa)003:665: thams cad bza' zhing brgyad par bya //
NK020(wa)003:666: a la la hoh bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK020(wa)003:667: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ldan pa //
NK020(wa)003:668: nam mkha'i sprin ltar gtibs dpungs nas //
NK020(wa)003:670: a la la hoh zhes lus dkyil 'khor lha rnams
NK020(wa)003:671: mchod pa'i don du nang gi sreg blugs kyis tshim
NK020(wa)003:672: par rol la / lhag ma bsdus te cho ga rgyas bsdus ji ltar rigs pas bsngo zhing /
NK020(wa)003:673: brtan ma'i gtor skyong yang byas la /
NK020(wa)003:676: zhes brjod pas rang gi snying ga'i 'od kyis phog
NK020(wa)003:677: pas dag pa'i snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang
NK020(wa)003:678: la thim / de gzhi lus kyi lha yab yum la thim /
NK020(wa)003:680: yab kyi lus dkyil gyi lha rnams kyang gnas de
NK020(wa)003:681: nyid du 'od du zhu nas gzhi lus kyi lha
NK020(wa)003:682: dang bcas pa ye shes sems dpa' la //
NK020(wa)003:683: de ting 'dzin sems dpa' thugs srog gi yi ge la //
NK020(wa)003:684: de yang na da'i bar du rim gyis bsdus nas mi dmigs par gyur pa la mnyam bzhag bya /
NK020(wa)003:685: de'i ngang las chu las nya ldang ba ltar rang nyid zhi ba la kun tu bzang po dang /
NK020(wa)003:686: khro bor he ru ka phyag gnyis pa'i skur langs la /
NK020(wa)003:689: mgrin par +aah snying gar h+aum rnams kyis mtshan par bams la /
NK020(wa)003:690: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK020(wa)003:691: zhes lus rdo rje'i go chas zhu lugs su bcings
NK020(wa)003:692: pas sgo gsum rdo rje gsum dang dbyer mi phyed
NK020(wa)003:693: par bsam zhing bsngo shis kyis mtha' brgyan /
NK020(wa)003:694: snang grags rig gsum lha sngags chos nyid kyi rang
NK020(wa)003:695: bzhin du shes pas spyod lam thams cad don yod
NK020(wa)003:696: par spyod do // da ni zhi thung khro thung
NK020(wa)003:697: gi cho ga 'di la brten nas bsnyen pa byed
NK020(wa)003:698: tshul gyi chings cung zad bstod te /
NK020(wa)003:699: dben par mtshams dam par bcad nas thun bzhi'i rim
NK020(wa)003:700: pas thog mar zhi ba'i bsnyen pa rdzogs par bya
NK020(wa)003:701: / de rjes zhag gcig ngal bso ba'am zhi ba
NK020(wa)003:702: snga dro bsdus pa'i phyi dro'i thun nas brtsams kyang
NK020(wa)003:703: rung steng khro bo'i bsnyen pa la 'jug go //
NK020(wa)003:704: tshul des zhi khro gnyis la rab mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:705: 'bring dus bsnyen zla drug la sogs pa /
NK020(wa)003:706: tha ma grangs bsnyen la rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum las /
NK020(wa)003:708: so so'i sgos 'dzab bzla ba yin pas kun bzang dang che mchog gi sngags chig 'bum re /
NK020(wa)003:709: zhi ba'i rigs lnga dang rgyud lung gi he ru ka dgu la chig khri re /
NK020(wa)003:710: zhi ba'i sems dpa' man chad dang /
NK020(wa)003:711: khro bo'i dbang mo yan chad kyi 'khor sngags rnams lnga stong re /
NK020(wa)003:712: de man chad bka' nyan gyi dkyil 'khor la chig stong re tsam dang /
NK020(wa)003:713: spyi 'dzab gu h+ya ny+dz+aa na zhi khro so sor sum 'bum res mtha' brten pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:715: zhi ba rigs drug dang khro bo he ru ka bcu sngar ltar las /
NK020(wa)003:716: 'khor sngags rnams dor nas spyi 'dzab la 'jug ste grangs bshad ma thag pa bzhin no //
NK020(wa)003:718: spyi 'dzab gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na kho na zhi ba la 'bum phrag gsum mam gcig dang /
NK020(wa)003:719: khro bo la 'bum phrag bzhis mtha' brten pa bzla zhing /
NK020(wa)003:720: de thams cad la 'bum rjes su khri sogs bcu cha'i grangs kyi kha skong ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:721: bcu cha'i sbyin sreg dang bcas pa bya ba yin no //
NK020(wa)003:722: gal te blo nus chung bas khro bo la lus
NK020(wa)003:723: dkyil gyi lha yongs rdzogs bsgom par mi nus pas
NK020(wa)003:724: ni / bka' nyan gyi dkyil 'khor rnams dor nas he ru ka dgu /
NK020(wa)003:727: dbang mo rnams te rtsa dkyil gyi lha tshogs tsam
NK020(wa)003:728: bkod nas bzlas brjod bgyis na'ang chad pa'i skyon med
NK020(wa)003:729: do // yang lung gi zhi khro gnyis dkyus gcig la gyer ba'i tshe //
NK020(wa)003:730: phyi dkyil la 'god na sgrub thabs dngos grub char
NK020(wa)003:731: 'bebs ltar zhi khro steng 'og tu sgom pa yin
NK020(wa)003:732: la / 'dir lus dkyil gyi dbang du byas na /
NK020(wa)003:733: zhi lung gi bzlas pa'i bar song rjes khro dkyil du gnas bsgyur te /
NK020(wa)003:734: e yam sogs rten dang brten pa'i bskyed sngags dang gsal 'debs kyi tshig rnams brjod pas /
NK020(wa)003:735: phyi rin po che'i gzhal yas khang de nyid dur
NK020(wa)003:736: khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang dang gzhu lus kyi
NK020(wa)003:738: lus dkyil gyi rigs lnga rgyud kyi he ru ka lnga /
NK020(wa)003:741: bya byed thub drug dang bcas pa 'bar ma /
NK020(wa)003:742: ta kri ta yab bzhi sgo skyong gdong mo bzhi /
NK020(wa)003:743: yum bzhi gsang yum bzhi rnams su gnas bsgyur zhing /
NK020(wa)003:744: lung gi he ru ka bzhi yum bcas /
NK020(wa)003:750: pho nya sum brgya drug cu rnams sngags brjod pa tsam gyis gsar bskyed du lam gyis bsgom zhing /
NK020(wa)003:751: bskur rlob dbab drangs bstim pa rnams mi dgos pas 'dir mchod bstod dang bzlas pa rnams song rting /
NK020(wa)003:752: rjes chog gi tshogs gtor dang dkyil 'khor bsdu ba rnams byed pa yin no //
NK020(wa)003:753: lung gi zhi khro lus dkyil du sgrub pa'i sgo
NK020(wa)003:754: nas sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa ji ltar bya
NK020(wa)003:755: ba'i cho ga bshad pa'i le tshan no //
NK020(wa)003:758: da ni sgrub khog tu sgrub zhag du byed kyi chog khrigs rgyas pa'i skabs las /
NK020(wa)003:759: spro zhing nus na bzlas pa'i dus zhi ba la 'dzab bskul dang rjes kyi bstod pa /
NK020(wa)003:760: khro bo la gnas sgyur gyi bstod pa rnams zur
NK020(wa)003:761: 'debs ltar sbyar bar bya zhes kha 'phangs pa ni
NK020(wa)003:762: 'di yin te / de la thog mar 'dzab khang dbye ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:763: 'dzab dgongs kyi spro bsdu'i dmigs pa sgrub thabs ltar gsal btab nas /
NK020(wa)003:766: dang po zhi ba la yang /
NK020(wa)003:769: bstod pa 'bul ba ste gsum gsum du shes par bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:771: rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:772: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni /
NK020(wa)003:773: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK020(wa)003:775: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs na //
NK020(wa)003:776: rin chen nyi zla pad gdan la //
NK020(wa)003:777: e ma kun bzang rdo rje nyid //
NK020(wa)003:778: rig pa'i tshul snang sangs rgyas pa //
NK020(wa)003:779: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK020(wa)003:781: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK020(wa)003:782: dang po byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK020(wa)003:783: bar pa rdo rje dril bu 'dzin //
NK020(wa)003:784: tha ma mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK020(wa)003:785: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba /
NK020(wa)003:786: phyi yi yul la sangs rgyas pa //
NK020(wa)003:787: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK020(wa)003:788: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i yum //
NK020(wa)003:789: bya ba mo dang gnyis su med //
NK020(wa)003:790: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK020(wa)003:791: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:792: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:794: yid chos rang rig ma skyes sems //
NK020(wa)003:795: kun bzang yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:796: ting 'dzin byed por dbang bskur nas //
NK020(wa)003:797: ma lus kun gyi byed por shog /
NK020(wa)003:800: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK020(wa)003:803: byang chub sems mchog ye shes rdo rje thugs //
NK020(wa)003:804: srid gsum dbang sdud thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK020(wa)003:805: snyel ba mi mnga' 'gro ba'i skyabs mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:806: kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:808: gdon nas ma byung ma skyes chos kyi dbyings //
NK020(wa)003:809: mi skye mi 'gag dngos por 'dzin dang bral //
NK020(wa)003:810: 'byung byed thams cad bskyed pa yum gyi tshul //
NK020(wa)003:811: bzang mo bya ba mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:813: de bzhin du rigs 'gre shes par byas te /
NK020(wa)003:815: rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:816: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK020(wa)003:817: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK020(wa)003:818: 'khor lo'i lte bar gtso bo'i mdun //
NK020(wa)003:819: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs na //
NK020(wa)003:820: rin chen nyi zla pad gdan la //
NK020(wa)003:821: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' gtso //
NK020(wa)003:824: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK020(wa)003:825: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen g.yas //
NK020(wa)003:826: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK020(wa)003:827: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK020(wa)003:828: kun tu bzang dang gnyis su med //
NK020(wa)003:829: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK020(wa)003:830: yid dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:831: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:833: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK020(wa)003:834: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK020(wa)003:835: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:836: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang sgyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:837: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:840: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK020(wa)003:841: gzugs sku stong pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:842: yon tan ye shes lnga don thugs chud pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:843: rgyal mchog mi bskyod pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:844: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa las //
NK020(wa)003:845: rdo rje dbyings phyug yum mchod tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:846: yon tan rnam rtog mi mnga' cha 'dzin ma //
NK020(wa)003:847: rgyal yum kun tu bzang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:849: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du //
NK020(wa)003:850: glang chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs na //
NK020(wa)003:851: rin chen nyi zla pad gdan la //
NK020(wa)003:852: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad gtso //
NK020(wa)003:855: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus dkar zhal //
NK020(wa)003:856: 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen g.yas //
NK020(wa)003:857: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK020(wa)003:858: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK020(wa)003:859: sangs rgyas spyan dang gnyis su med //
NK020(wa)003:860: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK020(wa)003:861: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:862: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:863: gzugs phung sa yi ngo bo nyid //
NK020(wa)003:864: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK020(wa)003:865: snang mdzad yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:866: ting 'dzin sku ru dbang sgyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:867: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:870: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin gzugs sku me long lta bu'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:871: yon tan chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:872: rgyal mchog rnam snang mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:873: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa las //
NK020(wa)003:874: de bzhin dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:875: yon tan yod med stong pa'i cha 'dzin ma //
NK020(wa)003:876: rgyal yum sangs rgyas spyan la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:878: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du //
NK020(wa)003:879: rta mchog bsnol ba'i khri stengs na //
NK020(wa)003:880: rin chen nyi zla pad gdan la //
NK020(wa)003:881: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan gtso //
NK020(wa)003:884: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal //
NK020(wa)003:885: rin chen rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK020(wa)003:886: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK020(wa)003:887: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK020(wa)003:888: m+aa ma k+ai dang gnyis su med //
NK020(wa)003:889: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK020(wa)003:890: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:891: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:892: tshor ba chu yi ngo bo nyid //
NK020(wa)003:893: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK020(wa)003:894: 'byung ldan yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:895: ting 'dzin yon tan dbang sgyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:896: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:897: s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika m+aam mo ha ra ti //
NK020(wa)003:898: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK020(wa)003:899: gzugs sku mnyam pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:900: yon tan yid bzhin re ba skong mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:901: rgyal mchog rin chen 'byung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:902: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa las //
NK020(wa)003:903: rin chen dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:904: yon tan nga dang bdag med cha 'dzin ma //
NK020(wa)003:905: rgyal yum m+aa ma k+ai la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:907: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du //
NK020(wa)003:908: rma bya bsnol ba'i khri stengs na //
NK020(wa)003:909: rin chen nyi zla pad gdan la //
NK020(wa)003:910: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas gtso //
NK020(wa)003:913: g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus dmar zhal //
NK020(wa)003:915: dril bu rin chen ral gri g.yon //
NK020(wa)003:916: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK020(wa)003:917: gos dkar mo dang gnyis su med //
NK020(wa)003:918: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK020(wa)003:919: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:920: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:921: 'du shes me yi ngo bo nyid //
NK020(wa)003:922: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK020(wa)003:923: mtha' yas yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:924: ting 'dzin gsum du dbang sgyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:925: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:928: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK020(wa)003:929: gzugs sku so sor rtog pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:930: yon tan mtha' gnyis skyon gyis ma gos pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:931: rgyal mchog snang mtha' yas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:932: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa las //
NK020(wa)003:933: pad+ma dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:934: yon tan spyi dang rang gis cha 'dzin ma //
NK020(wa)003:935: rgyal yum gos dkar mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:937: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du //
NK020(wa)003:938: shang shang bsnol ba'i khri stengs na //
NK020(wa)003:939: rin chen nyi zla pad gdan la //
NK020(wa)003:940: bcom ldan don yod grub pa gtso //
NK020(wa)003:943: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NK020(wa)003:944: ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK020(wa)003:945: dril bu rin chen pad+ma g.yon //
NK020(wa)003:946: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK020(wa)003:947: dam tshig sgrol dang gnyis su med //
NK020(wa)003:948: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK020(wa)003:949: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:950: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:951: 'du byed rlung gi ngo bo nyid //
NK020(wa)003:952: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK020(wa)003:953: don grub yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:954: ting 'dzin las su dbang sgyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:955: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:956: h+aam pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika t+aam badz+ra ra ti //
NK020(wa)003:957: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK020(wa)003:958: gzugs sku bya ba grub pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:959: yon tan phrin las sna tshogs don mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:960: rgyal mchog don yod grub la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:961: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa las //
NK020(wa)003:962: las kyi dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)003:963: yon tan bdag gzhan don grub cha 'dzin ma //
NK020(wa)003:964: rgyal yum dam tshig sgrol mar phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:966: shar lho 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK020(wa)003:967: nyi zla pad+ma gdan steng na //
NK020(wa)003:968: byang sems sa yi snying po dang //
NK020(wa)003:969: yum chen lha mo l+aa s+ya gnyis //
NK020(wa)003:970: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:971: las nyon bag chags sbyang du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:972: mig gzugs sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK020(wa)003:973: sa snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:974: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang sgyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:975: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:977: h+aum l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)003:979: me long ye shes khyad par las //
NK020(wa)003:980: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:981: che ba'i yon tan bskyed mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:982: sa yi snying por phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:983: gnyis med dbyings kyi khyad par las //
NK020(wa)003:984: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:985: rnam rtog zil gyis gnon mdzad ma //
NK020(wa)003:986: l+aa s+ya ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:988: lho nub 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK020(wa)003:989: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng na //
NK020(wa)003:990: byang sems nam mkha'i snying po dang //
NK020(wa)003:991: yum chen lha mo m+aa l+ye gnyis //
NK020(wa)003:992: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:993: las nyon bag chags sbyang du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:994: sna dri sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK020(wa)003:995: nam snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:996: ting 'dzin sems dpa' dbang sgyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:997: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:999: tram m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hoh mnyam nyid ye shes khyad par las //
NK020(wa)003:1000: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1001: rnam rtog d+r+wa ba gcod mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1002: nam mkha'i snying por phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1003: gnyis med dbyings kyi khyad par las //
NK020(wa)003:1004: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1005: 'khor ba zil gyis gnon mdzad ma //
NK020(wa)003:1006: m+aa l+ye ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1008: nub byang 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK020(wa)003:1009: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1010: byang sems spyan ras gzigs dbang dang //
NK020(wa)003:1011: yum chen lha mo g+ai ti gnyis //
NK020(wa)003:1012: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK020(wa)003:1013: las nyon bag chags sbyang du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:1014: lce ro sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK020(wa)003:1015: spyan gzigs yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:1016: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang sgyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:1017: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:1018: h+r+ai h+aa h+aum pad+ma bra da ma /
NK020(wa)003:1019: h+r+ai g+ai ti r+aa ga ham /
NK020(wa)003:1020: sor rtog ye shes khyad par las //
NK020(wa)003:1021: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1022: mtha' yi dri mas ma gos pa //
NK020(wa)003:1023: spyan ras gzigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1024: gnyis med dbyings kyi khyad par las //

NK020(wa)003:1154: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:1155: 'thab rtsod sdug bsngal sbyang du gsol //

NK020(wa)003:1161: mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma g.yos kyang //

NK020(wa)003:1163: thugs rjes khong khro'i sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1164: bcom ldan lha min thub par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1166: gzhal yas snam bu'i lhor phyogs na //
NK020(wa)003:1167: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NK020(wa)003:1168: bcom ldan sh+aaka thub gseg par bsnams //

NK020(wa)003:1170: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //

NK020(wa)003:1206: ting 'dzin thub par dbang sgyur nas //

NK020(wa)003:1242: me long lta bu'i ye shes byin rlabs las //

NK020(wa)003:1244: thabs kyis lha yi bu yi bdud 'joms pa //
NK020(wa)003:1245: khro rgyal gshin rje'i gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1246: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK020(wa)003:1247: 'gro ba 'dul phyir khro mo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1248: thabs kyis 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1249: rdo rje lcags kyu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1251: gzhal yas khang gi lho sgo ru //
NK020(wa)003:1252: rdo rje brag chen nyi gdan steng //
NK020(wa)003:1253: 'joms byed khro rgyal stobs po che //
NK020(wa)003:1254: 'ching ba'i lha mo zhags pa ma //
NK020(wa)003:1255: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:1256: gshin rje'i gdon rnams 'dul du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:1257: reg bya chad par ma skyes sems //
NK020(wa)003:1258: stobs chen yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:1260: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:1261: h+aum pra dz+ny+aan+ta kri ta phata /
NK020(wa)003:1262: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:1263: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK020(wa)003:1264: gshin rje 'dul phyir khro bo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1265: thabs kyis 'chi bdag bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1266: khro rgyal stobs po che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1267: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK020(wa)003:1268: 'gro ba 'dul phyir khro mo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1269: thabs kyis bla med gnas su 'dren mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1270: rdo rje zhags pa ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1272: gzhal yas khang gi nub sgo ru //
NK020(wa)003:1273: rdo rje brag chen nyi gdan steng //
NK020(wa)003:1274: 'joms byed khro rgyal rta mgrin dang //
NK020(wa)003:1275: sdom byed lha mo lcags sgrog ma //
NK020(wa)003:1276: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:1277: klu yi gdon rnams 'dul du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:1278: reg byed bdag 'dzin ma skyes sems //
NK020(wa)003:1279: rta mgrin yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:1281: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:1282: h+aum pad+ma n+ta kri ta phata /
NK020(wa)003:1283: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:1284: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK020(wa)003:1285: klu chen 'dul phyir khro bo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1286: thabs kyi phung po'i bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1287: khro rgyal rta mchog dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1288: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK020(wa)003:1289: 'gro ba 'dul phyir khro mo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1290: thabs kyis nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1291: nyi zla lcags sgrog ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1293: gzhal yas khang gi byang sgo ru //
NK020(wa)003:1294: rdo rje brag chen nyi gdan steng //
NK020(wa)003:1296: 'bebs byed lha mo dril bu ma //
NK020(wa)003:1297: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:1298: gnod sbyin gdon rnams 'dul du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:1300: bdud rtsi yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK020(wa)003:1302: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:1304: karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:1305: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK020(wa)003:1306: gnod sbyin 'dul phyir khro bo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1307: thabs kyis nyon mongs bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1308: khro rgyal bdud rtsi 'khyil la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1309: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK020(wa)003:1310: 'gro ba 'dul phyir khro bo'i skur ston cing //
NK020(wa)003:1311: thabs kyis 'gro ba ma lus don mdzad ma //
NK020(wa)003:1312: rdo rje dril bu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1314: gnas sgyur gyi bstod pa gsal gdab pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1315: 'dzab bzla ba gnyis su shes par bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:1317: ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1318: rgyal ba khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK020(wa)003:1319: che ba'i nang nas che mchog bla na med //
NK020(wa)003:1320: che btsan 'gran zla bral ba kun gyi mchog /
NK020(wa)003:1321: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:1322: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1323: 'khor lo 'bar ba'i dbus kyi lte ba ru //
NK020(wa)003:1324: bcom ldan dpal chen che mchog he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:1325: 'bar ba'i dbu ni nyi shu rtsa gcig gis //
NK020(wa)003:1326: sa ni nyi shu rtsa gcig rim pas mnan //
NK020(wa)003:1327: g.yas g.yon phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis na //
NK020(wa)003:1328: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs //
NK020(wa)003:1329: zhabs brgyad bgrad pas khro mo'i dbu brgyad bardzisa //
NK020(wa)003:1330: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer sku la brjid //
NK020(wa)003:1331: dpal gyi chas brgyad dur khrod rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK020(wa)003:1332: che mchog he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1333: kun tu bzang mo chos nyid gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1334: dpal 'bar khro mo kun gyi rje btsan yum //
NK020(wa)003:1335: shes rab dbyings nas sku bskyed thugs rjer ldan //
NK020(wa)003:1336: khro mo gnam zhal ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1338: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1339: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:1341: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1344: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:1346: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:1347: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK020(wa)003:1348: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbu //
NK020(wa)003:1349: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK020(wa)003:1350: dbu gsum bar du rngams pa ni //
NK020(wa)003:1351: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK020(wa)003:1352: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK020(wa)003:1353: srid gsum dbyings su sgrol pa'i zhal //
NK020(wa)003:1354: dbu gsum tha mar rngams pa ni //
NK020(wa)003:1355: g.yas g.yon dbus gsum mthing ga'i zhal //
NK020(wa)003:1356: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu /
NK020(wa)003:1357: khams gsum re ba skong ba'i zhal //
NK020(wa)003:1358: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol pa ni //
NK020(wa)003:1359: stong pa bco brgyad dbyings su thim //
NK020(wa)003:1360: bco brgyad phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK020(wa)003:1361: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK020(wa)003:1362: b+hany+dza zhing chung ti ra g.yon //
NK020(wa)003:1363: zhing zhags nyi ma khung chen g.yas //
NK020(wa)003:1364: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK020(wa)003:1365: me dang rgya mtsho ga'u g.yas //
NK020(wa)003:1366: klu dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK020(wa)003:1367: yon tan bco brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK020(wa)003:1368: khro rgyal rgyan rnams sku la brjid //
NK020(wa)003:1369: kro d+h+ai mthing nag 'khril pa'i tshul //
NK020(wa)003:1370: rdo rje dung dmar yab la stob /
NK020(wa)003:1371: khro rgyal dpal chen he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:1372: dbang mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1373: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1374: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1375: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1376: dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK020(wa)003:1377: rdo rje mi bskyod gnas gyur pa /
NK020(wa)003:1380: mchod cing byin rlabs gsal sgrub pa //
NK020(wa)003:1381: badz+ra he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1382: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1383: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal ba //
NK020(wa)003:1384: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK020(wa)003:1385: badz+ra kro d+he shwa r+air bstod /
NK020(wa)003:1386: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1387: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK020(wa)003:1389: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK020(wa)003:1391: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1392: dri za bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK020(wa)003:1393: rnam par snang mdzad gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1396: mchod cing sgrub ste byin rlabs pa //
NK020(wa)003:1397: bud+d+ha he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1398: sangs rgyas spyan ma gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1399: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal ba //
NK020(wa)003:1400: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK020(wa)003:1401: spyan drangs mchod cing sgrub pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:1402: bud+d+ha kro d+he shwa r+air bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1403: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1404: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1406: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1407: gshin rje bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK020(wa)003:1408: rin chen 'byung ldan gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1411: spyan drangs mchod cing sgrubs pa'i lha //
NK020(wa)003:1412: rat+na he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1413: m+aa ma k+ai las gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1414: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur byung ba //
NK020(wa)003:1415: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK020(wa)003:1416: spyan drangs mchod cing sgrub pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:1417: rat+na kro d+he shwa r+air bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1418: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1419: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1421: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1422: klu dbang bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK020(wa)003:1423: snang ba mtha' yas gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1425: 'jigs byed dmar nag ral pa can //
NK020(wa)003:1426: bsgoms shing mchod de sgrubs pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:1427: pad+ma he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1428: na bza' dkar mo gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1429: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur byung ba //
NK020(wa)003:1430: thabs shes byang chub sems sgrub pa //
NK020(wa)003:1431: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa rir bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1432: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1433: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1435: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1436: gnod sbyin bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK020(wa)003:1437: don yod grub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1440: gsal bar bskyed cing mchod sgrub pa //
NK020(wa)003:1441: karma he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1442: dam tshig sgrom lasama gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1443: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur ston pa //
NK020(wa)003:1444: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK020(wa)003:1445: lhag ma byang chub sems 'phros pa //
NK020(wa)003:1446: karma kro d+h+ai shwa r+air bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1447: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1448: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1450: shar lho 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1451: mthu stobs mnga' bdag gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1452: sgrol byed chen po bdud rnams 'joms //
NK020(wa)003:1453: bdud dang srin po sgrol la brtson //
NK020(wa)003:1454: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK020(wa)003:1455: rak+sha he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1456: lha mo ral gcig gnas gyur pa /
NK020(wa)003:1457: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK020(wa)003:1458: yab yum thabs dang shes rab sbyor //
NK020(wa)003:1459: rak+sha kro d+he shwa r+air bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1460: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka rak+sha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1461: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1463: lho nub 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1464: mkhyen rab bdag po gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1466: ser nag mdog can 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK020(wa)003:1467: gang sgrub mthu dang dbang stsol ba'i //
NK020(wa)003:1468: sa nu he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1469: 'jigs rten bdag mo gnas gyur pa /
NK020(wa)003:1470: khro mo dbang phyug kun gyi rje //
NK020(wa)003:1471: sprul pa yang sprul kun gyi ma //
NK020(wa)003:1472: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa //
NK020(wa)003:1473: sa nu kro d+he shwa r+air bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1474: sa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka sa nu kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1475: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1477: nub byang 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1478: thugs rje'i bdag po gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1479: gsang ba'i don la mnga' mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1480: dmar nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK020(wa)003:1481: dus rnam rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK020(wa)003:1482: zhe sdang 'khor ba sgrol la brtson //
NK020(wa)003:1483: gu h+ya he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1484: gsung gi bdag mo gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:1485: khro mo chen mo gsang ba'i lha //
NK020(wa)003:1486: gsang ba'i don la bskul byed ma //
NK020(wa)003:1487: gu h+ya kro d+h+ai shwa r+air bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1488: gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka gu h+ya kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1489: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1491: byang shar 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK020(wa)003:1493: dpal chen dam tshig mnga' mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1494: ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK020(wa)003:1495: bskal pa brgyar yang dam tshig lha //
NK020(wa)003:1496: yak+sha he ru ka la bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1497: yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka yak+sha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1498: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK020(wa)003:1500: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1501: 'bar ba'i glo 'bur bzhi dang gru chad bzhir //
NK020(wa)003:1502: goo r+ai la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni //
NK020(wa)003:1503: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK020(wa)003:1504: sku mdog phyag mtshan sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK020(wa)003:1505: ye shes khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1507: de bzhin goo r+ai gnas su /
NK020(wa)003:1514: tsan+da l+ai rnams bcug pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1517: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1518: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dang po gser mdog na //
NK020(wa)003:1519: seng gdong ma sogs phra men brgyad rnams ni //
NK020(wa)003:1520: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma //
NK020(wa)003:1521: rnam 'phrul las kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1522: phra men yul ma brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1531: u l+au ka rnams bcug pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1533: khyams de'i shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ru //
NK020(wa)003:1534: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1535: rta gdong phag gdong sprel gdong sbyang gdong bzhi //
NK020(wa)003:1536: zhi rgyas dbang drag las la thogs med brtson //
NK020(wa)003:1537: rtag chad bdag 'dzin mtshan mar lta las grol //
NK020(wa)003:1538: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah badz+ra sngon 'gros /
NK020(wa)003:1541: b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hohrnamasa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1543: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1544: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis pa dkar po na //
NK020(wa)003:1545: chos nyid rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK020(wa)003:1546: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur pa'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK020(wa)003:1547: srid gsum zhing du sbyor bas g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK020(wa)003:1548: spor ma chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal badz+ra a
NK020(wa)003:1549: pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra
NK020(wa)003:1550: phata rak+mo h+aum / ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK020(wa)003:1551: bar khyams de yi shar lho nub byang sgor //
NK020(wa)003:1552: dgyes pa bskyed pa'i gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK020(wa)003:1553: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK020(wa)003:1554: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag sh+r+ai badz+ra mut+ga
NK020(wa)003:1555: ra mu kha shwa ra y+aa ya na mah sh+r+ai
NK020(wa)003:1556: badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa ra y+aa ya na mah
NK020(wa)003:1557: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ka pra dz+wa la y+aa ya
NK020(wa)003:1558: na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la y+aa ya
NK020(wa)003:1559: na mah zhes pa rnams dang ru lu spel //
NK020(wa)003:1561: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1562: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gsum pa dmar po na //
NK020(wa)003:1563: mi srin la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK020(wa)003:1564: dregs pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK020(wa)003:1565: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK020(wa)003:1566: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad la phyag ma nu rak+sha s+ai /
NK020(wa)003:1584: ma h+aa m+aa ra na badz+ra /
NK020(wa)003:1594: de thams cad kyi mjug tu b+h+yo re btags shing /
NK020(wa)003:1597: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1598: 'bar ba'i bar khyams bzhi pa gser mdog na //
NK020(wa)003:1599: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK020(wa)003:1600: 'dod dgur sgyur pa'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK020(wa)003:1601: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK020(wa)003:1602: mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis la phyag e +aa ra li h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1603: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK020(wa)003:1605: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1606: 'bar ba'i bar khyams lnga pa dmar po na //
NK020(wa)003:1607: 'jigs rten dregs pa 'dul ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)003:1608: phyi 'khor 'dul zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1609: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK020(wa)003:1610: bgegs srung ma sring tshogs la phyag ma ma d+h+aa tu h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1612: ru lu dang spel la bzla //
NK020(wa)003:1613: h+aum tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1614: 'bar ba'i bar khyams drug pa dkar po na //
NK020(wa)003:1615: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad ni /
NK020(wa)003:1616: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK020(wa)003:1617: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas brlag par byed //
NK020(wa)003:1618: ging chen ging lcam tshogs la phyag king+ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1619: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK020(wa)003:1620: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK020(wa)003:1621: 'bar ba'i bar khyams bdun pa nag po na //
NK020(wa)003:1622: bcom ldan h+aum mdzad sa gsum brjid kyis gnon //
NK020(wa)003:1623: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha yi lha //
NK020(wa)003:1624: 'jigs byed 'bar ba gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK020(wa)003:1625: khro bo khro mo rnams la phyag kro d+ha kro d+h+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1627: tshogs chen 'dus pa 'bar ba'i bar khyams brgyad pa phyogs mdog na //
NK020(wa)003:1628: ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:1629: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i las la thogs pa med //
NK020(wa)003:1630: ci bgyi bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:1631: phyogs bzhi'i pho nya'i tshogs la b+ha na b+ha na
NK020(wa)003:1632: am ku sha dzah ha la ha la p+aa sha
NK020(wa)003:1633: h+aum / gardza gardza s+pho ta bam /
NK020(wa)003:1634: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh zhes dang ru lu spel ba bzla //
NK020(wa)003:1636: tshogs chen 'dus pa 'bar ba'i bar khyams dgu pa ljang khu na //
NK020(wa)003:1637: stong khams yongs kyi las la dbang byed pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:1638: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag yum chen las la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK020(wa)003:1639: ma mo drug cu'i tshogs la ma me shwa ra h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1641: gsum pa rig 'dzin la'ang bstod bzlas gnyis te /
NK020(wa)003:1643: gzhal yas khang chen phyi rol khor yug na //
NK020(wa)003:1644: rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)003:1645: rnal 'byor lnga yi sa la legs bzhugs pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:1646: rtsa brgyud bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:1647: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dngos grub 'dir stsol cig /
NK020(wa)003:1648: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:1650: zhi khro'i 'dzab rgyas pa'i zur 'debs le tshan no //
NK020(wa)003:1654: che mchog zhal byang gi cho gas rtsa dkyil gyi
NK020(wa)003:1655: snying po bdud rtsi bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)003:1656: du zhal bsgyur ba tsam las /
NK020(wa)003:1657: cho ga'i spros pa gzhan rnams 'dir mi dgos kyang /
NK020(wa)003:1658: yig rgyun mi nub pa'i phyir lugs de'i chog khrigs
NK020(wa)003:1659: kyang zur 'debs su 'bri bar bya zhes kha 'phang
NK020(wa)003:1661: de la spyir rtsa rgyud kyi le'u nyi shu rtsa brgyad par /
NK020(wa)003:1662: bdud rtsi rang byung gi sgrub pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1669: rlon sbyor du sgrub pa dang brgyad gsungs pa las /
NK020(wa)003:1671: phye ma gnyis kyi cho ga'i khog cung zad bshad pa la gnyis kyi /
NK020(wa)003:1672: dang po khrol bu'i tho byang ni /
NK020(wa)003:1676: skyobs dang 'phrad du gyur pa'i la sman bod sman
NK020(wa)003:1677: sogs thams cad 'tshol ba dang bsrel ba la mkhas
NK020(wa)003:1678: pa'i sgo nas tshang bar 'du byas la /
NK020(wa)003:1679: dkyil 'khor ni he ru ka 'dus par dbus ling tshe dang /
NK020(wa)003:1680: rngams glog tu pad 'dab brgyad par bshad kyang /
NK020(wa)003:1681: rtsa rgyud ltar 'dir sgo bzhi rta babs can khyams
NK020(wa)003:1682: gru chad glo 'bur dang bcas pa'i nang du pad+ma
NK020(wa)003:1683: dmar po 'dab bzhi'i lte bar zla ga ma logs
NK020(wa)003:1684: mdun bstan dang / 'dab bzhir logs nang bstan re /
NK020(wa)003:1685: phyi'i khor yug pad rdor me'i ra bas bskor ba bris la /
NK020(wa)003:1686: de'i steng du sman snod ni /
NK020(wa)003:1687: dbus su thod pa srubs med tshangs skud can /
NK020(wa)003:1688: shar du dkar zlum sul 'greng mdzod spu can /
NK020(wa)003:1689: lhor dum gsum shing lo rgyas pa /
NK020(wa)003:1690: nub tu dum gnyis smin mtshams gnyis na 'bur yod pa //
NK020(wa)003:1691: byang du dum bzhi srubs rgya gram can rnams bkod /
NK020(wa)003:1692: de dag gi nang du sman ni /
NK020(wa)003:1714: ri dwags sna tshogs kyi sha /
NK020(wa)003:1718: sman gzhan rnams rigs lnga'i phyag rgya'i dbyibs dang /
NK020(wa)003:1720: ro nus sogs so so'i las kyis phye nas snod lngar bkod cing /
NK020(wa)003:1721: mtshams bzhir yang thod pa'am snod ji ltar rigs par shar lho nas rim bzhin 'o ma dang /
NK020(wa)003:1725: de rnams kyi steng nas dar g.yogs shing tshon skud
NK020(wa)003:1726: rgya gram du btab pa'i sne nas gzungs thag 'dren
NK020(wa)003:1728: de nas sman sbyang ba'i dgongs rgyun ni /
NK020(wa)003:1730: dam pa de nyid gsang chen gyi //
NK020(wa)003:1731: rigs brgya rigs lnga rigs gcig gis //
NK020(wa)003:1732: thams cad sbyang ba'i mchog tu bya //
NK020(wa)003:1734: dam pa rigs brgyas sbyong ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:1735: mtshams gcod sogs sngon du 'gro bas //
NK020(wa)003:1738: dkyil 'khor gzhal yas gdan dang bcas //
NK020(wa)003:1739: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor yab yum gnyis //
NK020(wa)003:1740: bskyed cing byin rlabs dbang bskur bya //
NK020(wa)003:1741: gnyis med gsal bstim mchod byas te //
NK020(wa)003:1742: byin rlabs sman gyi lha mo sbran //
NK020(wa)003:1743: bar chad bsal ba rgyun du bya //
NK020(wa)003:1746: bdag dang mdun gyi sman dkyil dbyer med du bsgoms
NK020(wa)003:1747: te dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med rtsa ba byang
NK020(wa)003:1748: chub kyi sems nyid bskyed sngags kyis sad pa las
NK020(wa)003:1749: // rten gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid rdzogs pa'i nang du //
NK020(wa)003:1750: brten pa lha dbus dang 'dab bzhir rigs lnga //
NK020(wa)003:1751: glo 'bur dang gru chad la sems dpa' //
NK020(wa)003:1752: sgor mthar byed rnams yum bcas dang //
NK020(wa)003:1753: khyams kyi phyogs mtshams su bya byed dang thub drug
NK020(wa)003:1754: ste bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bkra
NK020(wa)003:1755: lam gyis gsal bar bskyed la /
NK020(wa)003:1756: bskur rlob dbab drangs bstim brtan mchod cing bstod nas /
NK020(wa)003:1758: khrus bya ba ni sman gyi srung ma rnams dga' bar byas nas rtog pa gzhom pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:1759: zhes pas sman srung spyan drangs la rtog bsal byas rjes 'dzab khang phye nas /
NK020(wa)003:1760: bdag bskyed kyi thugs ka'i 'od kyis thugs rgyud bskul
NK020(wa)003:1761: bas mdun bskyed la spro bsdu'i dmigs pa sbyar te
NK020(wa)003:1762: / zhi 'dzab bo d+hi tsit+ta brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas /
NK020(wa)003:1763: de nas h+aum zhes brjod pas bdag mdun gyi thub pa drug kun bzang la bsdu /
NK020(wa)003:1764: kun bzang yab yum mi bskyod pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1765: mthar byed bzhi rang rang gi yum la bsdus te /
NK020(wa)003:1766: khro bo'i rten brten pa'i bskyed sngags brjod pa tsam gyis //
NK020(wa)003:1767: rten 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang khyams nyis rim can dang /
NK020(wa)003:1768: brten pa zhi ba'i lha tshogs khro bo ngo mtshar tshogs kyi lha sum cur bsgyur zhing /
NK020(wa)003:1769: khyams phyi mar dbang mo rnams krong bskyed byas la /
NK020(wa)003:1771: bdag mdun spro bsdu sngar ltar sbyar te /
NK020(wa)003:1772: khro mdzab ru lu'i bzlas pa brgya rtsa brgyad bazla'o //
NK020(wa)003:1773: de nas bdag bskyed kyi thugs ka nas sngags kyi
NK020(wa)003:1774: 'od zer gzungs thag la 'khril te song bas lha
NK020(wa)003:1776: de dag gi sku las 'phros pa'i 'od zer dang /
NK020(wa)003:1777: sman srung rnams kyis kyang brtan g.yo 'khor 'das kyi
NK020(wa)003:1778: rtsi bcud thams cad bsdus pa byang sems bdud rtsi'i
NK020(wa)003:1779: chu rgyun du zhu ba bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor la
NK020(wa)003:1782: khrol bu spyi sbyang ba'i snying po /
NK020(wa)003:1783: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta ra sa ya na ta na dza ya gu h+ya sid+d+hi h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK020(wa)003:1784: zhes stong tshang bar bzlas la mchod cing /
NK020(wa)003:1786: 'khor rnams 'od du zhu nas rigs lnga la thim /
NK020(wa)003:1787: rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyis bde ba chen
NK020(wa)003:1788: po'i ngo bor zhu ba dam rdzas dang ro gcig
NK020(wa)003:1790: de nas de nyid rigs lngas 'ju 'dul bya ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:1791: sman rnams phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga'i snod du bsdus te /
NK020(wa)003:1792: dbyings ye gnyis med las rten gzhal yas khang gi
NK020(wa)003:1793: dbus su snod ka p+aa la lnga'i nang du pad
NK020(wa)003:1794: zla nyi ma la gnas pa'i dam rdzas bdud rtsi
NK020(wa)003:1795: lnga po dpa' bo 'bru lngar gyur pa spro bsdus
NK020(wa)003:1796: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga yab yum gyi skur
NK020(wa)003:1797: bkra lam gyis gsal bar mos la /
NK020(wa)003:1798: dbang bskur nas rtog bsal gyi bar dang /
NK020(wa)003:1799: 'dzab khang phye ste spro bsdu sngar ltar sbyar la /
NK020(wa)003:1800: rigs lnga'i 'dzab brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas rjes /
NK020(wa)003:1801: bdag gi thugs ka'i 'od kyis bskul bas mdun bskyed
NK020(wa)003:1802: kyi rigs lnga yab yum gnyam par sbyor ba'i bde
NK020(wa)003:1803: ba'i sgra dang 'od zer gyis don gnyis byas /
NK020(wa)003:1804: ye shes lnga'i bcud bsdus pa yab yum gyi sbyor
NK020(wa)003:1805: mtshams nas babs te ye shes kyi bdud rtsi mu
NK020(wa)003:1806: tig dkar po dri ma med pa ltar 'khyil bar
NK020(wa)003:1807: mos la / +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa dz+ny+aa na pany+tsa s+pha ra na phata /
NK020(wa)003:1810: rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyis sogs bsdu ba sngar bzhin no //
NK020(wa)003:1811: de nas gsang chen rigs gcig ni /
NK020(wa)003:1812: sman thams cad snod gcig tu bsdus te /
NK020(wa)003:1813: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med las h+aum zhes brjod
NK020(wa)003:1814: pas rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum du bsgoms la
NK020(wa)003:1815: / dbang nas rtog bsal bar dang /
NK020(wa)003:1817: rdor sems yab yum gyi sngags brgya rtsa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1818: dmigs pa'i 'phro 'du sngar lta bus sman 'dzab /
NK020(wa)003:1819: +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra tsit+ta sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:1820: zhes stong bzlas la lha sngar ltar bsdu'o //
NK020(wa)003:1821: de ltar khrol sgrub ni mdo dbang dang sbrel ba'i
NK020(wa)003:1822: sman sgrub la mi mdzad pa shas che bas 'dir
NK020(wa)003:1823: tho byang tsam las ma smos te /
NK020(wa)003:1824: bya bar spro na rdzas bsag cing bsham pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1825: mjug don sogs cho ga'i rim pa rnams zhi ba
NK020(wa)003:1826: par gsang chen myur lam lta bus khog phub nas
NK020(wa)003:1828: gnyis pa phye ma la bzhi ste /
NK020(wa)003:1829: btag btsag bsre spol gyi dgongs pa /
NK020(wa)003:1830: yum gyis glu blangs te sbyong ba /
NK020(wa)003:1832: phye ma sgrub pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:1836: snod kyi sman rnams shes rab mas //
NK020(wa)003:1837: bsdus te 'thag pa'i cho ga yang //
NK020(wa)003:1838: yum gyis bzung zhing yab kyis 'thag /
NK020(wa)003:1839: rig 'dzin rtsal can dbab cing drang /
NK020(wa)003:1840: so so las kyi sngags brjod cing //
NK020(wa)003:1841: gtan gtun thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK020(wa)003:1842: sman nyid byang chub sems su sbyar //
NK020(wa)003:1844: yum mam der btags pa'i slob mas snod kyis sman rnams bsdus te bsar la /
NK020(wa)003:1845: thog mar rig 'dzin rnams dbab ste /
NK020(wa)003:1846: dpon slob thams cad dpal chen po'i nga rgyal gyis ru lu'i 'dzab zla zhing hastasa g.yab /
NK020(wa)003:1847: spos rol dang bcas pas dkyil 'khor la bskor bas /
