NK020(wa)003:1848: zhi khro sman gyi rig 'dzin dang bcas pa nam
NK020(wa)003:1849: mkha' 'gengs pa tsam du byon nas byin gyis rlob
NK020(wa)003:1850: par bsam la nyams bskyang ngo //
NK020(wa)003:1851: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi shar phyogs su slob dpon
NK020(wa)003:1852: dkyil 'khor la phyogs pa'i mdun du yum gnas pa'i
NK020(wa)003:1853: zhabs gnyis bsnol ba'i dbus su zhing lpags steng sman
NK020(wa)003:1854: gzhong bkod pa yum gyis mkha' dbyings kyi rgyas bzung
NK020(wa)003:1855: / yab kyis rdor bsdams las mdzub mo sgreng zhing mthe bong bkug pas gtun bu bzung ste /
NK020(wa)003:1856: gtso bo yab yum gyi nga rgyal gyis /
NK020(wa)003:1858: gtun bu yab kyi rdo rje /
NK020(wa)003:1859: sman byang sems dkar dmar gyi rang bzhin du mos la /
NK020(wa)003:1860: 'thag pa ni 'dod chags 'thag pa zhes bya ste /
NK020(wa)003:1861: rgyud kyi dngos bstan gyi dgongs pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:1862: gzhan yang khro mo'i gtun khung du khro bo 'bar
NK020(wa)003:1863: ba'i gtun tshogs kyis sman dgra bgegs kyi rnam par
NK020(wa)003:1864: bsam pa ni zhe sdang 'thag pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1865: chos kyi dbyings su rig pa'i ye shes kyis rnam
NK020(wa)003:1866: rtog gi mtshan ma 'thag pa ni gti mug 'thag
NK020(wa)003:1867: pa zhes tha snyad mdzad cing /
NK020(wa)003:1868: de thams cad kyi las sngags ni /
NK020(wa)003:1869: +aah h+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta mu sa la gra han+te ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:1872: dkyil 'khor gyi lho yum gyis dar tshags bzed cing yab kyis blug la /
NK020(wa)003:1873: chos nyid kyi klong du mtshan rtog rdul tsam yang mi gnas par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)003:1874: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta ho sa ya bi shud+d+he h+aum h+r+aih th+aa /
NK020(wa)003:1876: bsre spol gyi dgongs pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:1877: dkyil 'khor gyi nub tu yab yum gnas pas sman snod la lcags gaya'i dri med par byas te /
NK020(wa)003:1878: sbyor tshad sogs phyag bzhes mthong brgyud ltar nges pas /
NK020(wa)003:1879: dri bzang rnams dang dam rtsi'i dbang lag ma gtogs
NK020(wa)003:1880: thams cad 'dres par bsre zhing 'brum med par sbol
NK020(wa)003:1881: ba'i steng du / chang dang 'o ma dang rin
NK020(wa)003:1882: chen dang chu rnams so so'i las sngags rim par
NK020(wa)003:1883: ba'i steng du / / badz+ra a mri ta dza gad pra wa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:1884: ga tim sam shod+ha ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:1885: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta rat+na tsit+ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK020(wa)003:1886: a mri ta bi shud+d+ha kun+da l+ai s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:1887: zhes bzla bzhin du kha phru 'debs de nas dam
NK020(wa)003:1888: rdzas kyi phab sbyar ba'i chang gi nying khu btab
NK020(wa)003:1889: nas ska sla ran par gyur pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:1890: dri bzang gi phyes mdangs sgyur zhing dam rtsi'i phye btab la sbol bas /
NK020(wa)003:1891: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med du gyur par mos la /
NK020(wa)003:1892: badz+ra amri ta mu sa la mu sa la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:1895: dkyil 'khor gyi byang du nam zla dang bstun pa'i phab btab la yum gyis /
NK020(wa)003:1896: kun tu bzang mo'i gzhal yas su //
NK020(wa)003:1897: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa las //
NK020(wa)003:1898: 'khor ba bdud rtsi'i sman du sbyar //
NK020(wa)003:1899: ye shes lnga ru gsal ba las //
NK020(wa)003:1900: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs su rdzogs //
NK020(wa)003:1901: 'chi med bdud rtsis gcong rnying sbyong //
NK020(wa)003:1902: zhes glu len zhing 'khor 'das bde ba chen po
NK020(wa)003:1903: ro gcig tu gyur par bsam nas mi rkang ngam
NK020(wa)003:1907: mtshan ma brtag phyir gzhal nas ni /
NK020(wa)003:1909: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+ya g+r+ai wa hu lu hu lu h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK020(wa)003:1910: zhes bzla zhing sman dril bur gzhal bas grangs nges par byas te /
NK020(wa)003:1911: dar dmar gyi khug mar blug /
NK020(wa)003:1912: de mo thod la rak+tasa 'khor lo rtsibs bzhir rigs
NK020(wa)003:1913: lnga yum gyi sa bon bris pa'i nang du bcug
NK020(wa)003:1914: / pho thod la bdud rtsis 'khor lo rtsibs bzhir
NK020(wa)003:1915: yab lnga'i sa bon bris pas steng nas bkab ste
NK020(wa)003:1916: / kha sbyar / dar tshon lngas dril /
NK020(wa)003:1917: mchog gi rgyu mas rgya gram du bcings //
NK020(wa)003:1918: de'i sne mo steng du mdud pa la rdo rje
NK020(wa)003:1919: rgya gram gyis rgyas btab pas cis kyang mi shigs
NK020(wa)003:1920: par bsam mo // de nas drag sngags spos rol dang bcas pas bgegs bskrad la /
NK020(wa)003:1921: sman dbus kyi gtso bor mnga' gsol te /
NK020(wa)003:1922: che mchog gi sngags bzla bzhin du 'dus pa chen
NK020(wa)003:1923: po'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa'i steng gi lding khri bar
NK020(wa)003:1924: ma'i dbus su rus sbal gyi khog par h+r+aihyiga bris
NK020(wa)003:1926: sh+au nya t+aa sogs dbang sngags brjod nas sman gyi steng du dbu rgyan 'ching /
NK020(wa)003:1927: gzungs thag btags la srad bu phyir drangs te bzhag go //
NK020(wa)003:1928: de skad du'ang he ru ka 'dus par //
NK020(wa)003:1929: dang por btags btsag gzhal byas la //
NK020(wa)003:1930: tshad dang ldan pa'i bdud rtsi ni //
NK020(wa)003:1931: bdud rtsi 'khyil bar mnga' gsol la //
NK020(wa)003:1932: byin brlabs dbang bskur dbus su bzhag /
NK020(wa)003:1934: bzhi pa phye ma sgrub pa'i dgongs rgyud ni /
NK020(wa)003:1935: sgrub gzhung gzhan la brten pa'i phyogs la sman gyi
NK020(wa)003:1936: dkyil 'khor du zhal sgyur pa'i tshul sgrub khog tu
NK020(wa)003:1938: de la mdo'i sgrub pa'i skabs 'dir sman zhar sgrub
NK020(wa)003:1939: tsam yin pas bzlas pa'ang lha 'dzab gtso bor 'don
NK020(wa)003:1941: da res 'dir sman rkyang sgrub kyi dbang du byas pa'i cho ga la /
NK020(wa)003:1944: stong pa'i ngang las rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje
NK020(wa)003:1945: yab yum du gsal ba'i sbyor mtshams nas khro tshogs
NK020(wa)003:1946: 'bar ba'i sprin spros pas gdug pa can thams cad
NK020(wa)003:1947: tshar bcad / tshur 'dus nas phyogs bcur 'khod pas mtshams kyi las mdzad par mos la /
NK020(wa)003:1949: rang byung khro bo chen po bcu //
NK020(wa)003:1950: bgegs rnams thams cad gzir ba'i phyir //
NK020(wa)003:1951: phyogs mtshams phur bus btab nas ni //
NK020(wa)003:1952: bsrung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK020(wa)003:1963: sum+b+ha sogs kyis gzir mnan bcad do //
NK020(wa)003:1965: bla ma rig 'dzin rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs mkha' khyab tu sad pa'i spyan sngar //
NK020(wa)003:1966: dang po skye ba thog ma med pa nas //
NK020(wa)003:1967: rnam par smin pa'i lus 'di yan chad du //
NK020(wa)003:1968: mi dge'i las kyis 'gro ba'i rgyu bsags pa //
NK020(wa)003:1969: byang zhing dag par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK020(wa)003:1971: kun tu bzang po sogs sh+lo ka gcig /
NK020(wa)003:1975: dus gsum bde gshegs 'khor dang bcas //
NK020(wa)003:1976: rang bzhin gnas nas sku bskyod de //
NK020(wa)003:1977: sgrub pa'i gnas mchog 'dir gshegs la //
NK020(wa)003:1978: dbang bskur byin phob dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:1980: zhes bdag gnas yo byad thams cad la rdo rje gsum gyi byin dbab /
NK020(wa)003:1981: de nas bdud rtsi gtor ma rak+ta phyi mchod dang
NK020(wa)003:1982: bcas pa'i byin rlabs zhi khro thung ba'i thun mong
NK020(wa)003:1983: gi sngon 'gror sngar bshad pa ltar las /
NK020(wa)003:1984: bdud rtsi byin rlabs song mtshams tshig dang bstun nas bsang gtor bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:1986: bdud rtsi rang byung chen po 'di //
NK020(wa)003:1987: ye shes lha la gtor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:1988: bdag dang gnyis su med par 'grub //
NK020(wa)003:1989: dam can mched la gtor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:1990: thugs dam gnyan po skongs par 'gyur //
NK020(wa)003:1991: rnal 'byor pa la gtor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:1992: rtog sgrib bag chags byang bar 'gyur //
NK020(wa)003:1993: mi mthun phyogs la gtor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:1994: drag po gtum po tshig par 'gyur //
NK020(wa)003:1995: mchod pa'i rdzas la gtor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:1996: thams cad bdud rtsi nyid du 'gyur //
NK020(wa)003:1998: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la bzhi ste /
NK020(wa)003:2002: dngos grub blang ba'i dgongs pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:2005: ta krita brgyad dang he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:2007: dbang bskur byin rlabs gnyis med bstim //
NK020(wa)003:2008: mchod bstod bdud rtsi srung ma sbran //
NK020(wa)003:2009: rang rang bdud rtsi'i bzlas pa dag /
NK020(wa)003:2010: rtse gcig ting 'dzin bar chad med //
NK020(wa)003:2011: ces pa'i las rim ltar las /
NK020(wa)003:2012: dang po dam tshig pa bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2013: bdag mdun sgrub rdzas gsum dbyer med du bsgom pa ste /
NK020(wa)003:2015: e ma kun tu bzang po ni //
NK020(wa)003:2016: rang byung chos sku chen po las //
NK020(wa)003:2017: b+ha gar ji bzhin bzhag pa na //
NK020(wa)003:2018: byang chub de nyid ltung gnas med //
NK020(wa)003:2020: byang chub sems ni kun tu dag /
NK020(wa)003:2021: thig le chos skus khyab pa'i phyir //
NK020(wa)003:2022: ye nas dbyer med bya mi dgos //
NK020(wa)003:2023: dbyings su gyur nas mnyam gnas pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:2026: de nyid byang chub sems su gyur //
NK020(wa)003:2028: byang chub sems las rim bzhin bskyed //
NK020(wa)003:2031: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor a'i sgrar snang ba las /
NK020(wa)003:2032: e yam ram kem b+h+r+aum zhes pa'i sgra gdangs kyi
NK020(wa)003:2033: rkyen las 'byung lnga'i dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i 'bar
NK020(wa)003:2034: ba'i gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bkra lam
NK020(wa)003:2036: kun tu bzang mo nam mkha'i mkha' klong du //
NK020(wa)003:2037: dam tshig sgrol ma rlung dkyil rgya gram gtams //
NK020(wa)003:2038: m+aa ma k+ai ni rak+ta'i rgya mtshor 'khrug /
NK020(wa)003:2039: sangs rgyas spyan ma keng rus ri rab ste //
NK020(wa)003:2040: na bza' dkar mo kun tu drod 'bebs ma //
NK020(wa)003:2041: 'byung lnga yum lnga mtha' yas lhun gyis brtan /
NK020(wa)003:2042: b+h+r+aum las bskyed pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK020(wa)003:2043: nam mkha'i dbyings na mnyam pa ru //
NK020(wa)003:2044: tshul bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK020(wa)003:2045: gzhal yas khang chen gsal bar 'bar //
NK020(wa)003:2046: de ltar 'dus pa chen po'i 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)003:2047: sgo rim dgu pa'i dbus gru chad bzhi glo 'bur
NK020(wa)003:2048: gyis mdzes pa'i steng 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa'i lte
NK020(wa)003:2049: bar bdud rtsi rang byung gi dkyil 'khor yam ram
NK020(wa)003:2050: a las rlung me thod pa'i snod yangs shing rgya
NK020(wa)003:2051: che bar pad zla'i gdan la bcud sha lnga bdud
NK020(wa)003:2052: rtsi lnga de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga yab yum
NK020(wa)003:2053: du gyur pa rjes chags kyis mnyam par sbyor bas
NK020(wa)003:2054: byang sems ye shes kyi bdud rtsir zhu zhing 'khyil
NK020(wa)003:2055: ba la dpa' bo 'bru ldas mtshan par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:2059: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la
NK020(wa)003:2060: man+da la phata phata ha la ha la h+aum phata
NK020(wa)003:2061: / ces pa'i sgra gdangs kyi rkyen las khro bo'i sprin spros pas gdug pa can rnams tshar bcad /
NK020(wa)003:2062: tshur 'dus pa mthar byed brgyad du gyur te bdud
NK020(wa)003:2063: rtsi'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol rtsibs brgyad la phyogs
NK020(wa)003:2064: skyong gi gdan steng 'khod par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:2065: de'i steng du sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)003:2066: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:2070: zhes pas mthar byed brgyad kyi steng phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi'i he ru ka yab yum /
NK020(wa)003:2071: khrag 'thung bzhi'i steng du badz+ra sh+r+ai sogs zhes pas /
NK020(wa)003:2072: badz+ra he ru ka'i zhabs bzhi bgrad pas rigs bzhi'i khrag 'thung gi dbu bardzisa pa /
NK020(wa)003:2073: de'i steng du mkha' mnyam klong gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)003:2076: s+pha sam nyid kyis mum gyis mtshan pa 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK020(wa)003:2077: a kra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:2078: ces pas yum gnam zhal ma dbu dgu phyag bco
NK020(wa)003:2079: brgyad pa zhabs bzhis badz+ra he ru ka'i g.yas g.yon
NK020(wa)003:2081: rtsa zhal gyi dbu ma'i spyan b+ha gar phyed nub tsam du chud pa /
NK020(wa)003:2082: de'i steng du 'chi med rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)003:2085: s+pha sam zla dkyil h+aum gis mtshan pa las 'phro 'dus //
NK020(wa)003:2086: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai hre ru ka h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:2087: ces pas che mchog he ru ka dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK020(wa)003:2088: phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis zhi ba'i lha tshogs bsnams pa /
NK020(wa)003:2089: zhabs brgyad yum gyi g.yas zhal g.yon bzhi bzhi dang sbyor zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2090: gsang ba'i rdo rje yum gyi rtsa zhal dang sbyor ba /
NK020(wa)003:2091: rta mgrin dbang gi dkyil 'khor ni che mchog gi
NK020(wa)003:2092: dbu'i rtser rta zhal dmar po rta skad 'tsher ba
NK020(wa)003:2093: / de thams cad gdod nas rnam par dag pa bdag rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du rdzogs pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:2094: ha he phata a dzahh+aum bam hohb+h+yo zhes brjod pas gnas ma brgyad /
NK020(wa)003:2099: dbang phyug nyer brgyad de khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK020(wa)003:2104: pho nya sum brgya drug cu sogs bka' nyan gyi
NK020(wa)003:2105: dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa nyi ma las 'od zer
NK020(wa)003:2106: gyi tshul du bkra lam gyis gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)003:2108: rigs lnga'i dbang rgya spyi bor gtugs la /
NK020(wa)003:2113: kri t+ya nush+th+aa na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)003:2114: zhes rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyis zhu ba'i
NK020(wa)003:2115: ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur bas de
NK020(wa)003:2116: bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngas dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:2118: rdo rje rgya gnas gsum du gtug cing /
NK020(wa)003:2119: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya w+aa
NK020(wa)003:2120: ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko &
NK020(wa)003:2122: 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje gsum gyi lhas rgyas btab par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:2123: de nas zhal byang gis gsal gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2124: e ma'o dpal chen che mchog he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:2126: byin rlabs mchog dang ldan par mdzad du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2127: zhes pa'i bar sgrub khog ltar brjod do //
NK020(wa)003:2128: de nas ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drangs shing bstim pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2129: rang gi snying ga'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas ye shes kyi 'khor lo sad par bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:2130: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:2131: zhes pas snyan gsan dbab pa //
NK020(wa)003:2132: thugs rje'i lcags kyu sogs kyi mthar //
NK020(wa)003:2133: dzahh+aum bam hoh e h+ye hi /
NK020(wa)003:2134: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo dzah dzahs spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)003:2135: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra sa ma ya mu dra a /
NK020(wa)003:2136: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka tish+tha sa ma ya lhan /
NK020(wa)003:2138: dam tshig gi 'khor lo dang dbyer med du bzhugs par gyur pa la /
NK020(wa)003:2139: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas spros pa'i he ru ka phyag gnyis pas mchod bstod byas par mos nas /
NK020(wa)003:2140: a la la hoh a ti pu hoh ma h+aa pu ru sha hoh zhes phyag bya /
NK020(wa)003:2146: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK020(wa)003:2147: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK020(wa)003:2148: gnyis med bde chen las byung ba //
NK020(wa)003:2149: byang chub sems ni rdo rje ste //
NK020(wa)003:2150: zas mchog tshe yi dri chen po //
NK020(wa)003:2151: sha chen mchod pa rin po che //
NK020(wa)003:2152: pad+ma me tog yang dag ldan //
NK020(wa)003:2153: rdo rje chu ste bdud rtsi mchog /
NK020(wa)003:2154: ga bur shel gyi pog phor dri //
NK020(wa)003:2155: rin chen me ltar 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)003:2156: yon tan 'bum phrag yangs pa'i bcud //
NK020(wa)003:2157: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK020(wa)003:2158: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK020(wa)003:2159: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba //
NK020(wa)003:2160: dug lnga sel ba'i thabs mchog ste //
NK020(wa)003:2161: thams cad bdud rtsi rnal 'byor che //
NK020(wa)003:2162: ma lus bsdus pa'i thig le che //
NK020(wa)003:2163: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba //
NK020(wa)003:2164: gcig tu dpa' bo'i ro rnams dang //
NK020(wa)003:2165: gnyis su med par mnyam sbyar nas //
NK020(wa)003:2166: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK020(wa)003:2167: rgyal ba rgya mtsho thams cad la //
NK020(wa)003:2168: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:2169: thugs rjes brtse dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:2170: ye sangs rgyas pa'i che mchog he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:2171: sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor nyid la rdzogs //
NK020(wa)003:2172: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes thugs rjes brtser
NK020(wa)003:2173: dgongs dbang dang dngos sgyu 'phrul dkyil 'khor ye shes
NK020(wa)003:2174: rang snang ba'i // rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la //
NK020(wa)003:2175: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas thugs rjes brtser dgongs
NK020(wa)003:2176: dbang dang 'jam dpal gzhon nu rta mgrin yab yum
NK020(wa)003:2177: dang // bdud rtsi srid 'dzin mnga' bdag lha tshogs la //
NK020(wa)003:2178: rnam dag bdud rtsi thugs rjes brtser dgongs khro mo gnam zhal goo sim bcu drug bcas //
NK020(wa)003:2179: yum chen mkha' mnyam klong gi dkyil 'khor la //
NK020(wa)003:2180: rnam dag bdud rtsi thugs rjes brtser tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:2181: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor yab yum la //
NK020(wa)003:2182: rnam dag bdud rtsi thugs rjes brtser gnas yul sgo skyong spor ma gsang yum bzhi //
NK020(wa)003:2183: dbang phyug mkha' 'gro ma sring ging pho nyar //
NK020(wa)003:2184: rnam dag bdud rtsi thugs rjes brtser bsrung dang bskrad dang mtshams kyi las mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:2185: rang byung bdud 'dul khro bo bcu rnams la //
NK020(wa)003:2186: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:2187: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:2188: slob dpon mched lcam rigs drug pha ma sogs //
NK020(wa)003:2189: 'khor 'das byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la //
NK020(wa)003:2190: rnam dag bdud thugs rje brtse dgongs zhes phul la dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:2191: thugs kyi dngos grub dam pa ni //
NK020(wa)003:2192: dngos po med las dngos grub blang //
NK020(wa)003:2193: byang chub sems kyi sprin chen las //
NK020(wa)003:2194: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub //
NK020(wa)003:2195: a ho su kha d+harma k+aa ya +aahh+aum sid+d+hi h+r+aih zhes lan gsum myang ngo //
NK020(wa)003:2196: i dam push+pe d+h+au pe ba lim pra t+ai ts+tsha hos gtor ma phul /
NK020(wa)003:2197: ye nas rgyu nyid dag pa la /
NK020(wa)003:2198: nga dang bdag tu rtog pa yis /
NK020(wa)003:2200: khams gsum thams cad bsgral ba'i zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2201: a tsa la sa ma ya d+harma d+h+aa tu swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&aham /
NK020(wa)003:2202: zhes pas zhe sdang bsgral mchod dang /
NK020(wa)003:2203: lus kun yongs su 'khyud pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:2204: rdo rje pad+mara ldan byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:2205: rang byung rnams kyi bde mchog sems //
NK020(wa)003:2206: phul bas myur du grub pa yin //
NK020(wa)003:2207: r+aa ga p+au dza hoh zhes pas 'dod chags sbyor mchod dang //
NK020(wa)003:2208: rgyud drug 'khor ba stong par bsgral slad du //
NK020(wa)003:2209: dug gsum rtsad bcad sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)003:2210: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog kun dang bral ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:2211: mnyam pa chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2212: ma h+aa m+aam sa kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)003:2214: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)003:2215: zhes pas dug gsum ro mnyam dang /
NK020(wa)003:2216: lha mo rol mo bro gar glu yi tshig /
NK020(wa)003:2217: mdzes ldan sgyu ma'i gar dang tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK020(wa)003:2218: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams la 'bul lags na //
NK020(wa)003:2219: kun tu bzang po'i mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2220: ma h+aa p+au dza hoh zhes glu gar rol mo ye shes kyis mchod do //
NK020(wa)003:2223: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK020(wa)003:2224: sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor rang snang ba //
NK020(wa)003:2225: snang srid thams cad yab yum sku la rdzogs //
NK020(wa)003:2226: che mchog yab yum gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:2227: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK020(wa)003:2228: khams gsum sems can thams cad 'dren pa'i dpal //
NK020(wa)003:2229: 'gro drug sems can kun gyi sgrib sbyor ba //
NK020(wa)003:2230: bdud rtsi rgyal po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:2231: dug lnga 'bar ba sku lngar sbyor //
NK020(wa)003:2232: len pa med cing gtong ba med //
NK020(wa)003:2233: rigs lnga dpal chen yab yum bcu //
NK020(wa)003:2235: chu zla lta bur rtog bral zhing //
NK020(wa)003:2236: thams cad rtog pa yongs kyis spongs //
NK020(wa)003:2237: gnas yul sgo dbang 'bar ma yum //
NK020(wa)003:2238: bdud rtsi sbyor la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:2239: bdag tu 'dzin med rnam par dag /
NK020(wa)003:2240: bdud dang ngan song gsum las thar //
NK020(wa)003:2241: mkha' 'gro ma sring king pho nya //
NK020(wa)003:2242: bdud kyi bdud la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:2243: ces bstod la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2244: hoh spros pa med pa'i dbyings /
NK020(wa)003:2246: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa rang byung rang snang gi dkyil 'khor chen po /
NK020(wa)003:2247: bcom ldan 'das khro bo thams cad kyi che ba'i mchog /
NK020(wa)003:2248: dpal chen po che mchog he ru ka dang /
NK020(wa)003:2250: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK020(wa)003:2251: yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa
NK020(wa)003:2252: las sprul pa'i sku phyag na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)003:2254: dkyil 'khor gyi lha mo gnas yul sgo skyong nyi shu /
NK020(wa)003:2255: dbang mo king sogs ye shes dang las las grub
NK020(wa)003:2256: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshogs dang bcas pa
NK020(wa)003:2257: rnams mkhyen pa dang byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du
NK020(wa)003:2258: gsol / hoh rnal 'byor gi mchod pa longs spyod
NK020(wa)003:2259: rdzogs pa'i tshul du sbyar ba chos nyid la chos
NK020(wa)003:2260: nyid 'byung ba 'phags pa kun tu bzang po'i mchod
NK020(wa)003:2261: sprin bsam gyis mi khyab par sprul nas bdag nyid
NK020(wa)003:2262: chen po 'khor dang bcas pa la dbang mi 'tshal
NK020(wa)003:2263: ba'i slad du phud dang gtsang mar spags te phul
NK020(wa)003:2264: gsol / bas / ye shes la ye shes rol /
NK020(wa)003:2265: chos nyid la chos nyid rol ba'i tshul gyis bzhes shing longs spyad du gsol /
NK020(wa)003:2267: ye nas gnyis med kyi bshangs pa'ang bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:2268: de yan chad kyis spyi'i dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med du bsgrubs nas /
NK020(wa)003:2269: da tha dad du sgrub pa'i phyir /
NK020(wa)003:2270: phata dzah zhes brjod pas bdag rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor las /
NK020(wa)003:2271: mdun bskyed bdud rtsi rang byung dang che mchog rtsa
NK020(wa)003:2272: ba'i dkyil 'khor lnga ste dkyil 'khor drug lngan gyi
NK020(wa)003:2273: ngo bor rten dang brten par bcas pa logs su
NK020(wa)003:2274: phye nas mdun gyi nam mkhar me ri 'dabs 'byar
NK020(wa)003:2275: gyi tshul du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:2276: de nas sman srung sbran pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2277: dar snas g.yab cing spos rol dang bcas pas /
NK020(wa)003:2279: rtsi dang sman gyi bdag po dang //
NK020(wa)003:2280: rtags ldan rig 'dzin bran mo dag /
NK020(wa)003:2281: rol mo cha byad mang pos 'bod //
NK020(wa)003:2282: 'dir gshegs bcud len dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:2283: zhes spyan drangs pas sman gyi pho brang steng gi
NK020(wa)003:2284: nam mkhar sprin 'thibs pa ltar byon nas bzhugs par
NK020(wa)003:2286: byin gyis brlabs pa'i bdud rtsi 'thor zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2288: tshangs dang drang srong gtsang ma za //
NK020(wa)003:2289: lha klu bram ze'ang gtsang ma za //
NK020(wa)003:2290: de dag grol bar ngas ma bshad //
NK020(wa)003:2291: bdud rtsi dag pa ye shes lnga //
NK020(wa)003:2292: rigs lnga sku lnga lhun grub yin //
NK020(wa)003:2293: gnyis med rtogs pa'i thabs mkhas kyis //
NK020(wa)003:2294: gtsang rme med par kun spyod na //
NK020(wa)003:2295: de dag grol bar ngas bshad do //
NK020(wa)003:2296: ces pas gtsang rme'i gnyis 'dzin dag nas sman srung
NK020(wa)003:2297: rnams dngos grub stsol bar dgyes bzhin du bzhugs par
NK020(wa)003:2299: rdzogs pa'i ye shes rmad po che //
NK020(wa)003:2300: zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen dbang //
NK020(wa)003:2301: shar gyi phyogs su kha bltas nas //
NK020(wa)003:2303: mchod khang yid bzhin rin po che //
NK020(wa)003:2304: ru lu 'bru brgyad ye shes phreng //
NK020(wa)003:2305: phar 'phros pas ni thugs dam bskul //
NK020(wa)003:2306: slar 'dus pas ni dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:2307: 'di yang bsnen pa'i mchog yin te //
NK020(wa)003:2308: nam yang nyams pa'i dus mtha' med //
NK020(wa)003:2309: dus gsum dbyings su sbyong bar mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:2310: ces bskul nas bdag mdun sems dpa' sum brtsegs kyi
NK020(wa)003:2311: thugs srog sngags phreng dang bcas pa las 'od zer
NK020(wa)003:2313: ru lu'i bzlas pa brgya rtsas nyung mtha' byas pa bzla /
NK020(wa)003:2315: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer spros pa mdun
NK020(wa)003:2316: gyi bdud rtsi'i pho brang la phog pas sman khol
NK020(wa)003:2317: ba'i zer rlangs las dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i 'od zer
NK020(wa)003:2318: 'phros pa 'gro 'dul nas rta mgrin dbang gi dkyil
NK020(wa)003:2319: 'khor gyi bar rim par brgyud de mchod cing thugs
NK020(wa)003:2320: dam bskul bas / de dag las ye shes kyi
NK020(wa)003:2321: 'od zer bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun rim par babs pa
NK020(wa)003:2322: 'gro 'dul gyi dkyil 'khor las dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK020(wa)003:2324: de las 'od zer mkha' khyab tu spros pas sems can gyi don byas /
NK020(wa)003:2326: rdo rje gsum gyi byin rlabs sogs 'khor 'das kyi
NK020(wa)003:2327: dwangs ma'i bcud thams cad bsdus nas bdag rang bzhin
NK020(wa)003:2329: de yang gu h+ya lag gi phyag rgya rta mgrin
NK020(wa)003:2330: yab yum la thim pas de gnyis rol pa'i byang
NK020(wa)003:2331: sems dang 'dres pa gzungs thag rdo rje'i khong sang
NK020(wa)003:2332: nas phyung ste bdud rtsi'i pho brang la thim pas
NK020(wa)003:2333: sman nyid ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du
NK020(wa)003:2334: mu tig dkar bo dri ma med pa ltar gyur
NK020(wa)003:2335: par mos la / g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyis gzungs thag la 'jus te /
NK020(wa)003:2336: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2337: zhes dgu pa'i sngags su grags pa ste /
NK020(wa)003:2339: dgu pa'i phyag rgyas mnan cing bzla /
NK020(wa)003:2340: zhes pas rtags ma mthong bar thun thams cad la sngags dang ting 'dzin 'di kho na bya ste /
NK020(wa)003:2341: sgrub khog tu bris pa'i sngags dang ting 'dzin ni
NK020(wa)003:2342: mdo'i bdud rtsi sgrub pa'i cho ga thun mong ba
NK020(wa)003:2344: de yang sngags stong phrag re'i mtshams su tshogs bya
NK020(wa)003:2345: bar bshad kyang 'grub dka' bas thun rjes ma'i mthar
NK020(wa)003:2346: lan re dang / thun thams cad la stong stong gi mtshams su sngags mchod re bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2347: bsnyen grogs yod bzlas pa gsung mi chag tu bazla'o //
NK020(wa)003:2348: gzhan yang dus gnad dang sbyar ba'i nyul le bsal
NK020(wa)003:2349: ba dang byin dbab pa'ang sgrub khog tu bshad pa
NK020(wa)003:2350: ltar ro // thun bsdu ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:2351: mdun bskyed kyi gzhal yas khang 'khor la /
NK020(wa)003:2352: 'khor rnams rim bzhin snying po'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK020(wa)003:2353: de nyid rta mgrin dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas 'gro
NK020(wa)003:2354: 'dul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi bar 'od du zhu
NK020(wa)003:2355: nas bdud rtsi la thim par bsgom mo //
NK020(wa)003:2356: bdag rang bzhin dkyil 'khor 'od gsal du bsdu zhing lngang ba sgrub thabs ltar ro //
NK020(wa)003:2357: gnyis pa bdud rtsi skyil ba'i dgongs pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2359: 'od dang du ba sgra dang dril //
NK020(wa)003:2360: lha mos lung bstan byung ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:2361: mang du 'phel na grub rtags yin /
NK020(wa)003:2362: zhes pa ltar rtags ci rigs byung ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:2363: snod b+hany+dza'i gzhal yas khang du bcud bdud rtsi rgya
NK020(wa)003:2364: mtshor skyil ba la sman srung rnams kyis kyang mtsho
NK020(wa)003:2365: la sbrang char babs pa bzhin du phob pas dngos
NK020(wa)003:2366: grub gsos btab par mos la /
NK020(wa)003:2367: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kun+da l+ai h+aum hrihth+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2369: sman srung rnams kyang bskul zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2370: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta me pra be sha ya pra be sha ya h+aum h+r+aih th+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2371: zhes bzla zhing dbab pa'i phyag rgyas sman la gtug go //
NK020(wa)003:2372: gsum pa dbang du bya ba'i dgongs pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2373: rtags brtan nas dngos grub blang ran pa dang bya ste /
NK020(wa)003:2374: sman gyi pho brang nang du rta mgrin yab yum
NK020(wa)003:2375: gsal ba'i byang sems sman dang 'dres nas gzungs thag
NK020(wa)003:2376: khong seng gi lam brgyud de byung ba bdag la
NK020(wa)003:2378: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mrii ta ha ya g+r+ai wa hu lu hu lu ban+d+ha ban+d+ha h+aum h+r+aih th+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2379: zhes bzlas pas dngos grub gzhan gyis mi 'phrog par bdag gis thob par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:2380: bzhi pa dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:2381: mtshams bshags dam bca' byin dbab rnams sngon du 'gro bas dngos grub bskul ba'i 'dzab ni /
NK020(wa)003:2382: lha tshogs rnams kyi gnas lnga nas rdo rje'i lnga'i
NK020(wa)003:2383: dngos grub thams cad 'chi med bdud rtsi'i rnam par
NK020(wa)003:2384: byung ba rang la thim par bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:2385: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta many+dzu sh+r+ai bya ba lo ki te h+aum h+r+aih th+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2387: de nas g.yon pa'i mtheb srin rtse sprad pas bdud rtsi'i steng nas mnan te /
NK020(wa)003:2388: a ho su kha d+harma k+aa ya ni a mri ta sid+d+hi h+aum h+r+aih th+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2390: sgrub khog tu gnad nas bskul ba'i tshig /
NK020(wa)003:2392: nam mkha'i mtha' klas chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab //
NK020(wa)003:2394: bdag gi las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:2395: ces pa'i bar gyis bskul rjes me tog dor nas
NK020(wa)003:2396: sman gyi dngos grub blang zhing dbang nod pa go
NK020(wa)003:2397: chu rub tu bya ba'ang sgrub khog bzhin du ste
NK020(wa)003:2398: / rgyas pa la mos na gsang chen myur lam ltar sbyar ro //
NK020(wa)003:2399: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2401: bdud rtsis lha mchod pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:2402: bdud rtsi bgo ba sogs bdud rtsi rang gi rjes
NK020(wa)003:2403: chog thun mong ma yin pa rnams ni gsang chen
NK020(wa)003:2404: myur lam ltar shes par bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2405: nyin re bzhin thun gyi mtha' rnams su bya ba'i las kyi made'u tshogs gtor dang /
NK020(wa)003:2407: go bgo lus bsrung bsngo shis rnams ni /
NK020(wa)003:2408: shas cher las byang yig rnying du'ang 'byung mod kyi /
NK020(wa)003:2409: 'on kyang 'dir lag len bde phyir sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs ltar bya ba yin no //
NK020(wa)003:2410: mdo'i sgrub khog gi sman sgrub las 'phros ba'i zur 'debs le tshan no //
NK020(wa)003:2413: mi 'gyur lhan skyes phyag rgyas 'khor 'das chos //
NK020(wa)003:2414: gnyis med ye shes rdo rjer byin brlabs nas //
NK020(wa)003:2415: 'gro kun phan bder mdzad po bla ma la //
NK020(wa)003:2416: phyag byas phyi nang dkyil 'khor rab gnas bshad //
NK020(wa)003:2418: phyi mdo dang thun mong ba'i rab gnas dang /
NK020(wa)003:2419: nang thun min gsang sngags bla med kyi rab gnas so //
NK020(wa)003:2421: phyag bzhes su 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag gi dkyil
NK020(wa)003:2422: 'khor yo ga man chad la rten 'brel gyi cho
NK020(wa)003:2427: nye 'khor gyi sa gzhi skyang nul dang phyags dar gyis dag par byas la ba'i rnam lngas byug /
NK020(wa)003:2428: rten gyi mdun du stegs bu gru bzhi pa khru
NK020(wa)003:2429: gang las mi chung pa la rten 'brel snying po
NK020(wa)003:2430: lan bdun bzlas pa'i tsan+dana gyi chus chag chag btab
NK020(wa)003:2431: pa'i khar dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab brgyad bri /
NK020(wa)003:2432: de'i dbus su many+dzi'i khar bum pa tshad ldan dar
NK020(wa)003:2433: gyi mgul chings dang 'khor lo'i mtshan ma can bshug
NK020(wa)003:2434: pa sogs bkra shis pa'i shing gis kha brgyan pa'i
NK020(wa)003:2435: nang du rin chen 'bru sman dri ste lnga tshan
NK020(wa)003:2436: bzhi'i rdzas dang chu gtsang mas bkang ba bkod /
NK020(wa)003:2437: bum pa'i khar gser dngul lam mkhar ba'i me long
NK020(wa)003:2438: la tsan dan dkar po'i chus rten 'brel snying po
NK020(wa)003:2440: yon chab sngon du 'gro ba'i nyer spyod lnga'i mchod rdzas ci 'byor dang /
NK020(wa)003:2441: khrus sder me long khrus ras gos zung me tog sogs yo byad thams cad tshogs par byas la /
NK020(wa)003:2442: khrus dang dkon mchog la phyag byas nas stan bde ba la 'dug ste /
NK020(wa)003:2444: lha mi dang nyan rang byang sems bzhi la theg
NK020(wa)003:2445: pa chen po'i gso sbyong dang sems bskyed kyi sdom
NK020(wa)003:2446: pa blang / cha gsum sgo 'byed kri yog bzhi
NK020(wa)003:2447: la rang rang gi lha'i rnal 'byor bzlas pa'i bar
NK020(wa)003:2448: pa blang / bya ba'am / yang na de thams
NK020(wa)003:2449: cad la rang gi lhag pa'i lha gang yang rung
NK020(wa)003:2450: ba bsgoms la bzlas pa cung zad cig bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:2452: +aahh+aum gis 'dod yon bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)003:2453: sarba big+h+nana na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa sogs kyis bsngosa la /
NK020(wa)003:2454: deng 'dir rten rab tu gnas par byed pa la
NK020(wa)003:2455: bar du gcod pa'i gdon bgegs thams cad gtor ma
NK020(wa)003:2456: 'dis tshim par gyis la 'dir ma gnas par gzhan
NK020(wa)003:2457: du dengs shig / +aahbig+h+n+aan+ta krita h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:2459: mchod rdzas rnams rten snying dang /
NK020(wa)003:2461: stong pa'i ngang las gnas khang mchod rdzas dang bcas
NK020(wa)003:2462: pa thams cad dag cing bzang ba phun sum tshogs
NK020(wa)003:2463: par bsam la / rten 'brel snying po brjod pas byin gyis brlab bo //
NK020(wa)003:2465: thog mar bum sgrub bya ste /
NK020(wa)003:2466: me long la bris pa'i rten snying tshar bdun po
NK020(wa)003:2467: re re la'ang tshar bdun bdun te bzhi bcu rtsa
NK020(wa)003:2468: dgu bzlas la tsan+dana gyi chus sngags kyi yi ge
NK020(wa)003:2469: bkrus pa bum par blug nas bum pa rten snying
NK020(wa)003:2471: stong pa'i ngang las rin po che'i bum pa mtshan
NK020(wa)003:2472: nyid rdzogs pa'i steng du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la
NK020(wa)003:2473: gnas pa'i rten 'brel snying po'i sngags phreng dkar po
NK020(wa)003:2474: g.yon du 'khor ba las 'od dkar po 'phros pas
NK020(wa)003:2475: / 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad nas lha'i bdud
NK020(wa)003:2476: rtsi'i chu rgyun rnams bsdus la zla dkyil sngags phreng
NK020(wa)003:2477: dang bcas pa zhu ba'i chu dang ro gcig tu
NK020(wa)003:2478: gyur pas bum pa gang bar bsgoms te /
NK020(wa)003:2479: lag g.yas pas bum par bkab la rten 'brel snying po brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas rjes /
NK020(wa)003:2487: shap+da pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2488: zhes btags pas bum pa la mchod pa dbul lo //
NK020(wa)003:2489: de nas rten sbyang zhing bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2490: mchod rten gyi bum pa'i nang dang /
NK020(wa)003:2492: sku rten gyi thugs kar bsgom pa yin pas /
NK020(wa)003:2493: 'dir gnas bya'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i gzugs brnyan rnams
NK020(wa)003:2494: kyi thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la rten 'brel
NK020(wa)003:2495: snying po'i sngags phreng dkar po g.yon du 'khor ba
NK020(wa)003:2496: las 'od zer dkar po 'phros pas 'jig rten gyi
NK020(wa)003:2497: khams thams cad snang bar byas /
NK020(wa)003:2498: des sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpal thams cad
NK020(wa)003:2499: bskul bas gnas bya'i rten so so'i rnam par byon
NK020(wa)003:2500: nas rang rang la thim par bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:2502: mthar gnas bya'i rten thugs ka'i sngags phreng dang bcas
NK020(wa)003:2503: pa ro gcig tu gyur te mi dmigs pa las
NK020(wa)003:2504: / ye d+ha r+m+aa zhes brjod pas slar yang sgyu
NK020(wa)003:2505: ma tsam du rten so so'i rnam par bzhengs par
NK020(wa)003:2506: / gyur / de nas ye shes pa spyan drang zhing bstim pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2507: spos btul zhing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas /
NK020(wa)003:2510: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK020(wa)003:2511: rgyal ba sras bcas ma lus kun //
NK020(wa)003:2513: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK020(wa)003:2514: thugs rjes dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2515: ye d+har+m+aa sogs brjod pas spyan drangs pa /
NK020(wa)003:2517: gnas mchog gzhal yas pho brang 'dir //
NK020(wa)003:2518: so so'i gdan khri bzang po la //
NK020(wa)003:2519: gnyis su med par bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2520: ye d+har+m+aa zhes pas ye shes pa rnams rten so so la thim par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:2521: de nas khrus gsol ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:2522: me long gi nang du rten gyi gzugs brnyan 'char du bcug la /
NK020(wa)003:2523: sngar byin gyis brlabs pa'i bum pas bkru zhing //
NK020(wa)003:2524: phun sum tshogs pa sogs dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis sngon du 'gro bas /
NK020(wa)003:2526: lha rdzas dam pa'i khrus chab 'di /
NK020(wa)003:2527: rgyal ba sras dang bcas la 'bul /
NK020(wa)003:2529: 'gro ba sems can don slar du //
NK020(wa)003:2530: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol /
NK020(wa)003:2531: ye d+har+m+aa'i sngags lan gsum bzlas pas khrus gsol nas /
NK020(wa)003:2533: rkang ba gnyis pa'i khrus chab 'di zhes pa'i tshab tu /
NK020(wa)003:2538: ye d+har+m+aa'i sngags dang bcas pas ras kyis 'phyi zhing
NK020(wa)003:2539: gos zung dang me tog gi phreng ba re re
NK020(wa)003:2540: dbul lo // de nas mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:2542: lha rdzas dam pa'i yon chab 'di //
NK020(wa)003:2543: rgyal ba sras bcas sogs sngar ltar las /
NK020(wa)003:2544: ye d+har+m+aa nas sh+ra ma nahar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2545: de bzhin du yon chab kyi gnas su /
NK020(wa)003:2558: shap+da rnams bcug ste phul nas /
NK020(wa)003:2560: sku ni rten cing 'brel ba'i sku //
NK020(wa)003:2562: thugs ni rten 'brel thams cad mkhyen //
NK020(wa)003:2563: sku gsung thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:2566: rten gyi gzugs brnyan me long du shar ba la
NK020(wa)003:2567: lag g.yas pas reg nas rten 'brel snying po brgya
NK020(wa)003:2570: rgyal ba sras bcas ma lus kun //
NK020(wa)003:2572: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK020(wa)003:2573: ji srid rten 'di gnas kyi bar //
NK020(wa)003:2574: thugs rjes dgongs ste bzhug su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2576: su pra tish+tha badz+re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2577: zhes bum chus rlan pa'i me tog 'thor ro //
NK020(wa)003:2578: slar yang yon chab la sogs pas mchod nas /
NK020(wa)003:2579: gtor ma rten snying dang 'bru gsum gyis brlabs te /
NK020(wa)003:2580: a k+aa ro'i sngags rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas
NK020(wa)003:2581: srung ma rnams la byin zhing 'phrin las bcol nas
NK020(wa)003:2583: rgyal ba dgra rgyal bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:2584: bden par gsungs pa de la sdig med cing //
NK020(wa)003:2585: lhar bcas lha min gyis rtag mchod pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:2586: bden pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)003:2587: dam chos bdud rtsi thams cad mkhyen pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:2588: zhal nas gsungs pa bsil ba'i ro 'di yis //
NK020(wa)003:2589: nyon mongs 'bar ba'i me yis gdungs gyur pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:2590: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal rtag tu zhi byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:2592: bum chu dang me tog gi sil ma 'thor pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:2594: phyi mdo dang thun mong ba rten 'brel rab gnas kyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)003:2597: gnyis pa nang thun mong ma yin pa gsang sngags
NK020(wa)003:2598: bla med kyi rab gnas cho ga la gsum ste
NK020(wa)003:2603: khro bo rdo rje las rim las /
NK020(wa)003:2604: sdoms ni sngon du bya ba dang //
NK020(wa)003:2605: ting 'dzin lhag bskyed rang bzhin dbab //
NK020(wa)003:2606: dbang po'i skyon bsal mnga' gsol dang //
NK020(wa)003:2607: khrus gsol bkra shis ras kyi 'phyi //
NK020(wa)003:2608: mchod pa phyi nang gsang gsum 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:2609: bden pa'i byin rlabs dmigs brtan bzhugs //
NK020(wa)003:2610: yon bdag bskor phyag smon lam gdab //
NK020(wa)003:2611: ces pa ltar don dagu'am rkang pa drug pa dang
NK020(wa)003:2612: bdun pa gnyis gcig tu bsdus na don brgyad du
NK020(wa)003:2613: bstan pa'ang rigs bsdu na sbyor dngos rjes gsum las
NK020(wa)003:2616: gnas bya'i dkyil 'khor gyi mdun phyogs su khrus stegs
NK020(wa)003:2617: dri dang ba byung gis chag chag btab pa la
NK020(wa)003:2618: dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon du bri /
NK020(wa)003:2619: de'i dbus su many+dzi'i khar rin po che'i khrus gzhong gi nang du me long bzhag /
NK020(wa)003:2620: de'i nub tu many+dzi'i khar rab gnas kyi dbang bum rdzas so lnga'i bcud kyis gtams pa /
NK020(wa)003:2621: shar du bum pa lta bu ri na po che'i snod bdun du chu gtsang /
NK020(wa)003:2627: rin chen lnga rnams sbyar ba'i chus gang ba ste zhi ba'i khrus chu bdun /
NK020(wa)003:2628: kha tshar ma nyams pa'i ras dri ma med pa
NK020(wa)003:2629: la dri'i thig le lnga byas pa'i sku 'phyis dang
NK020(wa)003:2630: bcas pa / lhor thod pa lta bu snod ji ltar rigs par zhun chen /
NK020(wa)003:2636: dri chu rnams sbyar ba'i chus gang ba ste khro bo'i khrus chu bdun /
NK020(wa)003:2637: ro ras la bdud rtsi'i thig le lnga byas pa'i sku 'phyis dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)003:2638: byang du mkhar ba'i bum par ba byung lnga sman dang dri bzang sbyar ba'i chus gang ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:2639: de'i g.yas su dri zhim pos bgos pa'i til mar ram 'bru mar gyi snod dang /
NK020(wa)003:2640: dri dang ba byung sbyar ba'i snod /
NK020(wa)003:2644: par+pa ta ste shing shun lnga rnams durba'i pir dang bcas pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:2646: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol shar phyogs su
NK020(wa)003:2647: khrus stegs kyi g.yas g.yon gang bder dbang bo'i skyon
NK020(wa)003:2648: bsal ba'i mig thur sogs bdun dang /
NK020(wa)003:2649: zhi khro'i mnga' dbul gyi yo byad dngos sam tsaka li dang /
NK020(wa)003:2652: sman gtor rak+ta sogs mchod rdzas ci 'byor 'bul ba'i stegs bu bkod legs pa 'du bya /
NK020(wa)003:2653: lho phyogs su rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg gi thab bca' /
NK020(wa)003:2655: byang phyogs su tshogs kyi yo byad rnams bsham /
NK020(wa)003:2656: gzhan yang me tog la sogs pa nyer mkho'i yo byad thams cad tshang bar 'du byas la /
NK020(wa)003:2658: sgrub thabs ltar zhi khro yongs rdzogs sam /
NK020(wa)003:2659: sgrub mchod dang ma 'brel ba'i ras bris lta bur
NK020(wa)003:2660: rkyang chog byed na lus dkyil dang sbyar ba'i zhi
NK020(wa)003:2661: thung tsam la brten kyang rung ngo //
NK020(wa)003:2664: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum zhes brjod pas rin po
NK020(wa)003:2665: che'i bum pa mtshan nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang
NK020(wa)003:2666: du h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa zhes brjod pas rigs lnga
NK020(wa)003:2667: yab yum gyi sku bkra lam gyi gsal bar bskyed
NK020(wa)003:2668: la / bskur rlob dbab drang bstim brtan mchod cing bstod nas /
NK020(wa)003:2670: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika m+aum d+h+aa t+wi shwa r+ai sogs rigs
NK020(wa)003:2671: lnga'i sngags la rten 'brel snying po btags pa ci
NK020(wa)003:2672: nus bzlas nas / yig brgyas bzod par gsol la lha mi zhu bar bzhag /
NK020(wa)003:2673: chu bdun tshan gnyis swa b+h+aa wa sogs chos nyid
NK020(wa)003:2674: rnam dag gi sngags rgyas rdzas rnams kyi dri ma
NK020(wa)003:2675: sbyangs / na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs
NK020(wa)003:2676: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgyas rdzas rnams rgya cher
NK020(wa)003:2677: sbyangs / sprel / badz+ra a mri ta sogs bdud
NK020(wa)003:2678: rtsi thabs sbyor gyi sngags rgyas dri ma sbyong ba
NK020(wa)003:2679: la thogs pa med pa'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi
NK020(wa)003:2680: nus ldan du gyur par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:2681: bzhi pa rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg ni /
NK020(wa)003:2682: spro zhing nus na skabs 'dir bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:2683: lnga pa rten gyi bgegs sbyang ni /
NK020(wa)003:2684: h+aum zhes brjod pas dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i thugs
NK020(wa)003:2685: ka nas bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje 'jigs shing
NK020(wa)003:2686: rngams pa'i skur thon pa'i shangs kyi h+aum ring dang
NK020(wa)003:2687: byang chub kyi sems sprin khro bo dang mtshon cha'i
NK020(wa)003:2688: tshogs su spros pas bgegs thams cad tshar bcad nas
NK020(wa)003:2689: tshur 'dus pa bsrung ba'i gur du 'khrigs par bsam
NK020(wa)003:2691: dbang mchog sgrub pa'i gnas 'di ru //
NK020(wa)003:2692: dkyil 'khor rab tu gnas bya yis //
NK020(wa)003:2693: phyogs skyong bcu po gnon pa dang //
NK020(wa)003:2694: 'khor gyi gdon bgegs ma lus kun //
NK020(wa)003:2695: dus gsum sangs rgyas bka' byung gis //
NK020(wa)003:2697: zhes bka' bsgoms la rdo rje gsor zhing dril bu 'khrol bas /
NK020(wa)003:2698: badz+ra kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum a a a h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:2700: gzhan yang khro bcu'i sngags dang sum+b+ha'i sngags bzla zhing gnas bya'i gzhir gu gul gyis bdug /
NK020(wa)003:2701: yungs thun gyis brab pa sogs drag po'i tsham rngams bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:2702: drug pa rten gyi dri ma dang bzo bo la
NK020(wa)003:2703: sogs pa'i mi ga tsang ba'i dri ma 'khrud pa
NK020(wa)003:2704: ni / rten gyi gzugs brnyan me long du 'char du bcug la /
NK020(wa)003:2706: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi shod+ha na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2707: zhes dri dang ba byung sbyar ba byug cing durba'i pir gyis bkru /
NK020(wa)003:2709: zhes til mar ram 'bru mar dri ldan durba'i pir gyis byug /
NK020(wa)003:2711: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi shwa d+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2712: zhes shing shun lnga'i phye mas phyis la /
NK020(wa)003:2713: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK020(wa)003:2714: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar //
NK020(wa)003:2715: lha yi chu ni dag pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:2716: de bzhin bdag gis khrus bagyi'o //
NK020(wa)003:2717: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:2718: zhes rol mo dang bcas pas dri sman ba byung sbyar ba'i bum chus bkru bar bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2719: rat+na pra b+hany+dza ra ha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2720: zhes ras kha tshar ma nyams pas phyis te /
NK020(wa)003:2723: zhes dri lnga'i chu thugs kar byug go //
NK020(wa)003:2724: bdun pa rang gi lha mchod cing gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2725: lag g.yas rdo rje dang bcas pa'i spos snod thogs la g.yon dril bu gsil zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2726: rang gi lce h+aum las byung ba'i rdo rjer mos la /
NK020(wa)003:2727: ji ltar sangs rgyas thams cad ni //
NK020(wa)003:2728: dga' ldan gnas nas gshegs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)003:2729: lha mo sgyu 'phrul lhums zhugs ltar //
NK020(wa)003:2730: de bzhin gzugs brnyan 'dir gshegs gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2731: mgon po 'dir ni gshegs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)003:2732: byang chub sems ni bskyed pa dang //
NK020(wa)003:2733: bdag sogs sems can don slad du //
NK020(wa)003:2734: ci 'byor ba yi mchod pa ni //
NK020(wa)003:2735: me tog la sogs 'di bzhes nas //
NK020(wa)003:2736: bdag dang slob mar bcas pa la //
NK020(wa)003:2737: rjes su brtse bas nyer dgongs te //
NK020(wa)003:2738: kun gyis byin gyis brlab mdzad cing //
NK020(wa)003:2741: rang gi snying ga'i 'od zer gyis 'dus pa chen
NK020(wa)003:2742: po'i lha tshogs mkha' khyab tu sad par bsam la
NK020(wa)003:2746: thal mo sbyar ba'i bar du me tog gi phreng ba bzung la /
NK020(wa)003:2748: mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid 'dus
NK020(wa)003:2749: pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs 'khor rgyal
NK020(wa)003:2750: ba rgya mtsho dang bcas pa thams cad bdag la
NK020(wa)003:2751: dgongs su gsol / deng bdag gis mtha' yas pa'i
NK020(wa)003:2752: sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK020(wa)003:2753: kyi go 'phang la 'god pa'i phyir rten 'di la
NK020(wa)003:2754: rab tu gnas pa'i phrin las bgyi bar 'tshal bas
NK020(wa)003:2755: dgongs su gsol / / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2758: rab gnas ye shes kyi snang ba thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)003:2759: pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh zhes me tog dor bas /
NK020(wa)003:2760: de nyid rang gi lhag pa'i lhas spyi bor bcings par bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:2761: rat+na m+aa le a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:2762: zhes rdo rje bsdams pa las gung mo gnyis sgreng
NK020(wa)003:2763: ba'i rgyas blangs te rang gi gtsug tu bkod do
NK020(wa)003:2764: // gnyis pa dngos gzhi la'ang bdun las /
NK020(wa)003:2765: dang po dam tshigs bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2766: tshad med pa bzhis kun nas bslangs pa'i byang chub
NK020(wa)003:2767: kyi sems gsal gdab la dar cig mnyam par bzhag
NK020(wa)003:2768: / de nas gnas bya'i rten la /
NK020(wa)003:2770: ces las bum gyi chu 'thor bas sbyangs /
NK020(wa)003:2772: zhes brjod pas bdag bskyed kyi gtso bo yab yum
NK020(wa)003:2773: snyoms par zhugs pa'i sbyor mtshams nas rdo rje sems
NK020(wa)003:2774: dpa' yab yum thon te mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs
NK020(wa)003:2775: par gyur / de'i thugs kar gnas pa'i h+aum yig 'bar ba las ram yam kham 'phros /
NK020(wa)003:2776: rten gyi dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa thams cad dag /
NK020(wa)003:2777: thal mo khong stong gi rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)003:2778: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na d+harma d+h+aa tu swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)003:2780: rab tu gnas bya'i gzhis mtshon pa'i phyi nang gi
NK020(wa)003:2781: chos thams cad stong pa nyid kyi ye shes chos
NK020(wa)003:2782: kyi dbyings mtha' bral nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin
NK020(wa)003:2783: du dag par mos la nga rgyal bya /
NK020(wa)003:2784: de'i ngang las rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs ka nas
NK020(wa)003:2785: e yam ra sum kem ram zhes rim par spros
NK020(wa)003:2786: pas yum lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa 'byung
NK020(wa)003:2787: ba lnga'i dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub par gyur
NK020(wa)003:2788: / slar yang b+h+r+aum 'phros steng khang rin po che
NK020(wa)003:2789: dang 'og khang 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang phyi nang
NK020(wa)003:2790: rim pa dgu pa lha so so'i gdan dang bcas
NK020(wa)003:2791: pa bkra lam gyis gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)003:2792: de nas rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum rjes su
NK020(wa)003:2793: chags pa'i sbyor bas snyoms par zhugs pa'i sbyor mtshams
NK020(wa)003:2794: nas byang chub sems kyi yi ge'i sprin phyungs te
NK020(wa)003:2795: so so'i gdan gyi steng du 'khod pa las brten
NK020(wa)003:2796: pa lha'i 'khor lor gyur pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2809: k+r+aim t+r+aum srum bram k+sham ye /
NK020(wa)003:2812: h+aum hohrnamasa yongs su gyur pa las rigs drug pa
NK020(wa)003:2813: kun bzang yab yum la sogs te zhi ba rdo
NK020(wa)003:2814: rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs bzhi bcu
NK020(wa)003:2815: rtsa gnyis dang / 'og khang du h+aum ha he
NK020(wa)003:2816: phata a dzah h+aum bam hoh b+h+yoh e h+aum ting
NK020(wa)003:2817: rtsa gnyis dang / ha h+aum / dzahh+aum bam hohm
NK020(wa)003:2818: rnams yongs su gyur pa las bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK020(wa)003:2819: chen po che mchog he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:2821: rgyud lung gi he ru ka dgu rnams so so'i yum dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)003:2822: gnas yul sgo skyong nyi shu /
NK020(wa)003:2829: khro bo khro mo ya drug cu /
NK020(wa)003:2830: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu /
NK020(wa)003:2831: ma mo drug cu ste bdud 'dul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs /
NK020(wa)003:2832: phyi khyams la dus gsum gyi rig 'dzin bla ma /
NK020(wa)003:2833: gzhan yang sprul pa dang yang sprul phyag brnyan 'bum
NK020(wa)003:2834: phrag mtha' yas pa sogs 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil
NK020(wa)003:2835: 'khor gyi 'khor lo thams cad dwangs pa'i mtsho la
NK020(wa)003:2836: gza' skar shar ba ltar skad cig gis gsal bar
NK020(wa)003:2837: gyur / gnyis pa ye shes pa spyan drang zhing bstim pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:2838: lha thams cad kyi thugs kar rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa' /
NK020(wa)003:2839: de'i thugs kar rang rang gi phyag mtshan sa bon
NK020(wa)003:2840: gyis mtshan pa las 'od zer 'phros pas nam mkha'
NK020(wa)003:2841: gang ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bde ba
NK020(wa)003:2842: chen po'i ngang las cho 'phrul gyi rnam rol zhi
NK020(wa)003:2843: khro rab 'byams rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor chen por sad
NK020(wa)003:2844: par bsam la / spos btul zhing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas //
NK020(wa)003:2846: rgyal ba gang bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK020(wa)003:2847: rdo rje dam can ji snyed pa //
NK020(wa)003:2848: thams cad kun nas dgongs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2849: rgyal ba'i thugs dam bskang ba dang //
NK020(wa)003:2850: 'khor ba yongs su spyod pa'i phyir //
NK020(wa)003:2852: thugs dam bzhin du gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2853: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahh+aum dzahzhesa snyan gsan dbab la /
NK020(wa)003:2855: chos sku rig pa rang snang ba //
NK020(wa)003:2856: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs dang /
NK020(wa)003:2857: khams gsum ma lus 'dul ba yi /
NK020(wa)003:2859: rdo rje 'chang gral rim brnyes pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:2861: smon lam dam tshig tshul bzhin du //
NK020(wa)003:2862: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:2863: dzahh+aum bam hohe h+ye hi ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo dzahdzah zhes pas spyan drangs te /
NK020(wa)003:2864: dzahh+aum bam hohs rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)003:2865: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i sta gon gyi lha dang bcas
NK020(wa)003:2866: pa dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la dbyer med du
NK020(wa)003:2868: gsum pa dbang po'i skyon bsal ba'i chas bdun 'bul ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:2869: mig sman byugs pa'i thur ma thogs te /
NK020(wa)003:2870: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:2871: rin po che yi thur ma yis //
NK020(wa)003:2872: spyan gyi dbang po'i skyon bsal bas //
NK020(wa)003:2873: spyan lnga yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2874: badz+ra tsak+shu sa man+ta bi shod+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2876: gser gyi snyan 'brus snyan spabs bsal ba ltar bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2877: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:2878: rin po che yi snyan 'bru yis //
NK020(wa)003:2879: snyan gyi dbang bo'i skyon bsal bas //
NK020(wa)003:2880: snyan lnga yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2881: sro k+sham pra be sha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2882: gser gyi rmang tsher gyis shangs bsal tshul bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2883: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:2884: rin po che yi rmang gzer gyis //
NK020(wa)003:2885: shangs kyi dbang po'i skyon bsal bas //
NK020(wa)003:2886: sems kyi rnam grangs shes par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2888: gser gyi ljags gzhar gyis ljags kyi dri ma bsal bltar bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:2889: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:2890: rin po che yi ljags gzhar gyis //
NK020(wa)003:2891: ljags kyi dbang po'i skyon bsal bas //
NK020(wa)003:2892: gsung rab ma lus 'chad par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2893: de bya mu kh+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2894: gser dang rus pa'i thur mas zhi khro so so'i tshems 'bru ba ltar byas te /
NK020(wa)003:2895: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:2896: rin chen rus pa'i tshems shing gis //
NK020(wa)003:2897: tshems kyi dri ma bsal ba yis //
NK020(wa)003:2898: mnyam par bzhag pa thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2900: dung gi so mngas kyis rgyan can rnams kyi dbu skra bshad pa ltar byas te /
NK020(wa)003:2901: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:2902: rin chen dung gi so mang gis //
NK020(wa)003:2903: dbu skra lcang lo'i skyon bsal bas //
NK020(wa)003:2904: mtshan nyid ma 'dres mkhyen par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2905: ma nu sam so s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2906: gser gyi spu gris thub drug sogs kyi dbu skra dang zhal spu 'breg tshul byas te /
NK020(wa)003:2907: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:2908: rin po che yi spu gri yis //
NK020(wa)003:2909: dbu dang zhal gyi spu bregs pas //
NK020(wa)003:2910: nyon mongs rtsad nas gcod par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2913: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:2914: 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams
NK020(wa)003:2915: la dbang po la sogs pa'i skyon bsal ba'i nyer
NK020(wa)003:2916: spyad phul pas / ye shes kyi spyan rnam par
NK020(wa)003:2917: dag pa la sogs te ji skad smos pa'i yon
NK020(wa)003:2918: tan de thams cad bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK020(wa)003:2919: can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:2920: bzhi pa dngos po'i skyon sbyang ba'i chas dgu las /
NK020(wa)003:2921: thog mar zhi khro thun mong du me long dbul te /
NK020(wa)003:2923: me long dag la gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK020(wa)003:2924: chos rnams rang bzhin gdon nas dag pa la //
NK020(wa)003:2925: che ba'i yon tan mang po 'byung 'gyur zhing //
NK020(wa)003:2926: rnam par byang ba'i chos nyid gsal bar shog /
NK020(wa)003:2928: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:2929: 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs la
NK020(wa)003:2930: me long phul bas kun gzhi bag chags kyi g.ya'
NK020(wa)003:2931: dang bral nas chos sku brjod med kyi don bdag
NK020(wa)003:2932: dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob
NK020(wa)003:2933: par gyur cig / zhi khro'i chu bdun tshan gnyis kyis khrus gsol zhing 'phyi ba las /
NK020(wa)003:2934: dang po sngar phul ba'i me long gi nang du
NK020(wa)003:2935: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gzugs brnyan 'char du bcug
NK020(wa)003:2936: la / zhi ba'i chu bdun gyis rim par bkru ste /
NK020(wa)003:2938: rgyal ba'i sku la nyon mongs mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)003:2939: sems can nyon mongs bag chags bsal slad du //
NK020(wa)003:2940: rgyal ba'i sku la chu gtsang khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:2941: las dang nyon mongs bag chags dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2942: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi shod+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2944: rgyal ba'i sku la rab rib mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)003:2945: sems can ma rig mun pa bsal slad du //
NK020(wa)003:2946: rgyal ba'i sku la spu chab khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:2947: rmongs pa'i rab rib ma lus dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2948: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2950: rgyal ba'i sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)003:2951: sems can sdug bsngal dri ma bsal slad du //
NK020(wa)003:2952: rgyal ba'i sku la 'dag 'chal khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:2953: tshul khrims mngon par byang chub sku thob shog /
NK020(wa)003:2954: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2956: rgyal ba'i sku la bsnyel ba mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)003:2957: sems can mu ge'i sdug bsngal bsal slad du //
NK020(wa)003:2958: rgyal ba'i sku la 'bru chab khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:2959: ting 'dzin phung po chos sku dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2960: sarba ta t+aa ga ta spos chab thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:2961: phrin las lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la //
NK020(wa)003:2962: spos chen dri yi sku khrus 'di gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:2963: dri mchog stong gsum kun tu 'byung ba dang //
NK020(wa)003:2964: shes rab phung po sprul sku thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2965: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi shod+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2967: rdo rje sku mchog nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK020(wa)003:2968: dri med sman chab sku khrus 'di gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:2969: nyon mongs sdug bsngal nad 'joms rgyal po yis //
NK020(wa)003:2970: rnam grol phung po rdo rje'i sku thob shog /
NK020(wa)003:2971: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rin po che'i chu thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:2972: chos rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i sku mchog la //
NK020(wa)003:2973: rin chen chab kyi sku khrus 'di gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:2974: yid bzhin nor ltar ma lus re skong ba'i //
NK020(wa)003:2975: ye shes phung po longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK020(wa)003:2976: sarba ta th+aa ga ta na mo /
NK020(wa)003:2977: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:2978: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs la chu
NK020(wa)003:2979: bdun gyis khrus gsol bas las nyon shes bya'i dri
NK020(wa)003:2980: ma dag nas zag med kyi phung po lnga dang
NK020(wa)003:2981: 'bras bu sku lnga bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK020(wa)003:2982: can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:2983: ras dkar gyi sku 'phyi thogs te //
NK020(wa)003:2985: thugs rje lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la //
NK020(wa)003:2986: sri zhu gus phyir ras kyis sku phyis pas //
NK020(wa)003:2987: las dang nyon mongs bag chags kun bsal nas //
NK020(wa)003:2988: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK020(wa)003:2989: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:2991: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:2992: bde bar gshegs pa la ras gtsang mas sku phyis
NK020(wa)003:2993: pas gzung 'dzin las byung ba'i dri ma dag nas
NK020(wa)003:2994: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sku bdag dang mtha'
NK020(wa)003:2995: yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur
NK020(wa)003:2996: cig / gnyis pa me long du khro dkyil gyi gzugs brnyan 'char du bcug la /
NK020(wa)003:2997: khro bo'i chu bdun gyis rim par bkru ste /
NK020(wa)003:2998: zhun chen gyi chu thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:3000: don dam bcud kyi thig le chen po 'dis //
NK020(wa)003:3001: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3002: lhan cig skyes pa'i dri ma kun dag nas //
NK020(wa)003:3003: byang chub sems kyi rlan dang ldan par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3004: bo d+hi tsit+ta dz+ny+aa na bi shu d+d+he h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3005: thal chen gyi chu thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:3007: lhag pa'i thal ba phrin las rdzogs pa'i chus //
NK020(wa)003:3008: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3009: bdag gzhan gnyis 'dzin dri ma kun spangs nas //
NK020(wa)003:3010: gnyis su med pa'i don dang ldan par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3011: badz+ra bi sa smi ti dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3012: byang sems kyi chu thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:3013: skye med byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK020(wa)003:3014: dkar la dag pa gnyis med ye shes ches //
NK020(wa)003:3015: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3016: rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3017: badz+ra bo d+hi tsit+ta dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3018: dri chen gyi chu thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:3020: dri chen gsang ba'i rdzas chen dam rdzas mchog /
NK020(wa)003:3021: skye shi med pa rdo rje tshe yi chus //
NK020(wa)003:3022: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3023: de bzhin gshegs rigs dngos grub thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3024: badz+ra +aahyu r+dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3025: sha chen gyi dwangs ma'i chu thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:3027: khams gsum rgyud drug 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK020(wa)003:3028: dug gsum bsgral pa sha chen bcud kyi chus //
NK020(wa)003:3029: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3030: rin chen rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3031: badz+ra ma h+aa m+aam sa bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3032: pad raka gi chu thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:3034: pad+ma rak+ta gsang ba dbang gi rdzas //
NK020(wa)003:3035: chags par byed pa dmar la dwangs pa'i chus //
NK020(wa)003:3036: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3037: pad+ma rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3038: pad+ma rak+ta ti la ka bi shu d+d+he h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3041: dri chus kun gyi gsos byed las kyi rigs //
NK020(wa)003:3042: thams cad dag byed bdud rtsi chen po'i chus //
NK020(wa)003:3043: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3044: las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3045: badz+ra ma h+aa ma ma ku ku dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3047: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:3048: 'dus pa chen po khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs la
NK020(wa)003:3049: dur khrod kyi rdzas dang bdud rtsi lnga'i khrus gsol
NK020(wa)003:3050: bas lhan skyes dang kun btags kyi dri ma dag
NK020(wa)003:3051: nas byang sems kyis rgyud rlan cing gnyis med kyi
NK020(wa)003:3052: don dang ldan pas rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dngos
NK020(wa)003:3053: grub bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad
NK020(wa)003:3055: ro ras kyi sku 'phyi thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:3056: thugs rje lhun rdzogs khrag 'thung dkyil 'khor la //
NK020(wa)003:3057: dur khrod chen po'i ras kyis sku phyis pas //
NK020(wa)003:3058: shes bya'i las dang nyon mongs sgrib sbyangs nas //
NK020(wa)003:3059: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK020(wa)003:3060: badz+ra sarba ta th+aa ga ta dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3062: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:3063: khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs la ras chen gyi sku
NK020(wa)003:3064: phyis phul bas shes bya'i dri ma dag nas spyod
NK020(wa)003:3065: lam rnam par dag pa'i sku bdag dang mtha' yas
NK020(wa)003:3066: pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig
NK020(wa)003:3067: / lnga pa che ba'i yon tan rgyan chas kyis
NK020(wa)003:3068: dbang bskur zhing mnga' gsol ba la thun khyad gnyis
NK020(wa)003:3069: las thun mong ba dbang bskur ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:3070: nam mkha'i gang ba'i dbang lha rnams kyis bum pa
NK020(wa)003:3071: thogs te ngo mtshar ba'i dge mtshan du ma dang
NK020(wa)003:3073: bun nang gi rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyi
NK020(wa)003:3074: sbyor bas zhu ba'i byang sems ye shes lnga'i rang
NK020(wa)003:3075: bzhin bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur bar mos
NK020(wa)003:3076: la / zhi ba las rim las /
NK020(wa)003:3077: rang gi bum pa'am gcig shos kyis /
NK020(wa)003:3079: zhes gsungs ba ltar dbang bum sger du yod na des bskur zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3080: med na gcig shos rnam bum btegs la //
NK020(wa)003:3081: rin chen bum pas dbang bskur nas //
NK020(wa)003:3082: dbang chen rdo rje'i skur bsgoms te //
NK020(wa)003:3083: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin gyis //
NK020(wa)003:3084: dbang bskur chos dbyings gsal bar shog /
NK020(wa)003:3085: dbu'i gnas lngar bum chu gtig pa'i tshul bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3091: dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko &aham /
NK020(wa)003:3092: zhes dbang bskur bas dbang rtags su de bzhin gshes pa rigs lngas dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:3093: lha tshogs thams cad kyi spyi mgrin snying gar zla
NK020(wa)003:3094: ba pad+ma nyi ma la gnas pa'i +aahh+aum gsum las
NK020(wa)003:3095: 'od zer spro bsdus rdo rje gsum gyi lha tshogs
NK020(wa)003:3096: spyan drangs te 'bru gsum la thim /
NK020(wa)003:3097: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs dang gnyis med du gyur par bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:3098: dpal ldan sangs rgyas sku gsung thugs //
NK020(wa)003:3099: rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)003:3100: deng bdag sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK020(wa)003:3101: rdo rje gsum du dbang bskur ro //
NK020(wa)003:3102: rdo rje phyag rgya gnas gsum du reg pa'i tshul bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3103: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)003:3104: zhes sku gsung thugs rdo rjer byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK020(wa)003:3105: rtags su spyi mgrin snying gar rdo rje gsum gyi
NK020(wa)003:3108: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:3109: 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams
NK020(wa)003:3110: la ye shes lnga dang sku gsung thugs kyi dbang
NK020(wa)003:3111: bskur bas nyon mongs pa lnga dang tshogs brgyad ye
NK020(wa)003:3112: shes lngar dag cing khams drug rdo rje gsum du
NK020(wa)003:3113: rnam par dag pa'i dbang dam pa bdag dang mtha'
NK020(wa)003:3114: yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur
NK020(wa)003:3115: cig / khyad par du mnga' gsol ba la gsum las /
NK020(wa)003:3116: dang po gzugs bye brag tu mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:3117: yi ge so so las 'od zer 'phros de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mchod cing byin rlabs bsdus /
NK020(wa)003:3118: ma dag pa'i snang ba thams cad sbyangs tshur 'dus
NK020(wa)003:3119: zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams kyi sku'i cha shas so
NK020(wa)003:3120: so la thim pas rnam pa bye brag pa de
NK020(wa)003:3121: dang de gzi byin mchog tu 'bar te sngar las
NK020(wa)003:3122: khyad par du spags pas lta bas chog mi shes
NK020(wa)003:3123: par bsam zhing / 'di dag ting 'dzin gyis rnam
NK020(wa)003:3124: pa bye brag ba byin gyis brlabs te mnga' gsol
NK020(wa)003:3125: ba yin pas tsaka li med kyang chog go //
NK020(wa)003:3127: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK020(wa)003:3128: bde gshegs sku la dbu yis mnga' gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3129: rnam par thar pa'i dbu gsum thob nas ni //
NK020(wa)003:3130: khams gsum yongs su dag pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK020(wa)003:3132: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK020(wa)003:3133: bde gshegs sku la phyag gis mnga' gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3134: ye shes drug gis 'gro ba'i don mdzad nas //
NK020(wa)003:3135: khams gsum 'gro drug rtsad nas gcod par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3136: dza dza dza dzah s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan
NK020(wa)003:3137: dkyil bde gshegs sku la zhabs kyis mnga' gsol bas
NK020(wa)003:3138: // rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis 'gro don mthar phyin nas //
NK020(wa)003:3139: bdud bzhi ma lus zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3141: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la
NK020(wa)003:3142: dbu skras mnga' khyab pa thugs rje chen po'i phrin
NK020(wa)003:3143: las kyis // lta ba mthar mi ltung dang ldan par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3145: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs
NK020(wa)003:3146: sku la smin mas mnga' thabs chen mang zhing mkhas
NK020(wa)003:3148: gdul bya'i 'phro rnams chud mi gson par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3150: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil bde gshegs sku
NK020(wa)003:3151: la spyan gyis mnga' spyan lnga ma lus yongs su
NK020(wa)003:3152: rdzogs nas ni // rmongs pa'i rab rib thams cad dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3154: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil bde gshegs sku
NK020(wa)003:3155: la ljags kyis mnga' sgra skad bsam gyis mi khyab
NK020(wa)003:3156: bye brag gis // gdul bya'i sems can thams cad smin grol shog /
NK020(wa)003:3158: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs
NK020(wa)003:3159: sku la mche bas mnga' skye shi'i sdug bsngal rtsad
NK020(wa)003:3161: sgrib pa thams cad ma lus zad byed shog /
NK020(wa)003:3164: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la
NK020(wa)003:3165: sku mdog mnga' mi 'gyur chos nyid skyon gyis ma
NK020(wa)003:3166: gos dang // che ba'i yon tan spyod cing ma 'gags pa //
NK020(wa)003:3167: sna tshogs rol pa'i rgyan du shar nas ni //
NK020(wa)003:3168: phrin las lnga po yongs su rdzogs gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:3169: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3170: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK020(wa)003:3171: bde gshegs sku la phyag mtshan mnga' gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3172: ye shes drug gis 'gro don yongs rdzogs nas //
NK020(wa)003:3173: phrin las chen pos bsam pa mthar phyin shog /
NK020(wa)003:3174: khyad par khro bo la yon tan nyi shu phrag lngas mnga' gsol ba las /
NK020(wa)003:3177: s+pha sam rol pa nyi shu dpal chen thugs kyi bdag /
NK020(wa)003:3178: chos kyi 'brug char rnga dang dung la sogs //
NK020(wa)003:3179: mchod gzungs rdzas dang ye shes ting nge 'dzin //
NK020(wa)003:3180: sprul pa chos kyi ro dang ldan par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3183: s+pha sam che ba nyi shu dpal chen nyid la ldan //
NK020(wa)003:3184: 'gran zla med pas che btsan nyid du 'byung //
NK020(wa)003:3185: mi nub go bas 'dod pa thams cad rdzogs //
NK020(wa)003:3186: kun tu mdzad pas 'gro drug 'dren par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3189: s+pha sam brjid chen nyi shu dpal chen nyid la ldan //
NK020(wa)003:3190: sku che rgyan ldan bkur 'os yid dang 'thad /
NK020(wa)003:3191: mdangs che kun la ston pa'i mtha' dang bral //
NK020(wa)003:3192: thugs rje thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dren par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3195: s+pha sam rngom chen nyi shu dpal chen nyid la rdzogs //
NK020(wa)003:3196: sku gsung thugs dang mthun pa'i yon tan las //
NK020(wa)003:3197: zhal ljags tshems dang dbyangs dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK020(wa)003:3198: phrin las la sogs thams cad 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3201: s+pha sam cho 'phrul nyi shu dpal chen nyid la ldan //
NK020(wa)003:3202: chos nyid thugs rje chos kun snang ba yi //
NK020(wa)003:3203: kun spyod go bas cir yang snang ba dang //
NK020(wa)003:3204: gang ltar 'tshams par 'gro drug 'dren par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3206: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:3207: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs la zhi khro'i sku'i
NK020(wa)003:3208: rnam pa bye brag pa bcu dang khro bo'i khyad
NK020(wa)003:3209: par gyi yon tan brgya nyi shus mnga' gsol bas
NK020(wa)003:3210: ji skad smos pa'i yon tan de thams cad bdag
NK020(wa)003:3211: dang mtha' yas pa'i sems cad thams cad kyis thob
NK020(wa)003:3212: par gyur cig / gnyis pa mdzes pa rgyan gyis mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:3213: stong pa'i ngang las yi ge so so'i 'phro 'dus
NK020(wa)003:3214: rgyan cha rnams rang rang gi phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK020(wa)003:3215: yon tan can du gyur bar mos la /
NK020(wa)003:3216: dngos sam tsaka li rnams rim par thogs te /
NK020(wa)003:3218: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK020(wa)003:3219: bde gshegs sku la dbu rgyan mnga' gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3220: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad gnas dag nas //
NK020(wa)003:3221: ye shes lnga yis 'gro don mthar phyin shog /
NK020(wa)003:3222: h+aum h+r+aih s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs
NK020(wa)003:3223: sku la cod pan mnga' khams gsum gdug pa ma
NK020(wa)003:3225: srid gsum chos kyi rgyal po byed par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3226: hoh s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la rin chen snyan cha dang //
NK020(wa)003:3227: mgur chu'i rgyan gyis legs par mnga' rdzu 'phrul snyan gyis mi g.yo gas na par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3229: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la
NK020(wa)003:3230: do shal mnga' don rnams thams cad rig par rtogs
NK020(wa)003:3231: nas ni // mi brjed gzungs dang rtag tu ldan par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3233: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la se mo do yis ni //
NK020(wa)003:3234: mnga' gsol phul bas mi brjed gzungs kyi sgo //
NK020(wa)003:3235: 'bum phrag rdzogs nas rgya lag phrang gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:3237: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la
NK020(wa)003:3238: dpung rgyan mnga' mi 'jigs bzhi yi ting 'dzin thob
NK020(wa)003:3239: nas ni // re dogs kun gyi mtha' dang bral gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:3241: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la
NK020(wa)003:3242: gdu bus mnga' tshul khrims rnam dag stobs bcu lhun
NK020(wa)003:3243: grub nas // mtshan ma thams cad zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3246: sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la sems can chen po lnga'i //
NK020(wa)003:3247: gdan khri brjid bag ldan pas mnga' //
NK020(wa)003:3248: che ba'i yon tan lnga po lhun grub nas //
NK020(wa)003:3249: kun gyi bkur gnas sangs rgyas sa thob shog /
NK020(wa)003:3250: sems can lnga ni zhi ba la seng ge sogs dang khro bo la khyu mchog sogs lnga'o //
NK020(wa)003:3253: sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la nyi zla pad+ma yis //
NK020(wa)003:3254: mnga' gsol phul bas thugs rjes kun khyab nas //
NK020(wa)003:3255: lta ngan sel zhing chags med spyod par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3257: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la rin chen khri rkang gi /
NK020(wa)003:3258: gdan khri mdzod mig bdun pas mnga' 'gro ba'i re 'dod yid bzhin skong bar shog /
NK020(wa)003:3260: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan bde gshegs sku la
NK020(wa)003:3261: 'od zer mnga' bsam mi khyab pa'i ye shes rang
NK020(wa)003:3262: gsal nas // spros pa'i mtha' rnams yongs su bral gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:3264: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil bde gshegs sku la dar gyi chas gos lngas //
NK020(wa)003:3265: mnga' gsol phul bas 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK020(wa)003:3266: nyon mongs gdung ba ma lus sel bar shog /
NK020(wa)003:3269: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dpal chen sku la ko rlon gos phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3270: g.yang gzhi khyab pa'i thugs rjes 'gro ba 'dul //
NK020(wa)003:3271: glang ko stongs bcus sdug bsngal zil gnon cing //
NK020(wa)003:3272: stag sham mi 'jigs rnam bzhis bdud 'joms shog /
NK020(wa)003:3274: s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dpal chen sku la byug rtsi gsum phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3275: dug gsum rang grol sku gsum don mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)003:3276: bdag dang mtha' yas 'gro bas thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3280: h+aum s+pha sam lhag pa gzugs brnyan dpal chen sku la gdags pa'i rgyan phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3281: thod phreng thugs rje mi brjed gzungs thob cing //
NK020(wa)003:3282: sbrul chun zhe sdang ye shes chen por shog /
NK020(wa)003:3284: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:3285: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs la mdzes pa rgyan
NK020(wa)003:3286: gyis mnga' gsol bas ji skad smos pa'i yon tan
NK020(wa)003:3287: de thams cad bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can
NK020(wa)003:3288: thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:3289: gsum pa che ba'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pas mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:3291: s+pha sam gzi byin khyad par 'phags pa'i dkyil 'khor las //
NK020(wa)003:3292: lha rdzas las byung gdugs 'phan rgyal mtshan dang //
NK020(wa)003:3293: bla re yol ba lhab lhub rgyan phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3294: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs dag nas //
NK020(wa)003:3295: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3297: s+pha sam 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK020(wa)003:3298: bde gshegs sku la man+dala 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3299: 'phags pa'i nor gyis dbul ba kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)003:3300: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3302: s+pha sam 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' brnyes pa /
NK020(wa)003:3303: bde gshegs sku la yul mkhar 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3304: yul snang 'dzin pa'i 'ching ba kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)003:3305: 'phags pa'i zhing khams rnam dag thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3307: s+pha sam bde gshegs sku la bu dang chung ma dang //
NK020(wa)003:3308: bran dang bzhon pa la sogs gces dgu kun //
NK020(wa)003:3309: phul bas log par lta ba yongs spangs nas //
NK020(wa)003:3310: gdul bya'i kha lo sgyur la dbang thob shog /
NK020(wa)003:3312: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:3313: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs la che ba'i longs
NK020(wa)003:3314: spyod phun sum tshogs pas mnga' gsol bas ji skad
NK020(wa)003:3315: smos pa'i yon tan de thams cad bdag dang mtha'
NK020(wa)003:3316: yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur
NK020(wa)003:3317: cig / drug pa mchod pa sa mnyes pa yongs su bzung bar mnga' dbul ba la gsum las /
NK020(wa)003:3319: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa t+wa ban+d+ha n+aam ka ro mi /
NK020(wa)003:3321: pra ti pu hoh lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yis //
NK020(wa)003:3322: bde gshegs sku la phyag gis mnga' gsol bas //
NK020(wa)003:3323: lha dang bdag nyid gnyis su med rtogs pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:3324: don dang mjal ba'i 'bras bu thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3325: gnyis pa mchod pa dngos la /
NK020(wa)003:3327: bde gshegs zhi khro gar la dgyes //
NK020(wa)003:3328: sku mdog zhal ni rnam par 'gyur //
NK020(wa)003:3329: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu ba //
NK020(wa)003:3330: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK020(wa)003:3332: h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa la mnyam bzhag dang /
NK020(wa)003:3333: h+aum ha he phata la snying gar khu tshur g.yon gyen bstan steng g.yas nang bstan sprad de /
NK020(wa)003:3336: zhes g.yon phyogs su se gol gyis 'grol lo //
NK020(wa)003:3337: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK020(wa)003:3338: bde gshegs sku la phyag rgya gar phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3339: mi 'da' dam tshig phrin las rol pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:3340: phyag rgya bzhi don yongs su mi 'da' shog /
NK020(wa)003:3341: phyi kun bzang dang rnam lnga'i mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:3342: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor lha tshogs la //
NK020(wa)003:3343: snang srid kun bzang mchod sprin 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3344: spyod yul yongs dag lha dang dbyer med pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:3345: don rtogs kun nas kun tu bzang por shog /
NK020(wa)003:3346: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs /
NK020(wa)003:3347: rang bzhin spros bral chos sku rnam dag kyang //
NK020(wa)003:3348: sri zhu gus pas ar+g+ham 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3349: phyi nang byang chub sems su rnam dag cing //
NK020(wa)003:3350: bsod nams mi zad gter gyi phul gyur shog /
NK020(wa)003:3352: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i sku mnga' ba'i //
NK020(wa)003:3353: sangs rgyas sku la bdug pa 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3354: dam tshig sdom pa'i nyes pa kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)003:3355: ye shes thugs rjes ma lus skyob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3356: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK020(wa)003:3357: yon tan lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la //
NK020(wa)003:3358: rin chen mdzes pa'i me tog 'di dor bas //
NK020(wa)003:3359: log lta'i nyon mongs tha ba kun bral te //
NK020(wa)003:3360: lta bas mi ngom mdzes pa'i sku thob shog /
NK020(wa)003:3361: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu //
NK020(wa)003:3362: rang rig thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes la //
NK020(wa)003:3363: mun pa snang byed mar me 'di gtams pas //
NK020(wa)003:3364: ma rig 'thibs po'i mun pa kun bsal nas //
NK020(wa)003:3365: sangs rgyas la sogs spyan lnga thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3366: +aa lo ke h+r+aih snyigs ma lnga nyid 'bras bur yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:3367: rgyal ba'i sku la dri chab 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3368: gdung ba'i zug rdu mya ngan kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)003:3369: 'od zer mtha' yas 'gyed pa'i sku thob shog /
