NK020(wa)003:3371: nang dam rdzas gsum dang lhag ting gi mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:3372: ye shes sku mnga' lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:3373: rgyal ba'i sku la bdud rtsis mnga' phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3374: dug lnga gdod nas ye shes lngar dag pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:3375: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3376: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)003:3377: chos rnams longs spyod yongs su dag pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:3378: rgyal ba'i sku la gtor ma 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3379: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)003:3380: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3381: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ba lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)003:3382: 'khor ba'i rtsa ba 'dod chags zhe sdang dang //
NK020(wa)003:3383: gti mug rang grol rak+ta 'di phul bas /
NK020(wa)003:3384: khams gsum bag chags gting nas zad gyur te //
NK020(wa)003:3385: thugs rje chags pas 'gro kun sgrol bar shog /
NK020(wa)003:3386: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa rak+ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)003:3387: bde gshegs sku la lhag pa ting 'dzin gyi //
NK020(wa)003:3388: mchod pa'i bre brag bsam mi khyab phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3389: phyi nang gsang don ma lus kun rdzogs te //
NK020(wa)003:3390: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes nas //
NK020(wa)003:3391: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la longs spyod shog /
NK020(wa)003:3392: gsang ba dug gsum gyi mchod pa las /
NK020(wa)003:3394: ye shes spyod yul yongs su dag pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:3395: rgyal ba' sku la ta na 'di phul bas /
NK020(wa)003:3396: khams gsum dug gsum rtsad nas dag gyur te //
NK020(wa)003:3397: sku gsum lhun grub zhing khams dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3398: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ta na p+au dza hoh 'dod chags sbyor mchod ni /
NK020(wa)003:3399: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:3400: bde chen sku la ga na 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3401: spyod yul byang chub sems su rnam dag ste //
NK020(wa)003:3402: mtha' yas snyoms par 'jug pa thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3403: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa
NK020(wa)003:3404: ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aa t+ma ko&a ham
NK020(wa)003:3405: / gti mug 'dod yon ro mnyam gyi mchod pa ni //
NK020(wa)003:3406: mtha' yas lhan dang 'bral ba med pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:3407: gnyis med sku la 'dod yon lnga phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3408: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)003:3409: bde ba chen po'i thabs rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3410: a la la hoh glu gar rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:3411: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa dang //
NK020(wa)003:3412: gar stabs rol mo nges sbyar nas //
NK020(wa)003:3413: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor mchod par bgyi //
NK020(wa)003:3414: spyod yul yongs su dag par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3415: ma h+aa p+au dza hoh chogs kyi mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:3416: sgrub thabs ltar skabs 'dir bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3417: rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg sngar sbyor ba'i skabs ma khom na 'dir byas kyang mi 'gal lo //
NK020(wa)003:3418: yongs su smin pa phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:3419: bde gshegs sku la tshogs mchod 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3420: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)003:3421: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK020(wa)003:3423: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK020(wa)003:3424: bde chen longs spyong rdzogs sku rigs lnga'i gtso //
NK020(wa)003:3425: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol pa'i lha //
NK020(wa)003:3426: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)003:3427: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK020(wa)003:3428: zhi khro'i lha tshogs che ba'i yon tan la //
NK020(wa)003:3429: dad cing gus pa'i bstod pa 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:3430: sku dang ye shes yon tan mthar phyin shog /
NK020(wa)003:3432: phyos bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)003:3433: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs la phyag mchod bstod
NK020(wa)003:3434: pas mnyes pa yongs su bzung bar mnga' gsol bas
NK020(wa)003:3435: ji skad smos pa'i yon tan de thams cad bdag
NK020(wa)003:3436: dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob
NK020(wa)003:3437: par gyur cig / bdun pa bden pas byin gyis
NK020(wa)003:3438: brlab cing ba rtan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni
NK020(wa)003:3439: par gyur cig / / slar yang kun bzang zhabs
NK020(wa)003:3440: bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod pa sngon du 'gro bas
NK020(wa)003:3441: par gyur cig / / / rten snying bzlas pa'i
NK020(wa)003:3442: dri zhim po'i chus rlan pa'i me tog dang bcas
NK020(wa)003:3443: pas thal mo snying gar sbyar te /
NK020(wa)003:3445: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:3446: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3447: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3448: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3449: bcom ldan 'das bde gshegs zhi khro rab 'byams tshogs
NK020(wa)003:3450: chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi
NK020(wa)003:3451: bden pa dang / sprul pa yang sprul phyag brnyan dang bcas pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3452: khyad par rgyal bas gsungs pa'i cho ga'i las rim rnams par dag pa bsgrubs pa'i bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3453: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis lhag pa
NK020(wa)003:3454: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i rten dang yo
NK020(wa)003:3455: byad 'di rnams la sngags dang phyag rgya dang ting
NK020(wa)003:3456: nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas rab tu gnas par byas
NK020(wa)003:3457: pas // 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi rten
NK020(wa)003:3458: yo byad dang bcas pa 'di dag dus 'di nas
NK020(wa)003:3461: 'byung ba bzhi'i gnod pas ma zhig gi bar du zhes dang /
NK020(wa)003:3463: gshegs gsol gyi cho ga ma byas kyi bar du zhe'am /
NK020(wa)003:3464: 'dod pa'i don yongs su ma rdzogs kyi bar du
NK020(wa)003:3465: bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi bsod nams dag
NK020(wa)003:3466: pa'i rten du brtan par bzhugs nas sems can gyi
NK020(wa)003:3467: don dpag tu med pa mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)003:3468: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ga tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK020(wa)003:3469: zhes me tog gtor zhing lan gsum bazla'o //
NK020(wa)003:3471: dpon slob thams cad kyi lag tu me tog thogs la /
NK020(wa)003:3472: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)003:3473: dang byang chub sems dpa' ma lus shing lus pa
NK020(wa)003:3474: med pa thams cad la mkhyen pa'i ye shes /
NK020(wa)003:3476: mdzad pa'i phrin las ngo mtshar chen po grangs med
NK020(wa)003:3477: bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' ba'i bden pa'i byin
NK020(wa)003:3478: rlabs dang / bdag gis sems can thams cad khyad
NK020(wa)003:3479: par rdo rje'i slob ma 'di rnams kyi don du
NK020(wa)003:3480: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor yo byad dang
NK020(wa)003:3481: bcas pa rab tu gnas par byas pa'i mthus /
NK020(wa)003:3482: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3483: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu thams cad sku tshe brtan
NK020(wa)003:3484: zhing thugs kyi bzhed pa'i don lhun gyis grub pa
NK020(wa)003:3485: dang / 'jig rten gyi khams kun tu nad mug
NK020(wa)003:3486: 'khrud rtsod sogs mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad zhi
NK020(wa)003:3487: dang / zhing / char chu dus su 'bebs pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3488: lo phyugs rtag tu legs pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3489: tshe ring zhing nad ma mchis pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3490: 'khor dang longs spyod thams cad mthun zhing 'byor bas
NK020(wa)003:3491: sems can thams cad bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK020(wa)003:3492: skal ba dang ldan par gyur te /
NK020(wa)003:3493: sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa dag nas bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs mthar phyin te /
NK020(wa)003:3494: bla na med pa byang chub kyi 'bras bu myur du thob par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:3496: ye d+har+m+aa bzla zhing me tog 'thor ba dang bcas te rol mo sna tshogs pa'i sgra sbyar /
NK020(wa)003:3497: de'i dus su yon bdag gis rten la bskor ba bya zhing phyag byas te smon lam gdab bo //
NK020(wa)003:3498: gal te ras bris lta bu la rab gnas rkyang chog byed tshe //
NK020(wa)003:3499: srung ma rnams la mchod gtor phul te sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)003:3500: kyi bstan pa ji srid gnas kyi bar de srid
NK020(wa)003:3502: ces srung ma bsgo ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:3503: bzod gsol dga' ston yon 'bul la sogs rjes chog ltar gzhan rnams spyi ltar bya zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3504: rdul tshon du ma zad ras bris kyi phyogs la'ang dbang dang 'brel tshe ma byas kyang chog go //
NK020(wa)003:3505: gang ltar yang mthar bkra shis rgya cher brjod par bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:3506: gnyis pa 'bring po'i cho ga ni /
NK020(wa)003:3507: rab gnas bya ba'i gzhir gu gul gyi dud pas
NK020(wa)003:3508: bdug cing zhe sdang rdo rje'i nga rgyal brtan pos
NK020(wa)003:3510: ji ltar bltams pa sogs kyi mthar /
NK020(wa)003:3511: a b+hi shi k+aa'i sngags sbyar nas las bum gyi chus khrus gsol la /
NK020(wa)003:3512: k+aa ya bi sho'i sngags kyis sku 'phyi /
NK020(wa)003:3513: de nas rten bskyed pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3514: ye shes pa spyan drang zhing stim pa sngar ltar dang /
NK020(wa)003:3515: dbang po'i skyon bsal las spyan dbye ba tsam byas
NK020(wa)003:3516: rjes rnam bum gyis dbang bskur zhing mchod bstod kyis
NK020(wa)003:3517: mnga' dbul nas / bden stobs kyis brtan bzhugs byas
NK020(wa)003:3518: mthar bkra shis kyi tshigs bcad dang rten 'brel snying
NK020(wa)003:3519: po bzla zhing me tog 'thor ba rnams bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:3520: gsum pa bsdus pa'i cho ga ni /
NK020(wa)003:3521: dkyil 'khor du skad cig gis bskyed cing ye shes pa spyan drangs te bstims nas /
NK020(wa)003:3522: rten 'brel snying po bzla zhing me tog 'thor la yi ge 'bru gsum gyis brtan par bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:3523: gal te cho ga 'di'i sgo nas rten gsum so so la rab gnas byed par spro na /
NK020(wa)003:3526: rten gang yin kyang spyir 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed pa'am /
NK020(wa)003:3528: sku gzugs rnams rang rang gi rnam pa ji lta ba'am /
NK020(wa)003:3529: yang na sku gzugs mchod rte gtsug lag khang sogs sku rten phal cher rnam snang /
NK020(wa)003:3530: glegs bam sogs gsung rten rnams snang ba mtha' yas sam yum sher phyin ma /
NK020(wa)003:3531: rdo rje dang 'khor lo sogs thugs rten phyag mtshan rnams mi bskyod par bskyed la /
NK020(wa)003:3532: spyan 'dren sogs tshig gi 'byin 'jug sgyur lugs dang /
NK020(wa)003:3533: rgyan can rgyan med kyi khyad par gyi yo byad dang /
NK020(wa)003:3534: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa sogs skabs thob ma 'dres shing /
NK020(wa)003:3535: glegs bam dang mchod rten sogs la rgyan 'bul bye
NK020(wa)003:3536: brag pa bsnan pa sogs stob tshul gyi gnad shes
NK020(wa)003:3537: par byas nas / dbang gi rjes su sku gzugs
NK020(wa)003:3538: sngar rang rang du bskyed pa rnams ma gtogs gzhan
NK020(wa)003:3539: rnams so so'i sngags bzlas pas rang gzugs su bsgyur
NK020(wa)003:3541: de ltar rab tu gnas pa'i phan yon ni /
NK020(wa)003:3543: dkyil 'khor la sogs gang byas kyang //
NK020(wa)003:3544: rab gnas ye shes mi ldan na //
NK020(wa)003:3545: tshogs dang 'bri ba'i nus pa med //
NK020(wa)003:3548: sa la sogs la phyag rgyar byas //
NK020(wa)003:3549: rnam grol rim pa thob 'gyur na //
NK020(wa)003:3550: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pas //
NK020(wa)003:3551: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK020(wa)003:3553: bla ma'i gsung ngag chu klung rgyun /
NK020(wa)003:3554: sher dbang 'jug ngogs bde ba las //
NK020(wa)003:3555: legs bshad chos dbyangs lhung lhung sgrar /
NK020(wa)003:3556: skal bzang rna ba'i dpal du babs //
NK020(wa)003:3557: dkyil 'khor gyi rab gnas phyi dang nang gi cho ga so sor bshad pa'i le tshan no //
NK020(wa)003:3560: rang rig ye shes me dpung gis //
NK020(wa)003:3561: bzung 'dzin bud shing kun bsregs nas //
NK020(wa)003:3562: 'gyur med bde chen mchog brnyes pa //
NK020(wa)003:3564: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyis //
NK020(wa)003:3565: gdul bya 'dul thabs rmad byung ba //
NK020(wa)003:3566: yo ga'i zhi rkyang 'dus pa mdo'i //
NK020(wa)003:3567: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg cho ga bshad //
NK020(wa)003:3568: re zhig thog mar yo ga'i sbyin sreg zhi rkyang gi cho ga khyer bde bar byed na /
NK020(wa)003:3569: dkyil 'khor gyi shar phyogs su thab stegs dri dang
NK020(wa)003:3570: ba byung gis byugs pa'i gzhir tshangs zur gyi thig
NK020(wa)003:3571: btab par dbus nas sor bcu gnyis kyis bskor ba
NK020(wa)003:3572: thab dngos dang de'i phyi sor bzhi pa gnyis bskor
NK020(wa)003:3573: ba mu ran dang kha khyer /
NK020(wa)003:3574: thab nang du 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa'i lte bar sor brgyad pa'i rdo rje dkar po dang /
NK020(wa)003:3575: rtsibs kyi phyogs bzhir de bzhin gshegs pa bzhi dang mtshams bzhir yum bzhi'i sa bon sogs dang /
NK020(wa)003:3576: kha khyer la rdo rje'i phreng bas bskor zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3577: phyi'i grwa bzhir zla phyed rdo rje bri /
NK020(wa)003:3578: lha mtshan rnams so so'i kha dog dang /
NK020(wa)003:3579: gzhan thams cad tshon dkar po bri'o //
NK020(wa)003:3580: mu ran gyi nang du 'o ma can gyi shing
NK020(wa)003:3581: ngam ba lang gi lci ba srog chags med pa'i
NK020(wa)003:3584: sreg rdzas 'o ma can gyi yam shing rtse mo'i
NK020(wa)003:3585: cha las byung ba sor bcu gnyis pa dri dkar
NK020(wa)003:3586: pos spags shing rtse mo mar sbrang 'o mar nyugs
NK020(wa)003:3590: ku sha til mar gyis byugs pa rnams med thabs med la /
NK020(wa)003:3597: gro ste 'bru rnams la mar gyis spags pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3598: durba 'o mas sngags pa rnams g.yas phyogs su rim par sgrig /
NK020(wa)003:3599: g.yon du nyer spyod dang dkar gsum gyis brgyan pa'i gtor ma 'das ma 'das kyi rim pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:3600: dung ngam nya lcibs kyi snod du rdzas bdun ldan
NK020(wa)003:3601: gyi mchod yon la gtso sngags kyis basngagasa pa rnams
NK020(wa)003:3607: de nas yar ngo'i srod lta bu dus dge bar
NK020(wa)003:3608: slob dpon chas gos dkar po bstar la 'jam pa'i
NK020(wa)003:3609: stan la pad+ma'i 'dug stangs kyis 'dug ste /
NK020(wa)003:3611: bdag gi rnam 'byor dang ldan pas /
NK020(wa)003:3612: yak+sha'i sngags dang las bum gyi chus thab dang /
NK020(wa)003:3614: rdor dril dgang blugs rnams bsang /
NK020(wa)003:3615: rdor dril bzung ste sngags rgyas dam tshig gsum dran par byas nas /
NK020(wa)003:3616: sgrub thabs ltar mchod pa byin gyis brlab cing /
NK020(wa)003:3617: sreg rdzas rnams ngo bo ye shes kyi bdud rtsi /
NK020(wa)003:3619: byed pa rang rang gi las sgrub pa'i nus ldan du mos la /
NK020(wa)003:3620: snying po'i sngags dang rdzas sngags rnams lan gsum re bzlas pas byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)003:3621: rtsub shing gi me'am rgyud bzhag gi me spar ba
NK020(wa)003:3622: la yak+sha dang las bum gyi chus g.yas bskor du
NK020(wa)003:3625: zhes me thab tu bcug cing rlung g.yab kyis spar /
NK020(wa)003:3626: snying po sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ri h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3627: zhes bzla zhing mar khu blugs gzar bdun phul bas gso /
NK020(wa)003:3628: ku sha la badz+ra sa t+wa ah zhes bzlas pas brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)003:3629: sngags des thab kyis kha khyer la rang gi g.yon
NK020(wa)003:3630: ngos nas brtsams te snga ma'i rtse phyi ma'i rtsa
NK020(wa)003:3631: bas non par byas te g.yas bskor du dgram zhing
NK020(wa)003:3632: / slar rtsa ba rang la bstan pas thab steng nas g.yog go //
NK020(wa)003:3633: de nas thab a k+aa ros stong par sgom /
NK020(wa)003:3634: stong pa'i ngang las sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ri h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3636: snying po de zhu ba las byung ba'i thab khung
NK020(wa)003:3637: dkar zhing zlum pa'i nang du ram las me dkyil
NK020(wa)003:3638: gru gsum pa'i dbus su las byung ba'i pad+ma dkar
NK020(wa)003:3639: po'i steng du ram yongs su gyur pa las me
NK020(wa)003:3640: lha dkar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa g.yas gnyis
NK020(wa)003:3641: bgrang phreng dang mi 'jigs pa'i rgya /
NK020(wa)003:3642: g.yon gnyis dbyug pa dang spyi blugs /
NK020(wa)003:3643: dar dkar dang rin po che'i rgyan can pad+ma'i 'dug stangs kyis bzhugs par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:3644: rang nyid khro bo khams gsum rnam rgyal du nga rgyal 'phos te /
NK020(wa)003:3646: h+aum tak+ki dzah zhes pas me lha bkug par bsam la //
NK020(wa)003:3647: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po che //
NK020(wa)003:3648: lha yi drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK020(wa)003:3649: sregs blugs zhal zas bzhes slad du //
NK020(wa)003:3650: 'dir ni yang dag bsnyen par mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:3652: dzah h+aum bam hoh'i sngags rgyas dgug gzhug bcing dbang du bya /
NK020(wa)003:3653: rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags rgya lan gnyis kyis phyir 'brang gi bgegs bsrad cing bsrung /
NK020(wa)003:3654: rang rdor sems su sgyur la /
NK020(wa)003:3655: rdor thal gyen du phye ste /
NK020(wa)003:3656: badz+ra a na ya ma h+aa b+h+r+aum ta dz+wa la ya sarba b+hasmi ku ru sarba dush+t+aam h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:3657: ces me lha'i rang sngags kyis mchod yon phul /
NK020(wa)003:3658: g.yas pa'i khu tshur bcas la mtheb mdzub kyis mchod yon gyi snod nas me tog blangs te /
NK020(wa)003:3659: pra w+aa ra sang+k+aa ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3660: zhes bzed zhal du sor mo brkyang bas zhabs bsil phul /
NK020(wa)003:3661: de nas phyag rgya bzhis rgyas gdab ste /
NK020(wa)003:3664: g.yas de bzhin gshegs pa'i khu tshur byas pa'i phyi'i
NK020(wa)003:3665: rdo rje rigs kyi khu tshur gnyis bcings la g.yas
NK020(wa)003:3666: pa'i sor mo rnams me 'bar ba ltar byas te
NK020(wa)003:3667: / badz+ra a na la sogs me lha'i sngags la
NK020(wa)003:3668: dri sh+ya zhes btags pas mdun gyi ye shes pa
NK020(wa)003:3669: / la blta / dzahh+aum bam hohs bstim /
NK020(wa)003:3670: sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes pas rgyab tu zla dkyil 'grub /
NK020(wa)003:3671: sa ma ya s+t+wam a ham zhes pas me lha'i sku gsal bar bsgoms la /
NK020(wa)003:3672: me lha'i sngags lan gsum brjod do //
NK020(wa)003:3674: lce la rdo rje dkar po'i lte bar dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:3677: snying gar a las sna tshogs rdo rje bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:3678: gar sngon 'gro'i phyag chen phyag mtshan med pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:3680: snying gar h+aum las zla ba'i rdo rje ba sam
NK020(wa)003:3681: la gar med pa'i phyag chen phyag mtshan can no
NK020(wa)003:3682: // de nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:3683: rdo rje rin chen gyi rgya bcing zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3684: badz+ra rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK020(wa)003:3685: zhes pas rdo rje rin po che'i cod pan dang /
NK020(wa)003:3686: trum gyis dar dpyang gi dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)003:3687: rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)003:3688: ha na sa ma ya h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:3689: ces pas dam la bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)003:3690: ag+ne de wa sa pa ri w+aa ra pu sh+pe pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa nas /
NK020(wa)003:3692: badz+ra l+aa s+ya h+aum nas gan+d+he ah'i bar gyi sngags rgyas sgeg sogs brgyad phul /
NK020(wa)003:3693: de nas byang chub mchog rgyas dgang blugs bzung la /
NK020(wa)003:3694: me lha cung zad 'dzum pa'i ljags la ram dang
NK020(wa)003:3695: dgang blugs kyi kha la h+aum gis mtshan par bsam
NK020(wa)003:3697: zhes mngar gsum bsreg pa'i mar blugs gzar gsum gyis
NK020(wa)003:3698: dgang gzar bkang la kha sbyar te lag gnyis pus
NK020(wa)003:3700: na mah sa m+aan+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ag+na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3701: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i nad gdon
NK020(wa)003:3702: sdig sgrib thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol s+w+aa
NK020(wa)003:3703: h+aa / zhes lan gsum dbul lo //
NK020(wa)003:3704: de nas rdzas rnams rim par 'bul te /
NK020(wa)003:3707: gzi brjid phun sum tshogs pa la bar du gcod pa thams cad sh+aa n+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3710: 'byor pa phun sum tshogs pa til nag /
NK020(wa)003:3711: sarba p+aa pam da ha na badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3712: sdig sgrib thams cad sh+aan+tim til dkar ram yungs kar /
NK020(wa)003:3714: dngos grub phun sum tshogs pa la bar du gcod pa zho zan /
NK020(wa)003:3716: bde ba phun sum tshogs pa la 'bras /
NK020(wa)003:3718: bsod nams phun sum tshogs pa la so ba /
NK020(wa)003:3719: badz+ra bi dz+aa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3720: nor dang 'bru phun sum tshogs pa la nas /
NK020(wa)003:3721: ma h+aa be g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3722: shugs phun sum tshogs pa la sran ma /
NK020(wa)003:3723: ma h+aa ba l+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3724: stobs phun sum tshogs pa la gro /
NK020(wa)003:3725: badz+ra g+ha sma ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3726: nad med pa phun sum tshogs pa la durba /
NK020(wa)003:3728: tshe ring ba phun sum tshogs tshogs pa la ku sha /
NK020(wa)003:3729: a pra ti ha ta badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:3730: bsrung ba phun sum tshogs pa la zhe rdzas re re bzhin lan gsum phul la /
NK020(wa)003:3731: las sngags kyis bsang gtor phul bas /
NK020(wa)003:3732: me lha nyid 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:3733: de nas 'das pa'i me lha mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:3734: rdo rje khu tshur kha sbyar la mgal me ltar bskor zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3735: badz+ra he tu bam zhes brjod pas thab kyi me'i
NK020(wa)003:3736: dbus su gzhal yas khang lha so so'i gdan dang
NK020(wa)003:3738: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyi sngags zlos shing /
NK020(wa)003:3739: me tog gis mtshon par spyan drangs la thab tu me tog skyur bas /
NK020(wa)003:3740: lha thams cad gzhal yas khang gi gnas so sor bzhugs par gyur pa la /
NK020(wa)003:3741: sarba ta th+aa ga ta push+pe p+au dza me g+ha
NK020(wa)003:3742: sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum
NK020(wa)003:3743: / de bzhin du push+pe'i gnas su d+h+au pe /
NK020(wa)003:3748: badz+ra zhes thams cad kyi 'gor sbyar te /
NK020(wa)003:3751: g+ai ti h+r+aih n+ri t+ye a /
NK020(wa)003:3755: zhes pa rnams kyis mchod la /
NK020(wa)003:3756: chos dbyings ye shes rnam par dag /
NK020(wa)003:3758: sa gnas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)003:3759: zhes pa'i bar sgrub thabs kyi bum bskyed ltar gyis bstod /
NK020(wa)003:3760: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi zhal cung
NK020(wa)003:3761: zad 'dzum pa'i ljags dang dgang blugs kyi kha la
NK020(wa)003:3762: yig gis mtshan par bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:3763: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ri h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:3764: zhes pa gsum gyis dgang gzar bkang la /
NK020(wa)003:3766: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i nad gdon
NK020(wa)003:3767: sdig sgrib thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol s+w+aa
NK020(wa)003:3768: h+aa / zhes btags pas dgang blugs gsum mam bdun phul nas /
NK020(wa)003:3769: lag mchod sbyin gyi rgyas yam shing nas ku sha'i
NK020(wa)003:3770: bar rdzas thams cad bshad ma thag pa'i snying po
NK020(wa)003:3771: spel tshig dang bcas pa brgya rtsa sogs ci 'byor
NK020(wa)003:3772: dbul zhing / yang na yam shing /
NK020(wa)003:3775: ku sha rnams ma gtogs pa phyogs gcig tu bsres nas phul kyang rung ngo //
NK020(wa)003:3776: mthar sngar bzhin dgang blugs phul la /
NK020(wa)003:3777: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi thugs ka nas byung
NK020(wa)003:3778: ba'i bdud rtsi dkar po'i chu rgyun gyis bsgrub bya
NK020(wa)003:3779: rnams la dbang bskur bas lus thams cad gang nad
NK020(wa)003:3780: gdon sdig sgrib thams cad dag par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:3781: de nas nyer spyod lnga dang /
NK020(wa)003:3782: tam+bu l+aa ya s+w+aa h+aas so rtsi /
NK020(wa)003:3783: badz+ra wastra ye s+w+aa h+aas na bza' /
NK020(wa)003:3787: yig brgyas nongs pa bzod par gsol nas /
NK020(wa)003:3788: sngar bzhin lha rnams me tog gis spyan drangs te
NK020(wa)003:3789: dkyil 'khor du rang rang so so'i gnas su bzhugs
NK020(wa)003:3790: par bsam mo // gal te dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod dang ma 'brel na /
NK020(wa)003:3791: 'jig rten pa'i me lha'i 'bar ba'i rnam par sgyur
NK020(wa)003:3792: rjes rdo rje 'khor lo'i sngags rgyas rten dang brten
NK020(wa)003:3793: par bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par sprul la /
NK020(wa)003:3794: rdo rje bsdu ba'i sngags rgyas ye shes pa spyan 'dren nas dbang gi bar sgrub thabs ltar dang /
NK020(wa)003:3795: mchod bstod byon skyems nas nongs pa bzod par gsol ba'i bar bshad ma thag pa ltar byas rjes //
NK020(wa)003:3796: khyed kyi sems can sogs kyis bskul nas /
NK020(wa)003:3797: badz+ra sa t+wa muhs phyag rgya bkrol te gshegs su gsol ba rnams khyad par ro //
NK020(wa)003:3798: slar yang ag+na ye dz+wa la ram zhes mar khu phul bas /
NK020(wa)003:3799: me lha sngar bzhin gsal bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:3800: sreg rdzas rnams dang dgang blugs gsum sngar ltar phul nas /
NK020(wa)003:3801: nyer spyod dang sgeg sogs kyis mchod //
NK020(wa)003:3802: so rtsi dang na bza' dbul /
NK020(wa)003:3803: 'jig rten dbang phyug tshangs dbang mgon gyi sras //
NK020(wa)003:3804: me lha'i rgyal po tak+kisa dbang bskur ba //
NK020(wa)003:3805: shes rab mchog gis nyon mongs thams cad bsreg /
NK020(wa)003:3806: 'dzin byed me lha nyid la rnam par 'dud //
NK020(wa)003:3808: gtor ma rdo rje gnod sbyin dang me'i sngags rgyas bsang sbyangs /
NK020(wa)003:3810: ag+ne la a k+aa ro btags pas phul la /
NK020(wa)003:3811: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di zhes la /
NK020(wa)003:3814: badz+ra sa t+wa muh zhes phyag rgya bkrol te gshegs su gsol /
NK020(wa)003:3815: de nas sbyin sreg brkyang par byed tshe /
NK020(wa)003:3816: bdag bskyed gshegs bsdu bdag nyid bsrung ba rnams sgrub
NK020(wa)003:3817: thabs ltar byas rjes me rang zhi 'am 'o mas
NK020(wa)003:3818: gzhil / las rjes mi mngon par bsdu'o //
NK020(wa)003:3819: yo ga'i zhi rkyang gi sbyin sreg gi cho ga'o //
NK020(wa)003:3822: da ni gnyis pa 'dus pa mdo'i sbyin sreg la bzhi ste /
NK020(wa)003:3826: ji ltar bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK020(wa)003:3828: spyir rnal 'byor pa gang zhig rgyal ba rnams mnyes par bya ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:3829: sdig sgrib sbyong zhing nyams chag skong ba sogs rang
NK020(wa)003:3830: gzhan gyi don gnyis myur du 'grub byed kyi phrin
NK020(wa)003:3831: las rmad du byung ba ni sbyin sreg gi las
NK020(wa)003:3833: rdo rje me yi las mchog 'dis //
NK020(wa)003:3834: rnal 'byor thabs su bde sbyar bas //
NK020(wa)003:3835: rgyal ba kun mnyes kun sreg skongs //
NK020(wa)003:3836: don grub las kyi mchog tu bshad //
NK020(wa)003:3838: bye brag tu don bya ba'i yul gud du phye na /
NK020(wa)003:3840: nad dang sdug bsngal zhi ba dang //
NK020(wa)003:3841: tshe dang longs spyod rgyas pa dang //
NK020(wa)003:3842: btsan dregs gzungs ma dbang byed dang //
NK020(wa)003:3843: dgra bgegs gdug pa tshar gcod pa //
NK020(wa)003:3844: dgos ched 'bras bur bshad pa yin //
NK020(wa)003:3845: zhes gang la bya ba'i yul bzhi la ltas nas
NK020(wa)003:3846: 'phrin las bzhi'i dbye bas de dang de'i don grub
NK020(wa)003:3849: spyir zhi rgyas gnyis bkra shis pa'i gnas dang /
NK020(wa)003:3850: dbang drag gnyis gnyan pa'i gnas su bya ba shis la /
NK020(wa)003:3852: gangs 'dabs dang ni chu gling dang //
NK020(wa)003:3853: nags tshal sman ljongs me tog tshal //
NK020(wa)003:3854: phug dang grog mdo 'jigs pa dang //
NK020(wa)003:3855: dur khrod shing gcig rmangs pa'i khyim //
NK020(wa)003:3856: zhes rkang pa re res zhi rgyas dbang drag gi gnas rim par bstan no //
NK020(wa)003:3859: dbyar dang ston dang dgun dang dpyid //
NK020(wa)003:3860: snga dro gung dang dgong ka dang //
NK020(wa)003:3861: nam gung rnams ni dus yin no //
NK020(wa)003:3862: zhes pas lo re dang zhag re la ltos pa'i
NK020(wa)003:3863: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi dus rim par bstan cing
NK020(wa)003:3864: / zla ba re la ltos na dkar phyogs la
NK020(wa)003:3865: zhi rgyas dang nag phyogs la dbang drag gi las
NK020(wa)003:3866: shis pas spyir de dag gis dus dang /
NK020(wa)003:3867: khyad par nad zhi bar 'dod pa sogs las de dang des don bya ba'i dus so //
NK020(wa)003:3868: bzhi pa ji ltar bya ba'i rim pa la /
NK020(wa)003:3874: gzugs brnyan gyi hom ste lnga las /
NK020(wa)003:3875: 'dir gzugs brnyan gyi hom la brten nas las bzhi sgrub par byed pa la gsum ste /
NK020(wa)003:3876: sbyor ba las bzhi'i bshams bkod thun mong du bshad pa /
NK020(wa)003:3877: dngos gzhi cho ga'i las rim so sor bshad pa /
NK020(wa)003:3878: rjes las bzhi thun mong du bstan pas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK020(wa)003:3881: las bzhi so so'i khyad par gyis //
NK020(wa)003:3882: phyogs dang kha dog dbyibs dang rdzas /
NK020(wa)003:3883: ji ltar yin pa de ltar sbyar //
NK020(wa)003:3889: dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod dang ma 'brel pa'i sbyin sreg
NK020(wa)003:3890: rkyang sgrub kyi tshe shar phyogs skyong ba'i lha dbang
NK020(wa)003:3891: pos mi mthun pa'i phyogs zhi bar byed pa la
NK020(wa)003:3892: sogs pa'i khyad par gyis 'jig rten pa'i phyogs dang
NK020(wa)003:3893: mthun par zhi ba la shar /
NK020(wa)003:3894: rgyas pa la byang dbang la nub /
NK020(wa)003:3895: drag po la lhor kha blta zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3896: yang sgrub mchod dang 'brel tshe dkyil 'khor gyi sgo
NK020(wa)003:3897: bzhi po las so so la shis pas dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)003:3898: gyi phyogs dang mthun par byas te /
NK020(wa)003:3899: dkyil 'khor gyi shar du zhi ba /
NK020(wa)003:3902: byang du drag po'i thab bcas la kha dkyil 'khor la phyogs pas blta ba'o //
NK020(wa)003:3903: gnyis pa thab kyi dbyibs mdog ni /
NK020(wa)003:3906: mthing ga'am nag po thal mdog sbyar //
NK020(wa)003:3907: zlum po pad+ma le tshe zhi //
NK020(wa)003:3908: 'khor lo gru bzhi zur brgyad rgyas //
NK020(wa)003:3909: zla gam gru chad gzhu dbyibs dbang //
NK020(wa)003:3910: gru gsum b+ha ga kha mngon spyod //
NK020(wa)003:3911: sum brtseg mdangs dang ri mor mdzes //
NK020(wa)003:3912: zhes pa'i drag po'i kha ni khro zhal te las
NK020(wa)003:3913: bzhi ka la thab bya tshul gsum gsum bshad kyang
NK020(wa)003:3914: / da lta phyag bzhes su mdzad pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:3916: zhi ba la ni zlum po ste /
NK020(wa)003:3917: rgyas pa'i thab khung gru bzhi pa //
NK020(wa)003:3918: dbang gi dkyil 'khor zla gam la //
NK020(wa)003:3919: drag po e ste mkha' 'dra'i dbyibs //
NK020(wa)003:3921: rdo rje yis ni rnam par brgyan //
NK020(wa)003:3922: zhes gsungs pa ltar stegs bu gru bzhi pa ngos
NK020(wa)003:3923: re la khru do dang dpangs su khru phyed pa
NK020(wa)003:3924: rtsig gam ma brtsigs kyang rung ste /
NK020(wa)003:3925: gzhi der dri dang ba byung gis chag chag btab pa la /
NK020(wa)003:3926: thab khung zhi ba la zlum po dkar po /
NK020(wa)003:3927: rgyas pa la gru bzhi ser po /
NK020(wa)003:3928: dbang la zla gam dmar po /
NK020(wa)003:3929: drag po la gru gsum nag po ste /
NK020(wa)003:3930: thams cad kyang rgyar khru gang dang dpangs su khru phyed pa /
NK020(wa)003:3931: kha khyer bang rim gsum gyi nang ma la 'od phreng las dang mthun pa'i kha dog can /
NK020(wa)003:3932: bar ma la zhi bar lcags kyu dkar po /
NK020(wa)003:3933: rgyas par zhags pa ser po /
NK020(wa)003:3934: dbang la lcags sgrog dmar po /
NK020(wa)003:3935: drag por dril bu sngon po /
NK020(wa)003:3936: tha ma la zhi bar 'khor lo dkar po /
NK020(wa)003:3937: rgyas par rin chen ser po /
NK020(wa)003:3939: drag por rdo rje sngon po rtse gsum rwa gdengs pa'i phreng bas bskor zhing /
NK020(wa)003:3940: thab kyi dbus su mtshan ma dgod pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:3941: zhi ba la 'khor lo dkar po'i lte bar /
NK020(wa)003:3942: rgyas pa la rin po che ser por t+r+aam /
NK020(wa)003:3943: dbang la pad+ma dmar por h+r+aih drag por rdo rje sngon po h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK020(wa)003:3944: thams cad kyang sor bzhi pa'i tshad can no //
NK020(wa)003:3945: thab kyi nang du 'chad 'gyur yam shing gi rgyu
NK020(wa)003:3946: dang rigs 'dra'i las mthun gyi bud shing thab dbyib
NK020(wa)003:3947: dang 'dra ba dpangs su mtho gang ba rtsigs pa'i
NK020(wa)003:3948: shar lho'i phyogs su me tshang bca' /
NK020(wa)003:3949: stegs bu'i grwa bzhir mda' las mthun gyi kha dog
NK020(wa)003:3950: can bzhi rang mdog can gyi zhags pa'i srad bu
NK020(wa)003:3951: bzhis sbrel ba'i tshul du dngos su 'god pa'am ri
NK020(wa)003:3952: mor bri zhing / steng du me dar dgab bo //
NK020(wa)003:3953: rang gi g.yas phyogs su rdzas stegs pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi lte bar zhun mar ni /
NK020(wa)003:3954: zhi rgyas la rtsi mar dang /
NK020(wa)003:3956: drag po la tshil zhun dang sbyar ba'i mar nag rnams dang dgang blugs /
NK020(wa)003:3957: mdun gyi pad 'dab la yam shing ni /
NK020(wa)003:3959: las bzhi'i shing ni rtse mo /
NK020(wa)003:3964: zhes gsungs pa ltar zhi ba la tsan+dana dkar po
NK020(wa)003:3965: dang bal bu sogs dkar zhing lo ma can gyi
NK020(wa)003:3966: rtse mo'i cha las byung ba /
NK020(wa)003:3967: rgyas pa la 'bras bu chags pa dang ser zhing
NK020(wa)003:3968: 'o ma can gyi yal ga'i cha las byung ba
NK020(wa)003:3969: / dbang la tsan+dana dmar po dang mdzo mo shing
NK020(wa)003:3970: sogs dmar ba dang skyur ba'i shing gi sdong po'i
NK020(wa)003:3972: drag po la dug shing dang tsher ma can nag cing rtsa ba'i cha las byung ba /
NK020(wa)003:3973: thams cad kyang mtho gang ba rang gi las mthun gyi mar khur rtse gnyis nyugs pa bkod /
NK020(wa)003:3974: pad 'dab lhag ma bdun la sreg rdzas gzhan rnams las mthun gyi snod du rim par bsham ste /
NK020(wa)003:3975: de la so so'i sreg rdzas ni /
NK020(wa)003:3977: zho dang 'bras til nas dkar chan /
NK020(wa)003:3978: mar gsar 'o ma zhi la sbyar /
NK020(wa)003:3980: zhi ba la til dkar nag dang /
NK020(wa)003:3982: nas dkar dang 'bras dkar gyi chan sogs kha zas dkar po dang /
NK020(wa)003:3983: tsan+dana dkar po sogs dri dkar po'i rigs dang /
NK020(wa)003:3984: tsam pa ka sogs me tog dkar po'i rigs rnams bsham /
NK020(wa)003:3985: rgyas pa la mngar gsum dang /
NK020(wa)003:3990: rgun 'brum star kha sogs 'bras bu'i rigs dang /
NK020(wa)003:3993: durba sogs rang bzhin gyis ser ba'am bcom pas ser por byas pa bkod /
NK020(wa)003:3994: dbang la ut+pala dmar po sogs me tog dang /
NK020(wa)003:3995: tsan+da dmar po sogs dri bzang zhing dmar ba'i rigs dang /
NK020(wa)003:3996: skyur ba'i shing dang 'bru 'bras kyi rigs /
NK020(wa)003:3998: shangs rtse ske tshe tsha ba'i mar sogs rang bzhin
NK020(wa)003:3999: nam rgya skeg gis kha dog dmar por sgyur la
NK020(wa)003:4000: bkod / drag po la dug dang tshil chen dang /
NK020(wa)003:4004: nim pa dang lan tsh+wa sogs rtsub pa'i rigs rnams
NK020(wa)003:4005: rang bzhin nam bcos pas nag por byas la bsham
NK020(wa)003:4006: mo // rang gi g.yon phyogs su mchod stegs pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi lte bar las gtor 'god de /
NK020(wa)003:4007: zhi ba la dngul phye dang 'bras phye me tog
NK020(wa)003:4008: dkar po rnams 'o ma dang sbyar ba'i gtor ma
NK020(wa)003:4009: dkar zlum / rgyas pa la gser phye dang me
NK020(wa)003:4010: tog ser po gro dang rgun 'bru'i phye rdong ros
NK020(wa)003:4011: dang bcas pa zho dang sbyar ba'i gtor ma gru
NK020(wa)003:4012: dkar zlum / bzhi ser po / dbang la zangs
NK020(wa)003:4013: phye bu ram pad rag rnams 'bras dmar dang ram
NK020(wa)003:4014: bu'i phye dang sbyar ba'i gtor ma zla gam dmar
NK020(wa)003:4015: dkar zlum / bzhi ser po / po / drag
NK020(wa)003:4016: po la lcags phye dug rdo'i phye ma rnams mi'am
NK020(wa)003:4017: khyi'i 'o ma dang ra khrag 'bru nag gi chan
NK020(wa)003:4018: dang sbyar ba'i gtor ma gru gsum nag po /
NK020(wa)003:4019: bzhi ka la mthe' kyus gcer ba'o //
NK020(wa)003:4021: de'i g.yas g.yon gyi 'dab mar sman raka /
NK020(wa)003:4022: 'dab ma lhag ma lnga la las mthun gyi rgyu
NK020(wa)003:4023: dang kha dog bsgyur ba'i zhabs bsil dang bzhi bsnol
NK020(wa)003:4025: rang gi mdun du las bzhi'i brub khung thab khung dang dbyibs mdog 'dra ba'i nang du /
NK020(wa)003:4026: bsgrub bya'i yul gang yin gyi mi'i zag rdzas sam rkang rjes dang /
NK020(wa)003:4027: mi ma yin gyi gnas rten gyi sa la rgyu
NK020(wa)003:4028: byas pa'i lid+ga pho mo gang yin gyi mtshan ma
NK020(wa)003:4029: can bzos pa'i dpral bar rus /
NK020(wa)003:4030: snying gar srog ming yig dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)003:4032: 'doms su las bzhi gang yin gyi spu gri ni che ge sh+aa n+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:4033: push+thim ku ru w+aa sham ku ru hoh m+aa ra
NK020(wa)003:4034: ya phata ces pa rnams gro shog la bris te
NK020(wa)003:4035: gnas so sor slan pa rnams bcug /
NK020(wa)003:4037: dngul dang gser dang zangs ma dang //
NK020(wa)003:4038: lcags kyi phur bu basngagasa pa yin //
NK020(wa)003:4039: zhes sam las kyi kha dog dang rjes su mthun pa'i shing la'ang rung ste /
NK020(wa)003:4040: zhi ba la phur bu dbal zlum po can drug /
NK020(wa)003:4041: rgyas par gru bzhi pa bzhi /
NK020(wa)003:4043: drag po la gru gsum pa gsum ste /
NK020(wa)003:4044: thams cad kyi mgo bo rgya mdud can rnams rang
NK020(wa)003:4045: rang gi brub khung gi kha khyer la bkod cing
NK020(wa)003:4046: / sgrol gri sogs nye bar mkho ba'i yo byad thams cad tshang zhing 'du bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:4047: gnyis pa dngos gzhi cho ga'i las rim so sor bshad pa la /
NK020(wa)003:4048: sgrub mchod dang 'brel na bdag bskyed logs su mi dgos na'ang /
NK020(wa)003:4049: sbyin sreg rkyang chog gi tshe zhi khro lus dkyil
NK020(wa)003:4050: la bkod pa'i cho ga zhi thung khro thung gang
NK020(wa)003:4051: rigs sam / yang na zhi rgyas la zhi ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4052: dbang drag la khro bor brten pa shis la /
NK020(wa)003:4053: gang ltar yang dzapa kyi tshe las dang mthun pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4054: 'od zer spro bsdus las de dang des rang gzhan
NK020(wa)003:4055: gyi don byas par bsam pa ni khyad par ro
NK020(wa)003:4056: // de yang rten dang brten pa lus dkyil gyi
NK020(wa)003:4057: lha rnams bsdus te rang nyid gzhi lus kyi rnam
NK020(wa)003:4058: par gnas pas sbyin sreg la 'jug pa'am /
NK020(wa)003:4059: yang na sngon 'gro zhi thung ltar las /
NK020(wa)003:4060: dngos gzhi'i tshe dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med
NK020(wa)003:4061: pa'i byang chub kyi sems nyid rang rang gi bskyed
NK020(wa)003:4065: dbang la pad+ma he ru ka /
NK020(wa)003:4066: drag po la badz+ra he ru ka rnams yum bcas te /
NK020(wa)003:4067: phyag rgya gcig pa'i lha bsgoms la /
NK020(wa)003:4068: rang rigs bdag por byas pas dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)003:4075: las mthun gyi 'od zer spro bsdus rang sngags kyi
NK020(wa)003:4076: bzlas pa byas rjes sbyin sreg la 'jug pa yin
NK020(wa)003:4077: no // de ltar nges par byas nas cho ga'i las rim la bzhi ste /
NK020(wa)003:4083: // dang po zhi ba'i sbyin sreg ni /
NK020(wa)003:4084: chas gos dkar po gyon nas rdo rje skyil krung
NK020(wa)003:4085: gis zhi zhing dang ba'i sems dang ldan pas shis
NK020(wa)003:4086: pa'i phyogs su kha bltas te /
NK020(wa)003:4087: bdag bskyed bzlas pa'i bar byas la /
NK020(wa)003:4088: las bum gyi chu'am bdud rtsi gtor bas las gtor dang sreg rdzas rnams bsang sbyangs //
NK020(wa)003:4089: stong pa'i ngang las ma a zhes brjod pas nyi
NK020(wa)003:4090: zla ga'u'i snod du rang gi thugs ka nas a
NK020(wa)003:4091: dkar po spros pa 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su
NK020(wa)003:4092: gyur pa las byung ba'i las gtor rin po che'i
NK020(wa)003:4093: mchod sdong 'od zer dkar po 'phro ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4094: bsreg rdzas rnams zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi
NK020(wa)003:4095: ro brgya ldan pa nam mkha' rab 'byams gang bas
NK020(wa)003:4096: zhi ba'i las sgrub pa la thogs pa med pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4097: nus pa dang ldan par byin gyis brlab /
NK020(wa)003:4098: de nas tshogs mchod kyi mchod bshags yan chad song ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4099: tha ma stob pa ni brub khung gi nya bo mdun du bkod la /
NK020(wa)003:4100: a ram bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:4101: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK020(wa)003:4102: phyi snod zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor chu shes gyi rang
NK020(wa)003:4103: bzhin can dkar zlum yangs pa 'od zer 'phro ba'i
NK020(wa)003:4104: dbus su nang bcud bud+d+ha rigs kyis gtso byas pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4105: khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor sprul pa'i 'od zer
NK020(wa)003:4106: dkar po 'phro ba'i skur bzhengs par bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4108: bsgrub bya che ge mo mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:4109: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahdzahh+aum bam hoh zhes bkug cing bstim la /
NK020(wa)003:4111: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK020(wa)003:4113: yud tsam gyis ni zhi mdzad nas //
NK020(wa)003:4114: zhi ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:4115: ces bskul bas lha tshogs rnams zhi ba'i las mdzad pa la dgyes par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:4116: de nas las gtor nas lag gnyis kyi mtheb mdzub
NK020(wa)003:4117: kyis gtor kyu blangs la g.yas g.yon du bskor zhing
NK020(wa)003:4118: // dngul dang 'bras chan dkar po rnams //
NK020(wa)003:4119: 'o mas sbyar ba'i gtor ma ni //
NK020(wa)003:4120: gang la dmigs te bskor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:4121: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams zhi bar 'gyur //
NK020(wa)003:4122: ma h+aa ba lim ta sarba du sh+tan sh+aan+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:4124: de nas zhi ba'i phur bu drug po thal mo'i bar du bzung la /
NK020(wa)003:4125: bud+d+ha k+ai li k+ai la ya phata dzahzhesa pas rang gi thugs ka nas bud+d+ha k+ai la ya spros /
NK020(wa)003:4126: phur bu la thim pas sras mchog bud+d+ha k+ai la yar gyur pa la /
NK020(wa)003:4127: +aa dar+sha thog mar byas pas dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)003:4129: phur bu kha dog dkar po yi //
NK020(wa)003:4130: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zlum por //
NK020(wa)003:4131: lha rnams bkod de gdab par bya //
NK020(wa)003:4133: bud+d+ha k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pam sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:4135: g+h+aa t+aa'i sngags kyis yan lag lnga dang snying la gdab /
NK020(wa)003:4136: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer dkar po 'phros /
NK020(wa)003:4137: dmigs bya la phog pas dug lnga ye shes lngar sbyangs /
NK020(wa)003:4138: dwangs ma bde chen byang chub sems kyi ngo bor spar /
NK020(wa)003:4139: tshe rten 'od zer gyi rnam par 'dus pa bdag
NK020(wa)003:4140: gi rdo rje'i tshe srog dang dbyer med du gyur
NK020(wa)003:4141: par mos la snying ga'i phur bu gdon /
NK020(wa)003:4142: badz+ra t+aik+sh+n+aa mum zhes gri 'jam dpal gyi ngo bor gyur pa thogs te /
NK020(wa)003:4143: sarba dush+t+aana sarba p+aa pam sh+aan+tinga ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)003:4144: zhes bsgrub bya pho yin na rkang pa g.yas pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4145: mthe bong dang mo yin na g.yon pa'i mthe chung
NK020(wa)003:4147: ling ro cha gsum du bgos te /
NK020(wa)003:4148: gcig mchod gtor la bran cing bdud rtsi gtor la /
NK020(wa)003:4149: ma h+aa ba ling+ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)003:4151: tsho gcig sreg rdzas rnams la bsre /
NK020(wa)003:4152: tsho gcig bro gdan gyi phyir brub khung nyid du bzhag go //
NK020(wa)003:4153: de nas sbyin sreg dngos ni /
NK020(wa)003:4154: rang nyid sngar bdag bskyed gang yin der nga rgyal 'phos la /
NK020(wa)003:4155: thog mar 'jig rten pa'i me lha mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:4158: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum zhes brjod pas mdun du
NK020(wa)003:4159: zhi ba'i thab khung dkar zhing zlum pa kha khyer
NK020(wa)003:4160: bang rim gsum dang ldan pa 'od zer dkar po
NK020(wa)003:4161: 'phro bar gyur / rang gi thugs ka nas ram
NK020(wa)003:4162: yig thab nang du spros pa las ye shes kyi
NK020(wa)003:4163: me 'od dkar por 'bar bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4164: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:4165: ces pas rgyal rigs sam dge bdun gyi rgyun bzhag
NK020(wa)003:4166: gi me'am rtsub shing las byung ba'i me du ba
NK020(wa)003:4168: thab kyi me'i dbus su nyi ma dang ra skyes
NK020(wa)003:4169: kyi gdan la ag+ne de wa ri shi h+aum zhes
NK020(wa)003:4170: brjod pas zhi ba'i me lha dkar po drang srong
NK020(wa)003:4171: gi chas can gun+d+he dang bgrang phreng 'dzin pa gsal
NK020(wa)003:4172: bar gyur / a dar+sha sogs kyis bskur brlab /
NK020(wa)003:4173: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas shar
NK020(wa)003:4174: lho nas me lha 'khor bcas bzhengs par bsam la
NK020(wa)003:4175: / ag+na ye de wa sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes se gol bsnol mar gdab /
NK020(wa)003:4176: mda' dar dmar po g.yab cing /
NK020(wa)003:4178: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)003:4179: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po che //
NK020(wa)003:4180: me lha drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK020(wa)003:4181: 'di nyid du ni gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:4183: ag+ne de wi ri shi dzahdzahsa spyan drangs la /
NK020(wa)003:4184: dzahh+aum bam hoh sa bstim pa la /
NK020(wa)003:4185: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK020(wa)003:4187: bde gshegs rigs las grub pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:4188: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK020(wa)003:4189: phrin las kun gyi dpang po mdzad //
NK020(wa)003:4192: me lha zhal cung zad gdangs pas sregs blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun drangs nas gsol bar mos la /
NK020(wa)003:4193: lag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i khu tshur gnyis su byas pas gzar bu bzung la /
NK020(wa)003:4196: zhes g.yas kyi blugs gzar bdun gyis g.yon gyi dgang
NK020(wa)003:4197: gzar bkang rjes gzar bu kha sbyar te pus mo'i
NK020(wa)003:4198: nang las mi 'da' bas g.yas su bskor zhing /
NK020(wa)003:4199: ag+ne de wa ri shi ha bya ka bya di
NK020(wa)003:4200: bya ma h+aa na ye di bya bdag cag dpon
NK020(wa)003:4201: slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i nad gdon sdig sgrib bar
NK020(wa)003:4202: chad mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru
NK020(wa)003:4203: s+w+aa h+aa / zhes lan gsum gyis dgang blugs phul /
NK020(wa)003:4204: sngags de kho nas thog mar yam shing dang mar khu /
NK020(wa)003:4205: de nas sreg rdzas rnams so so'am gcig tu bsres
NK020(wa)003:4206: nas phul kyang rung ste grangs ji ltar 'os pa
NK020(wa)003:4208: rig pa'i rgyal po khyod kyis las thams cad byed pas sreg rdzas lha'i zhal du 'bul ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4209: de nyid ye shes kyi mer byin gyis brlabs nas
NK020(wa)003:4210: bdag cag gi phrin las thams cad mdzad du gsol
NK020(wa)003:4212: de nas 'das pa'i me lha mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)003:4213: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na dz+wa la ram zhes brjod pas me
NK020(wa)003:4214: lha nyid thugs rje ye shes me 'bar ba'i rnam
NK020(wa)003:4215: par gyur pa'i klong du b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he
NK020(wa)003:4216: zhes pas gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bkra
NK020(wa)003:4218: h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram
NK020(wa)003:4219: zhes brjod pas steng khang du rnam snang gis gtso
NK020(wa)003:4220: byas pa'i zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi lha bzhi
NK020(wa)003:4222: 'og khang du bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4223: khrag 'thung tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK020(wa)003:4224: tshogs thams cad sku mdog dkar po g.yas 'khor lo
NK020(wa)003:4225: dang / g.yon zhi ba rnams dril bu dang khro
NK020(wa)003:4226: bo rnams dung khrag bsnams pa sku las 'od zer
NK020(wa)003:4227: dkar po'i phreng ba mkha' khyab tu spro ba'i dkyil
NK020(wa)003:4228: 'khor gyi 'khor lor bkra lam gyis gsal bar gyur
NK020(wa)003:4229: dang / / rnam snang bdag por byas pas dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)003:4234: dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod dang 'brel ba'i tshe gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa sngar bzhin bskyed rjes /
NK020(wa)003:4236: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)003:4237: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)003:4238: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK020(wa)003:4239: 'dir gshegs bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:4240: h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo /
NK020(wa)003:4241: dzahh+aum bam hoh e h+ye hi ru lu ru lu
NK020(wa)003:4242: h+aum b+h+yo dzahdzah zhes pas dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK020(wa)003:4243: rnams man+dala me tog gis mtshon par spyan drangs la
NK020(wa)003:4244: / de las me tog thab tu dor bas /
NK020(wa)003:4245: lha thams cad gzhal yas khang gi gnas so sor
NK020(wa)003:4246: rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs par bsam pa tsam
NK020(wa)003:4247: las bskur rlob sogs mi dgos so //
NK020(wa)003:4248: sgrub mchod dang 'brel ma 'brel gang ltar yang /
NK020(wa)003:4252: brjod med shes rab kyis bstod /
NK020(wa)003:4253: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje 'od
NK020(wa)003:4254: kyi sbu gu can gyis bsregs blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK020(wa)003:4255: rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4256: dzi na dzika zhes bdun gyis bkang ba'i dgang blugs sbyar ba sngar bzhin du /
NK020(wa)003:4257: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum gi mthar /
NK020(wa)003:4258: bdag cag dpon slob sogs spel tshig sngar ltar btags pas lan gsum phul /
NK020(wa)003:4259: de nas sngags de nyid kyis yam shing dang mar
NK020(wa)003:4260: khu sngon du 'gro ba'i sreg rdzas rnams brgya rtsa
NK020(wa)003:4261: sogs ji ltar rigs pa phul nas /
NK020(wa)003:4262: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa his bdud rtsi /
NK020(wa)003:4263: las gtor las gtor kyu blangs te /
NK020(wa)003:4264: ma h+aa ba lim ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa his gtor ma /
NK020(wa)003:4265: ma h+aa rak+ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa his rak+ta phul la //
NK020(wa)003:4266: klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK020(wa)003:4267: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:4268: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas rnams kyi //
NK020(wa)003:4269: nad gdon sdig sgrib kun zhi nas //
NK020(wa)003:4270: mchog thun dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:4271: zhes gsol ba btab pas lha tshogs rnams kyi sku
NK020(wa)003:4272: las 'od zer dkar po bdud rtsi'i rgyun lta bu
NK020(wa)003:4273: 'phros pas bsgrub bya'i nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad
NK020(wa)003:4275: de nas btang rag gi mchod bstod dang bzod gsol byas la /
NK020(wa)003:4276: dkyil 'khor dang 'brel tshe sngar ltar me tog gis
NK020(wa)003:4277: spyan drangs te dkyil 'khor du so so'i gnas su
NK020(wa)003:4278: bzhugs par bsam / ma 'brel na dz+ny+aa na man+da
NK020(wa)003:4279: la badz+ra muh zhes ye shes pa gshegs su gsol
NK020(wa)003:4280: bzhugs par bsam / / dam tshig pa rang la thim par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:4282: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:4283: ces blugs gzar gyi mar khus me gsos /
NK020(wa)003:4284: 'jig rten pa'i me lha sngar bzhin gsal bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4285: sreg rdzas lhag ma rnams phul /
NK020(wa)003:4287: las gtor nas gtor kyu blangs te /
NK020(wa)003:4288: ag+ne de ba ri shi ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa his gtor ma phul la 'dod don gsol /
NK020(wa)003:4290: badz+ra muhs me lha ye shes pa rang gnas su gshegs /
NK020(wa)003:4291: dam tshig pa 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:4292: gnyis pa rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg ni /
NK020(wa)003:4293: ras gos ser po gyon nas mnyam pa'i skyil krung
NK020(wa)003:4294: gis dga' zhing spros ba'i sems dang ldan pas shis
NK020(wa)003:4295: pa'i phyogs su kha bltas te /
NK020(wa)003:4296: bdag bskyed bzlas pa'i bar byas la /
NK020(wa)003:4297: las bum gyi chu'am bdud rtsis las gtor dang sreg rdzas rnams bsang sbyangs /
NK020(wa)003:4298: stong pa'i ngang las ma a zhes brjod pas nyi
NK020(wa)003:4299: zla ga'u'i snod du rang gi thugs ka nas tram
NK020(wa)003:4300: ser po spros pa 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su
NK020(wa)003:4301: gyur pa las byung ba'i las gtor rin po che'i
NK020(wa)003:4302: mchod sdong 'od zer ser po 'phro ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4303: sreg rdzas rnams zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi
NK020(wa)003:4304: ro brgya ldan pa nam mkha' rab 'byams gang bas
NK020(wa)003:4305: rgyas pa'i las 'grub pa la thogs pa med pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4306: nus pa dang ldan par byin gyis brlab /
NK020(wa)003:4307: de nas tshogs mchod kyi mchod bshags yan chad song ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4308: tha ma stobs pa ni brub khung gi nya bo mdun du bkod la /
NK020(wa)003:4310: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:4311: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK020(wa)003:4312: phyi snod rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor gser btso ma'i rang
NK020(wa)003:4313: bzhin can ser po gru bzhi yangs pa 'od zer
NK020(wa)003:4314: 'phro ba'i dbus su nang bcud rat+na rigs kyis gtso
NK020(wa)003:4315: byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor sprul pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4316: 'od zer ser po 'phro ba'i skur bzhengs par bsam
NK020(wa)003:4318: bsgrub bya ch+gee mo mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:4319: badz+ra am ku sha dzahdzahh+aum bam hoh zhes bkug cing bstim la /
NK020(wa)003:4321: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK020(wa)003:4323: yud tsam gyis ni rgyas mdzad nas //
NK020(wa)003:4324: rgyas pa'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:4325: ces bskul ba'i lha tshogs rnams rgyas pa'i las mdzad pa la dgyes par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:4326: de nas las gtor nas lag gnyis kyi mtheb mdzub
NK020(wa)003:4327: kyis gtor kyu blangs pa g.yas g.yon du bskor zhing
NK020(wa)003:4329: ldong ros gro chan gser phye rnams //
NK020(wa)003:4330: zho dang sbyar ba'i gtor ma ni //
NK020(wa)003:4331: gang la dmigs te bskor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:4333: ma h+aa ba lim ta +aa yuhpun+ya ba su dz+ny+aa na push+tim ku ru /
NK020(wa)003:4335: de nas rgyas pa'i phur bu bzhi po thal mo'i bar du bzung la /
NK020(wa)003:4336: rat+na k+ai li k+ai la ya phata dzah ces pas
NK020(wa)003:4337: rang gi thugs ka nas rat+na k+ai la ya spros
NK020(wa)003:4338: / phur bu la thim pas sras mchog rat+na k+ai la yar gyur pa la /
NK020(wa)003:4339: sa ma t+aa sogs kyis dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)003:4342: phur bu kha dog ser po yi //
NK020(wa)003:4343: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse gru bzhi //
NK020(wa)003:4344: lha rnams bkod de gdab par bya //
NK020(wa)003:4346: rat+na k+ai li k+ai la ya +aahyu pun+ya ba su dz+ny+aa na push+tim ku ru /
NK020(wa)003:4348: g+h+aa ta'i sngags kyis dpral mgrin snying lte bzhir gdab /
NK020(wa)003:4349: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK020(wa)003:4350: ser po 'phros dmigs bya la phog pas dug lnga
NK020(wa)003:4352: dwangs ma bde chen byang chub sems kyi ngo bor spar /
NK020(wa)003:4353: tshe rten 'od zer gyi rnam par 'dus pa bdag
NK020(wa)003:4354: gi rdo rje'i tshe srog dang dbyer med du gyur
NK020(wa)003:4355: par mos la snying ga'i phur bu gdon /
NK020(wa)003:4357: zhes gri 'jam dpal gyi ngo bor gyur pa thogs te /
NK020(wa)003:4358: +aa yuhpun+ya ba su dz+ny+aa na push+tim ku ru /
NK020(wa)003:4359: zhes bsgrub bya pho'i rkang g.yas kyi mthe bong dang mo'i g.yon pa'i mathe'u chung nas gtub la /
NK020(wa)003:4360: ling ro cha gsum du byas te /
NK020(wa)003:4362: ma h+aa ba ling+ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa hi zhes pas stob pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:4364: gcig bro gdan gyi phyir bzhag go /
NK020(wa)003:4365: de nas spyin sreg dngos ni /
NK020(wa)003:4366: rang nyid sngar bdag bskyed gang yin der nga rgyal 'phos la /
NK020(wa)003:4368: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum zhes brjod pas mdun du
NK020(wa)003:4369: rgyas pa'i thab khung ser por 'bar bar bsam la
NK020(wa)003:4370: / ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:4371: ces pas rje rigs kyi me'am nor bu las byung ba'i me du ba med pa spar la /
NK020(wa)003:4372: thab kyi me'i dbus su nyi ma dang ra skyes
NK020(wa)003:4373: kyi gdan la ag+ne de wa ri shi h+aum zhes
NK020(wa)003:4374: brjod pas rgyas pa'i me lha ser po drang srog
NK020(wa)003:4375: gi chas can rin po che'i sgrom bu dang bgrang
NK020(wa)003:4377: sa ma t+aa sogs kyis dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)003:4379: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas shar
NK020(wa)003:4380: lho nas me lha 'khor bcas bzhengs par bsam la
NK020(wa)003:4381: / ag+na ye de wa sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes so gol bsnol mar bdab /
NK020(wa)003:4382: mda' dar dmar po g.yab cing /
NK020(wa)003:4384: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)003:4385: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po che //
NK020(wa)003:4386: me lha drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK020(wa)003:4387: 'di nyid du ni gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:4389: ag+ne de wa ri shi dzahdzahsa drangs /
NK020(wa)003:4391: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK020(wa)003:4393: rin chen rigs las grub pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:4394: me lha'i rgyal po drang srog mchog /
NK020(wa)003:4395: phrin las kun gyi dbang po mdzad //
NK020(wa)003:4398: me lha zhal cung zang gdangs pas sregs blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun drangs nas gsol bar mos la /
NK020(wa)003:4399: rin po che'i khu tshur gyis dgang blugs bzung nas mar /
NK020(wa)003:4401: zhes g.yas pa'i blugs gzar bdun gyis g.yon pa'i dgang
NK020(wa)003:4402: gzar bkang rjes gzar bu kha sbyar te pus mo'i
NK020(wa)003:4403: nang las mi 'da' bas g.yas su bskor zhing /
NK020(wa)003:4404: ag+ne de wa ri shi ha bya ka bya di
NK020(wa)003:4405: bya ma h+aa na ye di bya bdag cag dpon
NK020(wa)003:4406: slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i tshe dang bsod nams ye
NK020(wa)003:4407: shes thams cad push+tim ku ru /
NK020(wa)003:4408: zhes lan gsum gyis dgang blugs phul /
NK020(wa)003:4409: sngags des yam shing dang mar khu sngon 'gros sreg
NK020(wa)003:4410: rdzas gzhan rnams so so'am gcig tu bsres nas grangs
NK020(wa)003:4413: rig pa'i rgyal po khyod kyis las thams cad byed pas sreg rdzas lha'i zhal du 'bul ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4414: de nyid ye shes kyi mer byin gyis brlabs nas
NK020(wa)003:4415: bdag cag gi phrin las thams cad mdzad du gsol
NK020(wa)003:4418: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na dz+wa la ram zhes brjod pas me
NK020(wa)003:4419: lha nyid thugs rje ye shes me 'bar ba'i rnam
NK020(wa)003:4420: par gyur pa'i klong du b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he
NK020(wa)003:4421: zhes pas gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bkra
NK020(wa)003:4423: s+w+aa h+aum +aam h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram
NK020(wa)003:4424: zhes brjod pas steng khang du rin 'byung gis gtso
NK020(wa)003:4425: byas pa'i zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi lha bzhi
NK020(wa)003:4426: bcu rtsa gnyis dang 'og khang du ran+ta he ru
NK020(wa)003:4427: kas gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung tshogs chen 'dus pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4428: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad sku mdog ser
NK020(wa)003:4429: po g.yas rin po che dang g.yon zhi ba rnams
NK020(wa)003:4430: dril bu dang khro bo rnams dung khrag bsnams pa
NK020(wa)003:4431: sku las 'od zer ser po'i phreng ba mkha' khyab
NK020(wa)003:4432: tu spro ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bkra lam
NK020(wa)003:4434: sa ma t+aa sogs kyis bskur rlob /
NK020(wa)003:4439: gzhal yas khang gdan bcas sngar bzhin bskyed rjes /
NK020(wa)003:4441: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)003:4442: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)003:4443: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK020(wa)003:4444: 'dir gshegs bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:4445: s+w+aa h+aum +aam h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo dzahh+aum
NK020(wa)003:4446: bam hohe h+ye hi ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo
NK020(wa)003:4447: dzah dzah zhes pas dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams
NK020(wa)003:4448: man+dala me tog gis mtshon par spyan drangs la /
NK020(wa)003:4449: de las me tog thab tu dor bas /
NK020(wa)003:4450: lha thams cad gzhal yas khang gi gnas so sor
NK020(wa)003:4451: rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs par bsam pa tsam
NK020(wa)003:4452: las bskur rlob sogs mi dgos so //
NK020(wa)003:4453: gang ltar yang de nas kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK020(wa)003:4454: brjod med shes rab kyis bstod /
NK020(wa)003:4455: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje 'od
NK020(wa)003:4456: kyi sbu gu can gyis bsregs blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK020(wa)003:4457: rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4458: s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika zhes bdun gyis bkang ba'i dgang blugs sbyang ba sngar ltar /
NK020(wa)003:4459: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na sogs kyi mthar /
NK020(wa)003:4460: bdag cag dpon slob sogs btags pas lan gsum phul nas /
NK020(wa)003:4461: sngags des yam shing mar khu sreg rdzas rnams brgya rtsa sogs ji ltar rigs ba phul la /
NK020(wa)003:4462: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa his bdud rtsi /
NK020(wa)003:4463: las gtor las gtor kyu blangs nas /
NK020(wa)003:4464: ma h+aa ba lim ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kha his gtor ma /
NK020(wa)003:4465: ma h+aa rak+ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa his rak+ta phul la //
NK020(wa)003:4466: klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK020(wa)003:4467: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:4468: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas rnams kyi //
NK020(wa)003:4469: tshe dang bsod nams rgyas gyur nas /
NK020(wa)003:4470: mchog thun dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:4471: zhes gsol ba btab pas lha tshogs rnams kyi sku
NK020(wa)003:4472: las 'od zer gser mdog nyi 'od lta bu 'phros
NK020(wa)003:4473: pas bsgrub bya'i tshe dang bsod nams rgyas par bsam
NK020(wa)003:4474: mo // de nas gtang rag gi mchod bstod dang bzod gsol byas nas /
NK020(wa)003:4475: dkyil 'khor dang 'brel tshe me tog gis spyan drangs te so so'i gnas su bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:4476: ma 'brel na dz+ny+aa na man+da la badz+ra muhs ye
NK020(wa)003:4477: shes pa gshegs dam tshig pa rang la thim par
NK020(wa)003:4479: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:4480: ces blugs gzar gyi mar khus me gsos pas /
NK020(wa)003:4481: 'jig rten pa'i me lha sngar bzhin gsal bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4482: sreg rdzas lhag ma rnams phul /
NK020(wa)003:4484: las gtor nas gtor kyu blangs te /
NK020(wa)003:4485: ag+ne de wa ri shi ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa his gtor ma phul la 'dod don gsol /
NK020(wa)003:4487: badz+ra muhs me lha ye shes pa rang gnas su gshegs /
NK020(wa)003:4488: dam tshig pa 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:4489: gsum pa dbang gi sbyin sreg ni /
NK020(wa)003:4490: chas gos dmar po gyon nas pad+ma'i 'dug stangs kyis
NK020(wa)003:4491: chags shing zhen pa'i shes dang ldan pas shis pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4493: bdag bskyed bzlas pa'i bar byas la /
NK020(wa)003:4494: las bum gyi chu'am bdud rtsis las gtor dang sreg rdzas bsang sbyangs /
NK020(wa)003:4495: stong pa'i ngang las ma a zhes pas nyi zla
NK020(wa)003:4496: ga'u'i snod du rang gi thugs ka nas h+r+aihdamara po
NK020(wa)003:4497: spros pa 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa
NK020(wa)003:4498: las byung ba'i las gtor rin po che'i mchod sdong
NK020(wa)003:4500: sreg rdzas rnams zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi
NK020(wa)003:4501: ro brgya ldan pa nam mkha' rab 'byams gang bas
NK020(wa)003:4502: dbang gi las 'grub pa la thogs pa med pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4503: nus pa dang ldan par brlab /
NK020(wa)003:4504: de nas tshogs mchod kyi mchod bshags yan chad song ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4506: grub khung gi nya bo mdun du bkod la /
NK020(wa)003:4507: wam ram mo pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:4508: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK020(wa)003:4509: phyi snod dbang gi dkyil 'khor pad+ma r+aa ga'i rang
NK020(wa)003:4510: bzhin dmar po zla gam yangs pa 'od zer 'phro
NK020(wa)003:4511: ba'i dbus su nang bcud pad+ma rigs kyis gtso byas
NK020(wa)003:4512: pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor sprul ba'i 'od
NK020(wa)003:4513: zer dmar po 'phro ba'i skur bzhengs par bsam la
NK020(wa)003:4515: bsgrub bya che ge mo mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:4516: badz+ra am ku sha dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes bkug cing bstim la /
NK020(wa)003:4520: yud tsam gyis ni dbang mdzad nas //
NK020(wa)003:4521: dbang gi phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:4522: ces bskul bas lha tshogs rnams dbang gi las mdzad pa la dgyes par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:4523: de nas las gtong nas lag gnyis kyi mtheb mdzub
NK020(wa)003:4524: kyis gtor kyu blangs pa g.yas g.yon du bskor zhing
NK020(wa)003:4525: / h+r+aih zangs phye bu ram 'bras gsar chan //
NK020(wa)003:4526: pad raka sbyar ba'i gtor ma ni //
NK020(wa)003:4527: gang la dmigs te bskor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:4528: dregs pa'i tshogs rnams dbang du 'gyur //
NK020(wa)003:4529: ma h+aa ba lim ta sarba lo ka p+aa sham ku ru hoh zhes ling+ga'i steng du brab /

NK020(wa)003:4536: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK020(wa)003:4537: lha rnams bkod de gdab par bya //
NK020(wa)003:4539: pad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba lo ka p+aa sham ku ru hoh zhes dang /
NK020(wa)003:4540: g+h+aa ta'i sngags kyis mig rna ba sna lce snying rnams la gdab /
NK020(wa)003:4541: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer

NK020(wa)003:4544: dwangs ma bde chen byang chub sems kyi ngo bor spar /

NK020(wa)003:4548: badz+ra t+ai k+sh+na mum zhes gri 'jam dpal gyi ngo bor gyur pa thogs te /

NK020(wa)003:4557: rang nyid sngar bdag bskyed gang yin der nga rgyal 'phos la /
NK020(wa)003:4559: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum zhes brjod pas mdun du

NK020(wa)003:4562: gyur / rang gi thugs ka nas ram yig thab

NK020(wa)003:4588: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK020(wa)003:4589: phrin las kun gyi dpang po mdzad //
NK020(wa)003:4592: me lha zhal cung zad gdangs pas bsregs blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun drangs nas gsol bar mos la /
NK020(wa)003:4593: pad+ma'i khu tshur gyis dgang blugs bzung nas mar khu

NK020(wa)003:4596: pus mo'i nang las mi 'da' bas g.yas su bskor

NK020(wa)003:4598: bya di bya ma h+aa na ye di bya bdag
