NK020(wa)003:4612: lha nyid thugs rje ye shes me 'bar ba'i rnam
NK020(wa)003:4613: par gyur pa'i klong du b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he
NK020(wa)003:4614: zhes pas gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bkra
NK020(wa)003:4616: +aam s+w+aa h+aum h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram
NK020(wa)003:4617: zhes brjod pas steng khang du snang mthas gtso byas
NK020(wa)003:4618: pa'i zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi lha bzhi bcu
NK020(wa)003:4619: rtsa gnyis dang 'og khang du pad+ma he ru kas
NK020(wa)003:4620: gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil
NK020(wa)003:4621: 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad sku mdog dmar po
NK020(wa)003:4622: g.yas pad+ma dang g.yon zhi ba rnams dril bu dang
NK020(wa)003:4623: khro bo rnams dung khrag bsnams pa sku las 'od
NK020(wa)003:4624: zer dmar po'i phreng ba mkha' khyab tu spro ba'i
NK020(wa)003:4625: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bkra lam gyis gsal bar
NK020(wa)003:4626: gyur / pra t+ya sogs kyis bskur brlab /
NK020(wa)003:4630: dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod dang tshogs rnams //
NK020(wa)003:4631: 'dir gshegs bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:4632: +aam s+w+aa h+aum h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo dzahh+aum
NK020(wa)003:4633: bam hoh e h+ye hi ru lu ru lu h+aum
NK020(wa)003:4634: b+h+yo dzah dzahs dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams man+da
NK020(wa)003:4635: la me tog gis mtshon par spyan drangs la /
NK020(wa)003:4636: de las me tog thab tu dor bas lha thams
NK020(wa)003:4637: cad gzhal yas khang gi gnas so sor rang gi
NK020(wa)003:4638: gdan la bzhugs par bsam pa tsam las bskur brlabs
NK020(wa)003:4641: de nas kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK020(wa)003:4643: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje 'od
NK020(wa)003:4644: kyi sbu gu can gyis bsregs blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK020(wa)003:4645: rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4646: +aam +aa ro lika zhes bdun gyis bkang ba'i dgang blugs sbyar ba sngar ltar /
NK020(wa)003:4647: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na sogs kyi mthar bdag cag dpon slob sogs btags pas lan gsum phul /
NK020(wa)003:4648: sngags des yam shing mar khu sreg rdzas rnams brgya rtsa sogs ji ltar rigs pa phul nas /
NK020(wa)003:4649: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa his bdud rtsi /
NK020(wa)003:4650: las gtor las gtor kyu blangs nas /
NK020(wa)003:4651: ma h+aa ba lid+ta pra t+aits+tsha kh+aa his gtor ma /
NK020(wa)003:4652: ma h+aa rak+ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa hi sa rak+ta phul la //
NK020(wa)003:4653: klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du /
NK020(wa)003:4654: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:4655: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas rnams kyis //
NK020(wa)003:4657: mchog thun dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:4658: zhes gsol ba btab pas lha tshogs rnams kyi sku
NK020(wa)003:4659: las 'od zer dmar po lcags kyu lta bu 'phros
NK020(wa)003:4660: pas bsgrub bya rnams rang dbang med par dbang du
NK020(wa)003:4662: de nas gtang rag gi mchod bstod bzod gsol byas nas /
NK020(wa)003:4663: dkyil 'khor dang 'brel tshe me tog gis spyan drangs te so so'i gnas su bzhugs par bsam /
NK020(wa)003:4665: dz+ny+aa na man+da la badz+ra muh sa ye shes pa gshegs /
NK020(wa)003:4666: dam tshig pa rang la thim par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:4668: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata ces blugs gzar gyi mar khus me gsol pas /
NK020(wa)003:4669: 'jig rten pa'i me lha sngar bzhin gsal bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4670: sreg rdzas lhag ma rnams phul /
NK020(wa)003:4672: las gtor nas gtor kyu blangs te /
NK020(wa)003:4673: ag+ne de wa ri shi ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa his gtor ma phul la 'dod don gsol /
NK020(wa)003:4675: badz+ra muhs me lha ye shes pa rang gnas su gshegs //
NK020(wa)003:4676: dam tshig pa 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:4677: bzhi pa drag po'i sbyin sreg ni /
NK020(wa)003:4678: chas gos nag po gyon nas rus sbal gyi 'dug
NK020(wa)003:4679: stangs kyis zhe sdang khros pa'i sems dang ldan pas
NK020(wa)003:4680: shis pa'i phyogs su kha bltas te /
NK020(wa)003:4681: bdag bskyed bzlas pa'i bar byas la /
NK020(wa)003:4682: las bum gyi chu'am bdud rtsis las gtor dang sreg rdzas bsang sbyangs /
NK020(wa)003:4683: stong pa'i ngang las ma a zhes pas nyi zla
NK020(wa)003:4684: ga'u'i snod du rang gi thugs ka nas h+aum nag
NK020(wa)003:4685: po spros pa 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur
NK020(wa)003:4686: pa las byung ba'i las gtor rin po che'i mchod
NK020(wa)003:4687: sdong 'od zer nag po 'phro ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4688: bsreg rdzas rnams zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi
NK020(wa)003:4689: ro brgya ldan pa nam mkha' rab 'byams gang bas
NK020(wa)003:4690: drag po'i las 'grub pa la thogs pa med pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4691: nus pa dang ldan par brlab /
NK020(wa)003:4692: de nas tshogs mchod gyi mchod bshags yan chad song ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4694: brub khung gi nya bo mdun du bkod la /
NK020(wa)003:4696: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)003:4697: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK020(wa)003:4698: phyi snod drag po'i dkyil 'khor lcags bsregs kyi rang
NK020(wa)003:4699: bzhin nag po gru gsum yangs pa 'od zer 'phro
NK020(wa)003:4700: ba'i dbus su nang bcud rdo rje rigs kyis gtso
NK020(wa)003:4701: byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor sprul pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4702: 'od zer nag po 'phro ba'i skur bzhengs par bsam
NK020(wa)003:4704: bsgrub bya che ge mo mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)003:4705: badz+ra am ku sha dzahdzahh+aum bam hoh zhes pas bkug cing bstim la /
NK020(wa)003:4707: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK020(wa)003:4709: yud tsam kyis ni brlag mdzad nas //
NK020(wa)003:4710: drag po'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:4711: ces bskul bas lha tshogs rnams drag po'i las mdzad pa la dgyes par gyur /
NK020(wa)003:4712: de nas las gtor nas lag gnyis kyi mtheb mdzub
NK020(wa)003:4713: kyis gtor kyu blangs pa g.yas g.yon du bskor zhing
NK020(wa)003:4715: lcags phye dug rdo 'bru nag chan //
NK020(wa)003:4716: khrag dang sbyar ba'i gtor ma ni //
NK020(wa)003:4717: gang la dmigs te bskor byas pas //
NK020(wa)003:4718: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams brlag par 'gyur //
NK020(wa)003:4719: ma h+aa ba lim ta sarba sha t+r+aum big+h+n+aam m+aa ra ya phata /
NK020(wa)003:4721: de nas drag po'i phur gsum po thal mo'i bar du bzung la /
NK020(wa)003:4722: badz+ra k+ai la ya phata dzahzhesa pas rang gi thugs ka nas badz+ra k+ai la ya spros /
NK020(wa)003:4723: phur bu la thims pas sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la yar gyur pa la /
NK020(wa)003:4724: sh+au nya t+aa sogs kyis bskur zhing brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)003:4726: phur bu kha dog nag po yi //
NK020(wa)003:4727: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse gru gsum //
NK020(wa)003:4728: lha rnams bkod de gdab par bya //
NK020(wa)003:4730: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba sha trum big+h+n+aam m+aa ra ya phata /
NK020(wa)003:4732: g+h+aa ta'i sngags kyis dpral mgrin snying ga rnams su gdab /
NK020(wa)003:4733: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK020(wa)003:4734: nag po 'phros dmigs bya la phog pas dug lnga
NK020(wa)003:4736: dwangs ma bde chen byang chub sems kyi ngo bor spar /
NK020(wa)003:4737: tshe rten 'od zer gyi rnam par 'dus pa bdag
NK020(wa)003:4738: gi rdo rje'i tshe srog dang dbyer med du gyur
NK020(wa)003:4739: par mos la snying ga'i phur bu gdon /
NK020(wa)003:4740: badz+ra t+aik+sh+na mum zhes gri 'jam dpal gyi ngo bor gyur pa thogs te /
NK020(wa)003:4741: sarba sha trum bi g+h+n+aam m+aa ra ya phata ces
NK020(wa)003:4742: pho'i rkang g.yas kyi mtheb chen dang mo'i g.yon pa'i
NK020(wa)003:4743: mthe chung nas gtub cing bsgral la /
NK020(wa)003:4744: ling ro cha gsum du byas te /
NK020(wa)003:4745: gcig ma h+aa ba lim ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa his stob /
NK020(wa)003:4747: gcig bro gdan gyi phyir bzhag go //
NK020(wa)003:4748: de nas sbyin sreg dngos ni /
NK020(wa)003:4749: rang nyid sngar bdag bskyed gang yin der nga rgyal 'phos la /
NK020(wa)003:4751: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum zhes brjod pas mdun du
NK020(wa)003:4752: drag po'i thab khung nag po gru gsum kha khyer
NK020(wa)003:4753: bang rim gsum ldan 'od zer nag po 'phro bar
NK020(wa)003:4754: gyur / rang gi thugs ka nas ram yig thab
NK020(wa)003:4755: nang du spros pa las ye shes kyi me 'od
NK020(wa)003:4757: ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:4758: ces pas shan pa'i me du ba med pa spar la /
NK020(wa)003:4759: thab kyi me'i dbus su nyi ma dang ra skyes
NK020(wa)003:4760: kyi gdan la ag+ne de wa rim shi h+aum zhes
NK020(wa)003:4761: brjod pas drag po'i me lha mthing nag drang srong
NK020(wa)003:4762: gi chas can tri sh+au la dang bgrang phreng 'dzin
NK020(wa)003:4764: sh+au nya t+aa sogs kyis bskur brlab /
NK020(wa)003:4765: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas shar
NK020(wa)003:4766: lho nas me lha 'khor bcas bzhengs par bsam la
NK020(wa)003:4767: / ag+na ye de wa sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes se gol bsnol mar gdab /
NK020(wa)003:4768: mda' dar dmar po g.yab cing /
NK020(wa)003:4770: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)003:4771: tshur gshegs tshul gshegs 'byung po che //
NK020(wa)003:4772: me lha drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK020(wa)003:4773: 'di nyid du ni gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)003:4774: lcags kyu'i rgya dang bcas ag+ne de wa ri shi dzahdzahsa spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)003:4776: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK020(wa)003:4778: rdo rje'i rigs las grub pa yi //
NK020(wa)003:4779: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK020(wa)003:4780: phrin las kun gyi dpang po mdzad //
NK020(wa)003:4783: me lha zhal cung zad gdangs pas bsregs blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyud drangs nas gsol bar mos la /
NK020(wa)003:4784: khro bo'i khu tshur gyis gzar bu bzung nas /
NK020(wa)003:4785: ag+ha ye s+w+aa h+aa zhes g.yon blugs gzar bdun gyis
NK020(wa)003:4786: g.yas pa'i dgang gzar bkang ba kha sbyar te pus
NK020(wa)003:4787: mo'i nang du mi 'da' bas g.yon du bskor zhing
NK020(wa)003:4788: / ag+ne de wa ri shi ha bya ka bya
NK020(wa)003:4789: di bya ma h+aa na ye di bya bdag cag
NK020(wa)003:4790: dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa la gnod cing 'tshe
NK020(wa)003:4791: ba'i dgra bgegs gdug pa can thams cad m+aa ra
NK020(wa)003:4792: / ya phata / ces lan gsum gyis dgang blugs phul /
NK020(wa)003:4793: sngags des yam shing dang mar khu sngon 'gros sreg
NK020(wa)003:4794: rdzas rnams so so'am gcig tu bsres nas grangs ji
NK020(wa)003:4797: rig pa'i rgyal po khyod kyis las thams cad byed pas sreg rdzas lha'i zhal du 'bul ba dang /
NK020(wa)003:4798: de nyid ye shes kyi mer byin gyis brlabs nas
NK020(wa)003:4799: bdag cag gi phrin las thams cad mdzad du gsol
NK020(wa)003:4802: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na dz+wa la ram zhes brjod pas me
NK020(wa)003:4803: lha nyid thugs rje ye shes me 'bar ba'i rnam
NK020(wa)003:4804: par gyur pa'i klong du b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+he
NK020(wa)003:4805: zhes pas gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bkra
NK020(wa)003:4807: h+aum mo s+w+aa +aam h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo
NK020(wa)003:4808: ram zhes brjod pas steng khang du mi bskyod pas
NK020(wa)003:4809: gtso byas pa'i zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi lha
NK020(wa)003:4810: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang 'og khang du badz+ra he
NK020(wa)003:4811: ru kas gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung tshogs chen 'dus
NK020(wa)003:4812: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad sku mdog
NK020(wa)003:4813: mthing nag g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon zhi ba rnams
NK020(wa)003:4814: dril bu dang khro bo rnams dung khrag bsnams pa
NK020(wa)003:4815: sku las 'od zer nag po'i phreng ba mkha' khyab
NK020(wa)003:4816: tu spro ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bkra lam
NK020(wa)003:4818: sh+au t+ya t+aa sogs kyis bskur brlab /
NK020(wa)003:4822: dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod dang 'brel tshe gzhal yas khang gdan bcas sngar bzhin bskyed rjes /
NK020(wa)003:4824: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)003:4825: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)003:4826: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK020(wa)003:4827: 'dir gshegs bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)003:4828: h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo dzahh+aum
NK020(wa)003:4829: bam hoh e h+ye hi ru lu ru lu h+aum
NK020(wa)003:4830: b+h+yo dzahdzahsa dkyil 'khor pa rnams man+dala me tog gis
NK020(wa)003:4832: de las me tog thab tu dor bas lha thams
NK020(wa)003:4833: cad gzhal yas khang gi gnas so sor rang rang
NK020(wa)003:4834: gi gdan la bzhugs par bsam pa tsam las bskur
NK020(wa)003:4836: gang ltar yang kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK020(wa)003:4838: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje 'od
NK020(wa)003:4839: kyi sbu gu can gyis bsregs blugs kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK020(wa)003:4840: rgyun drangs nas gsol bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4842: zhes bdun gyis bkang ba'i dgang blugs sbyar ba sngar
NK020(wa)003:4843: ltar gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na sogs kyi mthar bdag cag
NK020(wa)003:4844: dpon slob sogs btags pas lan gsum phul /
NK020(wa)003:4845: sngags des yam shing mar khu sreg rdzas rnam brgya rtsa sogs ji ltar rigs pa phul nas /
NK020(wa)003:4846: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa his bdud rtsi /
NK020(wa)003:4847: las gtor nas blangs pa'i gtor kyu ma h+aa ba lim ta pra t+ai ts+tsha kh+aa his gtor ma /
NK020(wa)003:4848: ma h+aa rak+ta pra t+aits+tsha kh+aa his rak+ta phul la //
NK020(wa)003:4849: klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK020(wa)003:4850: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)003:4851: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas rnams kyi //
NK020(wa)003:4852: gnod byed dgra bgegs brlag gyur nas //
NK020(wa)003:4853: mchog thun dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK020(wa)003:4854: zhes gsol ba btab pas lha tshogs rnams kyi sku
NK020(wa)003:4855: las 'od zer nag po mtshon cha'i char lta bu
NK020(wa)003:4856: 'phros pas gnod byed dgra bgegs thams cad brlag par
NK020(wa)003:4857: bsam mo // de nas gtang rag gi mchod bstod bzod gsol byas nas /
NK020(wa)003:4858: dkyil 'khor dang 'brel tshe me tog gis spyan drangs te so so'i gnas su bzhugs par bsam /
NK020(wa)003:4859: ma 'brel na dz+ny+aa na man+da la badz+ra muhs ye
NK020(wa)003:4860: shes pa gshegs dam tshig pa rang la thim par
NK020(wa)003:4861: bsam mo // slar yang ag+na ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:4862: ces blugs gzar gyi mar khus me gsos pas /
NK020(wa)003:4863: 'jig rten pa'i me lha sngar bzhin gsal bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)003:4866: las gtor nas gtor kyu blangs te a g+ne de
NK020(wa)003:4867: wa rim shi ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi
NK020(wa)003:4868: sa gtor ma phul la 'dod don gsol /
NK020(wa)003:4870: badz+ra muhs ye shes pa rang gnas su gshegs //
NK020(wa)003:4871: dam tshig pa 'bar ba'i rnam par gyur par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)003:4872: de ltar las bzhi ka la sbyin sreg bsdus pa'i lugs byed na /
NK020(wa)003:4873: lid+ga bsham bsgral stob pa rnas don nas sreg chog brkyang pa byas kyang rung ngo //
NK020(wa)003:4874: gsum pa rjes las bzhi thun mong du bstan pas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK020(wa)003:4875: ling ro sngar gud du bzhag pa de spungs pa'i mtha'am /
NK020(wa)003:4876: lid+ga med na thab kyi mthar mched rnams bro ra
NK020(wa)003:4877: bcas nas las bzhi gang yin gyi bro sgrub khog
NK020(wa)003:4878: tu bshad pa ltar brdungs rjes /
NK020(wa)003:4879: ling ro de'am med na thal sol zhi ba la lam gyi dkyil du /
NK020(wa)003:4882: drag po la lha 'dre gnyan po gnas pa'i sar las mthun gyi brub khung brus par blug /
NK020(wa)003:4883: de steng g.yam pa la 'og phyogs su zhi bar dkar po //
NK020(wa)003:4886: drag por h+aum nag po dang /
NK020(wa)003:4887: steng phyogs su lam ser po re bris pas /
NK020(wa)003:4888: lam s+t+wam+b+ha ni stam+b+ha ni h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)003:4889: ces kha bcad la sas bsub cing /
NK020(wa)003:4890: las dang rjes su mthun pa'i smon lam gdab par bya'o //
NK020(wa)003:4891: ngag tshig 'di'i mthus rgyal pa'i phrin las bzhi //
NK020(wa)003:4892: gdul bya'i rgyud la dbang 'byor ye shes mes //
NK020(wa)003:4893: las nyon sgrib pa'i chos can dbyings sbyangs nas //
NK020(wa)003:4894: don gnyis mtha' phyin dpal la spyod par shog /
NK020(wa)003:4895: 'dus pa mdo'i las bzhi'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga bshad pa'i le tshan no //
NK020(wa)003:4898: da ni sgrub khog gi lnga ba gtor ma btang ba'i skabs su /
NK020(wa)003:4899: las mkhan gyis dkyil 'khor khang ba'i phyi rol tu lhag chog rgyas par bya /
NK020(wa)003:4901: dang po bsham zhing byin gyis rlob pa /
NK020(wa)003:4903: gsum pa mchod pa'i las rim gyi nang tshan spyir mchod pa dang /
NK020(wa)003:4904: bye brag tu mchod pa las kha phru gdab pa yan chad /
NK020(wa)003:4905: bzhi pa bshags shing bsdu ba rnams sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs ltar las /
NK020(wa)003:4906: bye brag tu mchod pa'i nang tshan rkang thon du mchod pa'i tshig /
NK020(wa)003:4908: bcom ldan rdo rje mi bskyod pas //
NK020(wa)003:4909: zhes sogs lung gi lhag chog chung ba yin pas /
NK020(wa)003:4910: 'dir de'i tshab tu lung gi lhag chog che ba 'di bya ste /
NK020(wa)003:4912: dpal chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:4913: goo r+ai'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:4914: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad rnams kyis //
NK020(wa)003:4915: goo r+ai khro mo brgyad du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4916: srin mo chen mo brgyad rnams btul //
NK020(wa)003:4917: byang sems sa yi snying po yis /
NK020(wa)003:4918: khro mo chen mo goo r+ai ra sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4919: srin mo chen mo king thod btul //
NK020(wa)003:4920: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK020(wa)003:4921: rdo rje'i dam las bro skyal te //
NK020(wa)003:4922: gtan gyi bran du mchis kyi 'tshal //
NK020(wa)003:4923: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK020(wa)003:4924: rdo rje'i dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK020(wa)003:4925: las kyi lhag ma 'di longs la /
NK020(wa)003:4926: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK020(wa)003:4927: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:4928: phyi yi dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig /
NK020(wa)003:4929: ces lhag ma la sogs pa'i rkang pa dgu po 'og ma kun la 'agre'o //
NK020(wa)003:4930: byang sems nam mkha'i snying po yis /
NK020(wa)003:4931: khro mo chen mo tsoo r+air sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4932: srin mo chen mo mda' 'phen btul //
NK020(wa)003:4933: lhag ma sogs rkang pa dgu /
NK020(wa)003:4934: byang sems spyan ras gzigs dbang gis /
NK020(wa)003:4935: khro mo chen mo pra mor sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4936: srin mo chen mo 'dzin byed btul //
NK020(wa)003:4938: byang sems phyag na rdo rje yis /
NK020(wa)003:4939: khro mo chen mo be tar sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4940: srin mo chen mo za byed btul //
NK020(wa)003:4942: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa yis /
NK020(wa)003:4943: khro mo chen mo puk+kara sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4944: srin mo nang rol 'dren ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:4946: byang sems sgrib pa rnam sel gyis /
NK020(wa)003:4947: khro mo chen mo g+hasmara sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4948: srin mo chen mo rab 'jigs btul //
NK020(wa)003:4950: byang sems kun tu bzang po yis /
NK020(wa)003:4951: khro mo chen mo sma shar sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4952: srin mo chen mo srog gcod btul //
NK020(wa)003:4954: byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal gyis //
NK020(wa)003:4955: khro mo chen mo tsan+dara sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4956: srin mo chen mo smyon ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:4959: dpal chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:4960: phra men tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:4961: dpal chen khrag 'thung zhal bzhad pas //
NK020(wa)003:4962: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad rnams kyis //
NK020(wa)003:4963: sid+ha phra men brgyad du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4964: srin mo mgo brnyan brgyad rnams btul //
NK020(wa)003:4965: shar phyogs lha mo l+aa s+ye mas /
NK020(wa)003:4966: khro mo chen mo seng mgor sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4967: srin mo 'jigs byed seng mgo btul //
NK020(wa)003:4969: lho phyogs lha mo m+aa l+ye mas //
NK020(wa)003:4970: phra men chen mo stag mgor sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4971: srin mo za byed stag mgo btul //
NK020(wa)003:4973: nub phyogs lha mo g+airti mas //
NK020(wa)003:4974: phra men chen mo wa mgor sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4975: srin mo len byed wa mgo btul //
NK020(wa)003:4977: byang phyogs lha mo nirti mas //
NK020(wa)003:4978: phra men chen mo spyang mgor sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4979: srin mo ra ro khyi mgo btul //
NK020(wa)003:4981: shar lho lha mo d+h+au pe mas //
NK020(wa)003:4982: phra men chen mo rgod mgor sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4983: srin mo bya rgod mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:4985: lho nub lha mo me tog mas //
NK020(wa)003:4986: phra men kad+ga'i mgo ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4987: srin mo kad+ga'i mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:4989: nub byang lha mo mar me mas //
NK020(wa)003:4990: phra men bya rog mgo ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4991: srin mo 'joms byed bya rog btul //
NK020(wa)003:4993: byang shar lha mo dri chab mas //
NK020(wa)003:4994: phra men u l+au mu khar sprul //
NK020(wa)003:4995: srin mo bskul byed 'ug mgo btul //
NK020(wa)003:4998: dpal chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:4999: sgo ma'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5000: tshad med sgo ma bzhi rnams kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5001: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5002: shar gyi byams pa lcags kyu mas //
NK020(wa)003:5003: sgo ma rta gdong lcags kyur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5004: srin mo rta yi mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5006: lho yi snying rje zhags pa mas //
NK020(wa)003:5007: sgo ma phag gdong zhags par sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5008: srin mo phag gi mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5010: nub kyi dga' ba lcags sgrogs mas //
NK020(wa)003:5011: sgo ma dred mgo lcags sgrog sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5012: srin mo dred kyi mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5014: byang gi btang snyoms dril bu mas //
NK020(wa)003:5015: sgo ma chen mo spyang mgor sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5016: srin mo chen mo spyang mgo btul //
NK020(wa)003:5019: dpal chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:5020: spor ma'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5021: dpal chen thugs rje sbyor ba las //
NK020(wa)003:5022: thub drug yid chos brgyad po yis //
NK020(wa)003:5023: spor ma chen mo brgyad du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5024: phyogs skyong brgyad kyi bu mo btul //
NK020(wa)003:5026: kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:5027: spor ma nyi zer zhags par sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5028: 'bar ma nyi zer zhags pa btul //
NK020(wa)003:5030: yi dwags thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:5031: spor ma glog phreng 'dzin du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5032: 'bar ma chen mo glog phreng btul //
NK020(wa)003:5034: mi yi thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:5035: spor ma mdung thung 'phen du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5036: 'bar ma gtum mo mdung thung btul //
NK020(wa)003:5038: dmyal ba'i thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:5039: spor ma gshin rje ral grir sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5040: 'bar ma gshin rje ral gri btul //
NK020(wa)003:5042: kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:5043: spor ma dril 'khrol ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5046: lha min thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:5047: spor ma skra mda' gtong du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5050: byol song thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:5051: spor ma blag sha sdeb tu sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5052: 'bar ma ban glang sna tshogs btul //
NK020(wa)003:5054: lha yi thub pa gnas gyur pa //
NK020(wa)003:5055: spor ma khyung thogs ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5056: 'bar ma gnod sbyin khyung thogs btul //
NK020(wa)003:5059: dpal chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:5060: gsang ba'i yum bzhis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5061: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba las //
NK020(wa)003:5062: yi ge h+aum bzhi sprul byas nas //
NK020(wa)003:5063: de las gsang ba'i yum bzhir sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5064: de bzhis srin mo bzhi btul te //
NK020(wa)003:5065: shar gyi bde ba za byed mas //
NK020(wa)003:5066: srin mo za byed khrag 'thung btul //
NK020(wa)003:5068: lho yi bde ba rmongs byed mas //
NK020(wa)003:5069: srin mo chen mo rus 'chang btul //
NK020(wa)003:5071: nub kyi bde ba rgyas 'debs mas //
NK020(wa)003:5072: srin mo dur khrod ro rkun btul //
NK020(wa)003:5074: byang gi bde ba tshe 'phel mas //
NK020(wa)003:5075: srin mo dur khrod bdag mo btul //
NK020(wa)003:5078: dpal chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:5079: dbang phyug tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5080: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba las //
NK020(wa)003:5081: tshangs ma la sogs ye shes pa'i //
NK020(wa)003:5082: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5083: las kyi dbang mo mgo brnyan tshogs //
NK020(wa)003:5084: 'jig rten rnam pa'i srin po ste //
NK020(wa)003:5085: lag na glo snying nang khrol thogs //
NK020(wa)003:5086: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs su sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5087: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad la /
NK020(wa)003:5088: 'gal byed gnod pa'i tshogs rnams btul //
NK020(wa)003:5091: dpal chen rak+ta he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:5092: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5093: dpal chen sku yi 'od zer las //
NK020(wa)003:5094: sems dpa' sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5095: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5096: srin mo sum cu rtsa gnyis btul //
NK020(wa)003:5097: byang sems rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK020(wa)003:5098: mkha' 'gro dga' byed ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5099: srin mo chen mo dga' byed btul //
NK020(wa)003:5101: sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal po yis //
NK020(wa)003:5103: srin mo chen mo 'dren byed btul //
NK020(wa)003:5105: sems dpa' rdo rje chags pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:5106: mkha' 'gro gsod byed ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5107: srin mo chen mo gsod byed btul //
NK020(wa)003:5109: sems dpa' rdo rje legs pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:5110: mkha' 'gro spor byed ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5111: srin mo spor ma chen mo btul //
NK020(wa)003:5113: sems dpa' rdo rje rin chen gyis //
NK020(wa)003:5115: srin mo chen mo 'bar ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5117: sems dpa' rdo rje nyi ma yis //
NK020(wa)003:5118: mkha' 'gro gzi brjid ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5119: srin mo chen mo gzi brjid btul //
NK020(wa)003:5121: sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK020(wa)003:5122: mkha' 'gro bdud rtsi rgyal byed sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5123: srin mo rgyal byed dbang ldan btul //
NK020(wa)003:5125: sems dpa' rdo rje bzhad pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:5127: srin mo chen mo 'joms ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5129: sems dpa' rdo rje chos rab kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5130: mkha' 'gro chags byed ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5131: srin mo chen mo chags ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5133: sems dpa' rdo rje rnon po yis //
NK020(wa)003:5134: mkha' 'gro chags bral ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5135: srin mo chen mo chags bral btul //
NK020(wa)003:5137: sems dpa' rdo rje 'khor lo yis //
NK020(wa)003:5139: srin mo chen mo 'khor lo btul //
NK020(wa)003:5141: sems dpa' rdo rje smra ba yis //
NK020(wa)003:5143: srin mo chen mo rgyas ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5145: sems dpa' rdo rje sna tshogs kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5146: mkha' 'gro sna tshogs gzugs su sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5147: srin mo chen mo sna tshogs btul //
NK020(wa)003:5149: sems dpa' rdo rje go cha yis //
NK020(wa)003:5150: mkha' 'gro chen mo bsrung mor sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5151: srin mo chen mo ma srin btul //
NK020(wa)003:5153: sems dpa' rdo rje mche ba yis //
NK020(wa)003:5154: mkha' 'gro gnod sbyin ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5155: srin mo chen mo gnod sbyin btul //
NK020(wa)003:5157: sems dpa' rdo rje khu tshur gyis //
NK020(wa)003:5159: srin mo chen mo 'phrog ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5161: sems dpa' dpa' bar 'gro ba yis //
NK020(wa)003:5162: mkha' 'gro bya rog gdong du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5163: srin mo chen mo rig 'byin btul //
NK020(wa)003:5165: sems dpa' kun tu bzang po yis //
NK020(wa)003:5167: srin mo chen mo 'jigs byed btul //
NK020(wa)003:5169: sems dpa' zla 'od gzhon nu yis //
NK020(wa)003:5171: srin mo chen mo mun mthong btul //
NK020(wa)003:5173: byang chub sems dpa' bzang skyong gis //
NK020(wa)003:5174: mkha' 'gro bzhad gdong ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5175: srin mo bzhad kyi mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5177: sems dpa' d+r+wa ba can 'od kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5178: mkha' 'gro khyi mgo ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5179: srin mo khyi yi mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5181: sems dpa' rdo rje snying po yis //
NK020(wa)003:5182: mkha' 'gro phag gdong ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5183: srin mo phag gi mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5185: sems dpa' nam mkha' mdzod kyis ni //
NK020(wa)003:5186: mkha' 'gro rnga mong gdong mar sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5187: srin mo rnga mong mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5189: sems dpa' 'od dpag med kyis ni //
NK020(wa)003:5190: mkha' 'gro bong bu'i gdong mar sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5191: srin mo bong bu'i mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5193: sems dpa' ngan song kun sbyong gis //
NK020(wa)003:5194: mkha' 'gro ra mgo ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5195: srin mo ra yi mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5197: sems dpa' rgyal ba ye shes kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5198: mkha' 'gro byi la'i mgo can sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5199: srin mo byi la'i mgo can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5201: sems dpa' blo gros mi zad pas //
NK020(wa)003:5202: mkha' 'gro keng rus ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5203: srin mo keng rus 'dzin ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5205: sems dpa' spobs pa brtsegs pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:5206: mkha' 'gro rus phreng can du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5207: srin mo rus pa'i phreng can btul //
NK020(wa)003:5209: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:5210: mkha' 'gro bum sna ma ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5211: srin mo bum sna'i chung ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5213: sems dpa' ngan song kun 'dren gyis //
NK020(wa)003:5215: gshin rje rnam 'joms chung ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5217: sems dpa' spos kyi glang po yis //
NK020(wa)003:5218: mkha' 'gro d+ha sha g+r+ai bar sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5220: byang sems don yod grub pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:5222: gnod sbyin 'bod sgrog chung ma btul //
NK020(wa)003:5224: h+aum dpal chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:5225: pho nya'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5226: 'od zer sum brgya drug cur las //
NK020(wa)003:5227: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5228: shar du 'od zer dkar po las //
NK020(wa)003:5229: dung gi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5230: dri za'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK020(wa)003:5232: lho ru 'od zer sngon po las //
NK020(wa)003:5233: lcags kyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5234: gshin rje'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK020(wa)003:5236: nub tu 'od zer dmar po las //
NK020(wa)003:5237: zangs kyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5238: klu yi gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK020(wa)003:5240: byang du 'od zer ljang khu las //
NK020(wa)003:5241: g.yu yi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5242: gnod sbyin gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK020(wa)003:5244: steng du 'od zer ser po las //
NK020(wa)003:5245: gser gyi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5246: ya bdud gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK020(wa)003:5249: bse yi mi mo drug cur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5250: ma mo'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK020(wa)003:5253: dpa' chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:5254: king chen tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5255: dpal chen he ru ka bzhad pas //
NK020(wa)003:5256: rdo rje king chen bco brgyad sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5257: gdon gyi rgyal po bco brgyad btul //
NK020(wa)003:5260: dpal chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:5261: ma bdud tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5262: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba yis //
NK020(wa)003:5263: yi ge h+aum bdun spros pa las //
NK020(wa)003:5264: gsang ba'i ma mo bdun du sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5265: srin mo chen mo bdun po btul //
NK020(wa)003:5268: dpa' chen rak+sha he ru kar //
NK020(wa)003:5269: sring mo bzhi yis bskor ba ni //
NK020(wa)003:5270: gling bzhi dbang 'gyur chen mo yis //
NK020(wa)003:5271: sring mo chen mo bzhi ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5272: bgegs kyi rgyal po bzhi po btul //
NK020(wa)003:5275: bcom ldan rdo rje mi bskyod pas //
NK020(wa)003:5276: dpal chen badz+ra he rur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5277: dbus kyi yi dwags srin po btul //
NK020(wa)003:5279: bcom ldan rnams par snang mdzad kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5280: dpal chen bud+d+ha he rur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5281: shar gyi dri za srin po btul //
NK020(wa)003:5283: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan gyis //
NK020(wa)003:5284: dpa' chen rat+na he rur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5285: lho yi gshin rje srin po btul //
NK020(wa)003:5287: bcom lda snang ba mtha' yas kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5288: dpal chen pad+ma he rur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5289: nub kyi klu yi srin po btul //
NK020(wa)003:5291: bcom ldan don yod grub pa yis //
NK020(wa)003:5292: dpal chen karma he rur sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5293: byang phyogs gnod sbyin srin po btul //
NK020(wa)003:5294: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK020(wa)003:5295: rdo rje'i dam las bro skyal te //
NK020(wa)003:5296: gtan gyi bran du mchis kyis 'tshal //
NK020(wa)003:5297: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK020(wa)003:5298: rdo rje'i dam las ma 'da' zhig /
NK020(wa)003:5299: las kyi lhag ma 'di longs la //
NK020(wa)003:5300: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK020(wa)003:5301: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:5302: phyi yi dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig /
NK020(wa)003:5303: rigs kyi yum chen lnga rnams kyis //
NK020(wa)003:5304: khro mo chen mo lnga ru sprul //
NK020(wa)003:5305: srin mo chen mo lnga rnams btul //
NK020(wa)003:5306: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK020(wa)003:5307: sngon gyi dam las ma g.yel bar //
NK020(wa)003:5308: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la /
NK020(wa)003:5309: thugs dam chen po ji bzhin du //
NK020(wa)003:5310: rnal 'byor bcom ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK020(wa)003:5312: mdo'i lhag chog 'dor len gyi sgo nas lung lhag che ba ji ltar bya ba'i le tshan no //
NK020(wa)003:5313: bla ma'i gsung ngag bdud rtsi rna dbang las /
NK020(wa)003:5314: chos kyi 'khor lor yongs 'khyil 'dus pa mdo'i //
NK020(wa)003:5315: cho ga'i bzur 'debs sngon med legs bshad dpal //
NK020(wa)003:5316: lha yi dpag bsam snye ma de ring 'khrungs //
NK020(wa)003:5317: dge 'dis rgyud lung man ngag rtser son pa //
NK020(wa)003:5318: mdo yi dbang bzhi'i chu bos rab smin nas //
NK020(wa)003:5319: bskyed rdzogs chos kyis 'gro kun rgyud grol te //
NK020(wa)003:5320: dpal ldan 'bras rgyud sku bzhi thob par shog /
NK020(wa)003:5321: 'dus pa mdo'i sgrub dkyil sgrub khog dang bcas pa'i
NK020(wa)003:5322: zur 'debs dpag bsam snye ma zhes bya ba 'di
NK020(wa)003:5323: yang / mkha' shing grub pa'i skyes chen dam pa du ma'i gsung gis bskul ba la brten nas /
NK020(wa)003:5324: rigs kun khyab bdag dpal rdo rje 'chang chen po
NK020(wa)003:5325: rje btsun bla ma dam pa gter chen chos kyi
NK020(wa)003:5326: rgyal po'i bka' drin gyis 'tsho ba'i smyos kyi dge
NK020(wa)003:5327: slong rmongs pa d+har+m+aa sh+r+ais shing mo bya'i lo rgyal
